As the flagship, I participated in many naval exercises, carried out surveillance, and engaged in confrontations, leaving behind lasting achievements that I can be proud of. Though I never participated in live combat, I am the destroyer with the most miles under her belt in the entire world!
501010.main: Woah, this is my first time seeing a battleship! |Where did Fu Shun run off to? Would it really kill her to do as I say every now and then? |My sisters - Fu Shun, Chang Chun, and Tai Yuan - are all my pride and joy!
501010.win_mvp: Commander, being able to help you out is the greatest!
501010.feeling5: I'm so blessed to have met you, Commander. I've made so many friends and so many memories... Hey, Commander, once I complete my duty as one of the "Four Unbreakables," let's go travel around the world together!

501010.hp_warning: Commander, concentrate and be extra careful!
501010.mail: Commander, you have new mail. Should I unseal it for you?
501010.skill: Let the protection of heaven surround the brave!

301270.feeling4: Your Grace, I beg your pardon. Recently I find myself distracted from the mission, thinking again and again about Your Grace's "communication." Please, you must punish me...
301270.propose: I once thought that absolute devotion to the mission was all there was to being a ninja, but I have learned so much from you, Commander... I, Kuroshio, from this point forward, am no longer your shadow alone, Commander, I am now your partner. And we will stand together until the end of our days.
301270.detail: Your Grace... Please don't stare at me so...
couple_encourage: For the master...!
301270.upgrade: I stand ready to execute your will.
301270.battle: Naught but death awaits those who oppose my master.
301270.home: Your Grace, are you tired? Is there any way I can be of assistance to you?
301270.mission_complete: Your Grace, mission rewards have been issued. Inspect them at your leisure.
301270.feeling3: While I struggle with Your Grace's concepts of "communication" and "games," still... I... can't say I dislike them.
301270.unlock: Third ship of the Kagerou-class, Kuroshio reporting in... I am here to carry out my master's will.
301270.feeling2: A true ninja has no need of emotion. She needs only her master's will to execute.
301270.touch2: As this body belongs to Your Grace, please do with it as you will... Nnng... Aaaah...
301270.profile: Third ship of the Kagerou-class, Kuroshio. As part of the 2nd Fleet and Destroyer Division 15, I joined in the Battle of the Java Sea, operations in the South Pacific, the Third Battle of the Solomon Islands, and other engagements until I was sunk during a transport mission. ... I will not let that happen again. I will commit all of my resources to ensure that I am of service to Your Grace.
301270.main: Hm...? Your Grace? Did you want me to say something?|I am not sure what to say... But I would be happy to listen to anything Your Grace wishes to impart.|The flower in my hair? It was a gift from Oyashio. Oyashio, she's... very colorful.
301270.win_mvp: I am Your Grace's shadow. I have no need of glory or acclaim.
301270.feeling5: So this is an "emotion"... before such things I had no problem keeping a clear head, but even now it seems not so wicked... Yes, this "emotion" drives a powerful need to stand by Your Grace's side, and it grows ever stronger.
301270.lose: Your Grace, it is time to retreat. I will cover your withdrawal.
301270.expedition: Your Grace, the fleet you dispatched on commission has returned as scheduled.
301270.mail: Your Grace, a letter has arrived.
301270.mission: Your Grace, a new mission has been issued.

Or maybe some wisdom cubes, nya? Or... maybe a generous bit of both, nya?
312012.feeling5: Commander, Akashi wants a lap pillow, nya! ...The other way around? No way, nya! Akashi wants to curl up in your lap, nya!
312012.drop_descrip: Heheh, this is what I've been saving up for, nya~♪ A special dress that combines Gothic fashion with Sakura charm! Commander, how about those gems, nya?

107031.detail: Commander...? Thank you for before. As an Eagle Union carrier, I shouldn't be feeling down after losing in beach volleyball! ...Yep! Saratoga, launching again!
107031.upgrade: If I evolve once more, I'm gonna show the Royals what I'm made of!
107031.home: We~ are back~ Phew~ it's so hot!
107031.login: Commander, let's head to the beach today! I want to eat chilled watermelon!
107031.mission_complete: Commander, are you done with the mission? I'm tired from volleyball practice as well. Phew... It's so hot I'm too worn to prank...
107031.unlock: Even in a day off, I'm not loosening up! Phew... Swimsuit, check. All preparations complete! Launch time! I'll show you Sister Sara's power!

107031.touch2: Commander! Saratoga won! Come and see! I beat Honolulu! She can't believe it!

107031.drop_descrip: Even if we don't get to relax on holiday, it's always good to have a swimsuit! Ok, let's go! Are you ready to swim?

103131.drop_descrip: Textbooks, pencils and erasers... hey, must students always pay attention in class... Commander? Can you arrange for us to get more extracurricular activities?

202170.feeling4: You end up on the path of Evil if you only focus on your own justice, your own desires. Never let the Darkness out of sight. I'm here with you, Boss.
202170.propose: Boss, what we are doing is carving a path through the Wilderness. And being here to walk beside you is the greatest blessing of my life.
202170.detail: Boss, can you check if these chains are covering my left eye? I'll reposition my arm.
couple_encourage: Let's go, partner!
Sheffy, have you awakened to your Heart of Justice?
202170.feeling1: Unfortunately, Boss, it seems your Goals differ from mine...
202170.upgrade: It's not enough... I need more power...!
202170.home: I feel Evil wriggling within the depths of my heart... Boss, let's enjoy this Peace while it lasts.
202170.login: Boss, my Eye has seen it... Your necktie is slightly loose.

202170.feeling3: An age of justice? That is not what I want. Where there is light, there is dark. Evil cannot be eradicated so easily, Boss.
202170.unlock: Ugh... my eye is throbbing again... So you're the Boss, huh? The name's Jamaica. All is in the name of Justice...
202170.feeling2: Boss, care for a chat? There seems to be a need for us to Know one another.
202170.touch: ...Boss, keep your hands to yourself. Otherwise you'll startle me when I'm concentrating.
202170.touch2: ...Boss, t-this isn't the place for this...
202170.profile: It is I. I, Jamaica, who sabotaged Iron Blood's operation in the Barents Sea; I, who sealed Scharnhorst to her fate: to sink in the Battle of the North Cape. Operation Tungsten? Of course I was there. As was I during the subsequent civil war... As long as Evil continues its march, I will keep fighting... Yes, all my choices were made by Justice itself...
202170.main: Boss, is the "you" that my Eye sees really "you"?|Boss, care to race with me? I will show you what real Lighting looks like.|I feel it. Somewhere in the world, the darkness of night is enveloping something...
202170.win_mvp: Eradicating you fiends is the meaning of Justice.
202170.feeling5: One needs a Heart of Justice. As long as we have it, no matter what struggles we face, we will surely see our journey to the end. We are Just, therefore... you are never alone, Boss.
202170.lose: It's not pain I fear... it's being completely helpless... Ugh!
202170.hp_warning: Victory comes to those who are determined! Stand Proud!
202170.expedition: Boss, the commission team has returned... "Stop posing on the veranda"? U-understood...
202170.mail: Boss, you have mail from one of your partners.
202170.skill: The eulogy of life... is the eulogy of Courage!
202170.mission: Boss, are there any Missions for me to tackle?

207030.feeling4: Commander... do you want to try... a soft landing?
207030.propose: Even though light should be shared equally among us all, it's fine for you to have a bit more. After all, I've received something important from the Commander as well.

couple_encourage: How's Saratoga doing these days?
May the light illuminate Kaede's Legion!
207030.feeling1: Not even my light can reach the darkness within your heart?

207030.touch2: Seriously, Commander, you're like a little kid.

201020.feeling4: Commander... give this some thought: isn't it boring, being with me...?
201020.propose: ... Sorry... I'm just so happy that I don't even know what to say... I'll take good care of this...

201020.feeling2: I just can't be bothered... Maybe I should go to sleep...

201020.mail: Got some mail... Wonder if it's for you.

202171.touch2: Boss... even though I told you to hold on to me tight, I didn't mean right there...

207031.drop_descrip: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?

201021.drop_descrip: Hm? Guess we're both about to head out... Don't stare at me like that... Even I go outdoors sometimes... Since we're both, uh, headed the same way... maybe we could... walk there together?

301790.hp_warning: Agh... So this is why they say you can't flee from pain...

... I just have a slow reaction time...

207040.hp_warning: Oh dear, I've let my guard down.

207040.skill: O beautiful world, sing to me a song!

201030.propose: Even though we're married, we still have long times ahead... But even in days where things don't happen, as long as you are here, Commander, things won't get boring. Ehehe~

201030.feeling1: I was mistaken for being so friendly with you... I'm sorry...

201030.feeling2: Say, Commander, do you think we get along with each other very well? Yes, yes! I too, think that you are very much like a close friend!
201030.touch: Umm... if we walk so close together, people might misunderstand...
201030.touch2: Whaa! This kind of thing... At least wait until you're at home!

201030.main: Are you hungry, Commander? Let's have a lunch together?|Uh, C-Commander, are there spare parts? I want to do a bit of periodic checking~|Uh, have you heard about it? Ugh... so you've gotten bored of me... Just kidding~
201030.win_mvp: That was a good battle, cost performance wise~
201030.feeling5: This is probably what daily life feels like, I think... Nothing too intense, just living on normally. So Commander, shall we continue to live our days just like this?
201030.lose: Wha! Hurry and retreat, or else we'll get heatstroke!

201030.mail: Ah, you were just gone. A letter came by– Here.
201030.drop_descrip: A-class destroyer – Ardent, Hull Number H41.
201030.mission: You have a mission, you know? Good timing. I'm now letting you know what it is.

102050.feeling4: I think I've been more at ease lately... No, I was just too tense up until now. It's all thanks to the courage you've given me by being beside me.
102050.propose: A promise... from you, Commander? I see... I'm so happy...
102050.detail: I can't rely on this thing alone...
couple_encourage: Penny, cover me!
SG, full area scan! I will never let that tragedy repeat itself!
Chicky Unit... sounds kind of cute!
102050.upgrade: I'll use this power to protect everyone!
102050.battle: The enemy can't hide from me.
102050.home: Did everyone make it back safe and sound? Good. But there's spare parts lying around in the docks now... I wonder why...
102050.login: ... Ah, welcome back, Commander. Sorry, I was just brooding over something.
102050.mission_complete: Resources are no good if they just pile up. We should make use of them.
102050.feeling3: My expression? Ah... it's because I left while we were on the losing end of the war... I might just not be so used to peace and happiness. But don't worry, I'll be fine!

102050.feeling2: If only my recon could help the others...
102050.touch: Hm? I'm fine. I'm just... a little distracted.
102050.touch2: If this makes you feel good, then... I'm fine with it.
102050.profile: I was designed to be on par with heavy cruisers, but just my power alone isn't enough to save everyone... Commander, can you help me?

102050.lose: ... Please, save me... Ignore the enemy, just let them go...
102050.hp_warning: SG, lock on the enemy position!
102050.expedition: Hey, Commander, could I lend my SG radar to my sisters this time?
102050.mail: You've got new mail. It's important to stay in touch with your loved ones.
102050.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Helena, Hull Number CL-50!
102050.mission: Bit by bit we'll build the foundation for victory. We'll start by doing missions.

101411.detail: The teacher didn't find out about the note I passed, right? Commander, don't you tattle on me, got it?
101411.home: I'm down for a slightly longer recess~

101411.mail: This envelope with a heart on it sure is suspicious... Commander, who'd you get it from?
101411.drop_descrip: Stanly's brand new "Student Mode," activate! Commander, come check out my new look!

501040.propose: Thanks, Commander... Even though I'm still not very reliable, from now on, you can count on me!

couple_encourage: To help An Shan, I have to do my best...

The "Nuclear Physics Hypothesis" is a very interesting book... It would be nice if my sisters liked it too...

501040.hp_warning: Eh...? U-um... what should I do...
501040.expedition: Eek! Someone came back... Oh, An Shan, I'm fine...
501040.mail: C-commander, there's new mail. Perhaps Fu Shun should... um, never mind...
501040.drop_descrip: An Shan-class destroyer No. 4 - Tai Yuan (104)
501040.skill: Let the heavens focus our minds, so we can adapt to any situation!
501040.mission: This mission... looks quite difficult. Will we be able to do it?

103010.feeling4: Are you tired? OK, come over here and lie down. I'll wake you up in an hour! Good night~

103010.feeling1: Hey, Commander, this isn't OK at all.

I never realized how peaceful and beautiful snow can be.

102051.drop_descrip: I... want to be part of the new year festivities too. Oh, you don't have to worry about me. I'm no longer the fledgling I once was.

couple_encourage: My sister, let us fight for glory!
203080.feeling1: Please do not bring shame upon the royal family.

203080.feeling2: Commander, don't be blinded by romance.

203080.lose: Curses... I shall have my revenge!

203080.skill: For the glory of the royal family!

201290.mission_complete: Mission complete~♪ Echo will bring you the rewards, Commander!
201290.feeling3: Commander, you can't give up so easily. You must get into shape~ Come on, take a stroll around the port with Echo~♪

201290.feeling2: Commander, please be positive. Be like Echo: smile, and be happy~ Ehehe♪

201290.main: I made a promise to Edinburgh: I must return to port now and then, no matter how far away I go~♪|Be it with my E-class sisters or strangers, I can make friends with anyone I have fun with, so don't worry about me!|Echo is by your side, Commander! 201290.win_mvp: Wowee~♪ Echo got MVP? Ehehe~ So, you're basically praising me?

201290.mail: Mail has arrived~♪ Maybe there are yummy snacks enclosed within it~ Ehehe~

102052.login: Commander, the party is about to start.

I have so many things I want to tell you.

301560.detail: C-Commander, I haven't, um... disappointed you... have I?
301560.feeling1: I knew I probably wouldn't be of any use to you...
301560.upgrade: Commander, whenever I think about failing to meet your expectations... it almost makes me start crying... *Sob*...
301560.battle: A real battle... I'll give it my all...!
301560.home: Commander... you're not hurt, are you...?
301560.login: Commander, I've sorted all your documents... You wanted your documents sorted... right?
301560.mission_complete: Commander, I brought the mission rewards. I didn't make another mistake, did I...?
301560.feeling3: I'm trying my best not to cause trouble for people, but I don't know how... So instead I ended up making a lot of mistakes...
301560.unlock: I'm {namecode:125}, the fifth ship of the {namecode:26}-class. I-I sincerely hope I can be of servish to... *Whimper*... I've made another mistake... Even though I practiced on it so much...
301560.feeling2: Commander, is there something you wish me to do? I-is it possible I might have caused you trouble without realizing it?
301560.touch: Commander? I'm worrying if I did something wrong today... I-I don't think... I have...

301560.profile: I'm {namecode:125}, I'm the fifth ship of the {namecode:26}-class, I was constructed as part of the Circle Four Plan. But... I might be the least useful ship ever constructed... *Sob*...

I-I hope this will work...

101350.profile: Ahah! I'm the numero uno coolest Fletcher-class destroyer, Bache! My fire support in the Surigao Strait was no big deal! Also, no other destroyer has experienced the glory of resting beside the Colossus of Rhodes as much as I have! Hahahahah!
101350.main: It's windy as all hell today... and when it gets too windy, bad things happen. You get me, Commander?|This outfit is what's in vogue! Do you seriously not know fashion when you see it?|If the other Fletchers were as flashy as me then maybe I could actually remember their names!
101350.win_mvp: So weeeak! What a buncha losers! Hahahaha!
101350.feeling5: Y'know, your fashion sense has really improved; you don't look so lame anymore! Keep it up and I might fall for you~ Pfft, yeah right☆
101350.lose: I'll be back to smack the crap outta you dolts, just you waaaaaait!
101350.hp_warning: Not bad! But I'm badder and stronger than you! Hahaha!
101350.expedition: Commander, someone's back! Remember how it's part of the job to greet the commission team? Yeah, don't forget it!
101350.mail: Heh heh! You've got mail! Since you're such a busy bee and I'm so considerate, I'll read it out for ya!
101350.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bache, Hull Number DD-470.
101350.mission: If you can't finish your missions then magnanimous me's gonna have to step up to the plate!

301054.detail: This outfit feels light and easy to move in, not bad at all... Very cute? Um... thank you...
301054.login: Commander, the girls from the Dragon Empery seem to be having a banquet... Want to come with me to have a look?
301054.unlock: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?
301054.touch: Commander, this dress is made with really comfortable materials... Want to feel...?
301054.touch2: Commander, you can't... lift that part...
301054.main: This year's zodiac animal is... Eh? Commander, did you see where the piglet ran off to? |Commander, are we under attack? I hear a lot of explosions... Eh? So those are a form of celebration? That sounds interesting, yes... |What is this "ding-a-ling" sound? It reminds me... of our New Year back home...
301054.feeling5: I wish you a happy and peaceful holiday~ Commander, I hope that we can continue being together like this forever...
301054.drop_descrip: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?

301310.feeling4: Lately when I'm alone, I've been asking myself "is the commander taking care of himself?," "is he eating enough?," "does he think about me?"... Ahh, never mind that last one!
301310.propose: You're saying you want to take a lifelong vow with me? Eheheh, sure~ Then I, Matsukaze, swear to always, always look after you!
301310.detail: I wonder how my sisters are doing... I'm worried about them...
301310.feeling1: Sigh... Where did I go wrong with you...
301310.upgrade: Thanks! You could have saved caring about me for later, though.
301310.battle: Don't do anything too dangerous, okay?
301310.home: You must be tired after that last battle... Don't overexert yourself, come here and lie down.
301310.login: You can't fight on an empty stomach, Commander! I made lots and lots of food, so eat to your heart's content!
301310.mission_complete: You've done great, Commander. Bravo, bravo!
301310.feeling3: Yeah... I'm pretty bad with electronics... You should teach me how to properly use them, Commander!
301310.unlock: This is the fleet everyone's in, right? Seems pretty rowdy~ I'm Matsukaze! Nice meeting you!
301310.feeling2: If you don't have anything to do, you should tidy things up. Organization is fundamental to leading a good life.
301310.touch: Yeah? Are you feeling tired? Then wait just a moment, I've finished making some snacks!
301310.touch2: Eek?! ...Commander, sit right over there! You need to be scolded!
301310.profile: I'm the Kamikaze-class destroyer Matsukaze! I was in Destroyer Division 5 along with my sisters. We're a little outdated compared to something like the Mutsuki-class, but we won't let any newer classes beat us when it comes to combat or escorts! ...Sigh... I wonder how Asakaze's team will fare without me...
301310.main: This thing I've got? It's what's known as a ladle. Yeah, if it was a little smaller you could even serve tea with it.|This place is lacking in greenery... We should put some potted plants in here, Commander~!|Ahhh, the smell of laundry hung out to dry in the sun~ Isn't it great?
301310.win_mvp: Heheh, you'll have a really bad time if you underestimate a veteran!
301310.feeling5: You just need to focus on your goals and I'll handle all the minor details. I'm happy to help you with anything, not just combat or missions~!
301310.lose: Ugh... I'll be fine, just make a break for it, everyone...
301310.expedition: The commission team is back, Commander. It's not nice to keep them waiting!
301310.mail: Letter for you, Commander! Want me to read it out loud?
301310.skill: Don't you dare try to hurt my commander!
301310.mission: Are you doing your duty properly, Commander? I'm here if you need me.

301055.drop_descrip: “Welcome, Commander...” I should greet customers like this... yes?

299010.feeling4: Having that said, I believe that a truly intelligent person knows how to rely on others when appropriate. Ah, that's right~ Commander, would you feed me some cake?
299010.propose: "You are my world?" Did you think you could fool me with such flattery? Ehehe... well, I suppose there's a chance that I would let you fool me~ But first, you would have to repeat it ten times, nay, a hundred times~
299010.detail: Want to know about this? It's called a trident. Don't you think it's cool?
299010.feeling1: Commander, did you know how high my expectations were for you at first? What a shame, for you shall now never know.
299010.battle: So this is a battlefield? Ahaha... how interesting.
299010.home: You've done well to return home safe and sound.
299010.login: That simply will not do, Commander, keeping me waiting all this time~
299010.mission_complete: Commander, what do you hope to gain through not collecting the mission rewards? Perchance you are waiting for me to remind you?
299010.feeling3: The correct answer is - to do everything in your power to prevent that situation from occurring in the first place. Heehee~ Commander, if you wish to woo me, you will have to use your brain more~
299010.unlock: Who am I? I am the Royal Navy's large light cruiser, Neptune. I shall see to it that you will never forget my name~♪ Yes, pleased to be of service~♪
299010.feeling2: Commander, I have a question. If in the future you were given the option to sacrifice me for world peace, what would you choose?
299010.touch: You would like to challenge me to a game? Very well. Do not expect me to hold back though, hehe~♪
299010.touch2: That simply will not do, Commander. You cannot seek to gain my attention that way.
299010.profile: My background? Ehehe, I am the large light cruiser who only existed on paper, Neptune, so it is understandable that you have never heard of me before. Though I have yet to step onto the battlefield, my abilities are top notch... allow me to prove that to you in live combat~
299010.main: Unlike the other girls, this is my "maiden voyage" onto the battlefield. I wish to confirm for myself what this oft-touted "difference in experience" looks like. |Commander, if you get on your knees and beg, "Please, Mistress Neptune," perhaps there would be a chance for something nice to happen? |Commander, if you wish to taste my freshly-baked cake, then please first brew your finest tea~
299010.win_mvp: Ehehe~ As a special service, I shall allow you to praise me more~♪
299010.feeling5: Commander, have you planned where we're going to go for our date? If you have picked out an outfit for me, why don't you help me put it on? Eh~? "Why don't I wear it myself?" Silly, that's what love is all about~ L.O.V.E~♡
299010.lose: I shall not repeat this mistake again.
299010.hp_warning: I seem to have underestimated the battlefield...
299010.expedition: Commander, I shall temporarily grant you permission to leave my side so that you may greet the girls who have returned from commissions.
299010.mail: Commander, there's mail for you. Hmm? I didn't do anything in particular~
299010.skill: I have no intention of getting friendly with the enemy~
299010.mission: Commander, I see you have allowed your unfinished missions to pile up. I am not very fond of lazy people, you know?

201039.detail: Commander, don't you also think that these clothes are way cuter?
201039.home: Good work out there, Commander! What culinary creation did Ardent come up with today? You'll find out soon enough!
201039.login: Commander, did you miss my cooking? Hold on just a second~ it's coming right up!
201039.unlock: New outfit, new rigging, same ardent spirit! Ahaha, I'm serious~! Commander, thanks a lot~!
201039.touch: Commander, just being around you has taught me a lot about how the fleet works. That's right~ you can just sit back and leave it to me~!
201039.main: Commander, I've found some hot date spots, wanna come with me some time?|Commander, what kind of lunch would you like me to pack you for tomorrow?|Hey, Commander, don't you think Acasta would be super cute if she got dolled up a bit?
201039.drop_descrip: New outfit, new rigging, same ardent spirit! Ahaha, I'm serious~! Commander, thanks a lot~!
201039.mission: I've finished organising the new missions. Don't forget to check them~!

101351.detail: When it comes to bikes... I don't know squat! So I just got my Royal Navy pal to help out! I've gotta thank her later!
101351.home: Speed-star, engine at full throttle! Let's roll! ... Teehee~ I came up with that sweet catchphrase long ago!
101351.login: Hmm? Hmmmmmm? Man, you look miserable, Commander! Sit here and I'll take you on a wild ride! Ahahahaha!
101351.unlock: Ahaha~! Are you seeing this, Commander? This sturdiness, this gorgeous paint job, and these special accessories hand-picked by yours truly! Muahaha! I am the true speed-star of this port!
101351.touch: Aha! You're digging my bike and style, aren't you, Commander? Aren't you jelly? Since I'm so nice, I'll let you stare until you're satisfied!
101351.touch2: Seizing the chance to feel me up, huh~? You dirty perv~
101351.main: Still looking brand new? Well yeah, thanks to my daily pro-level maintenance!|You wanna ride my bike? Of course you... can't! Think what'd happen if you crash it!|If there's somewhere you wanna go, if you ask me really nicely with a cherry on top, I just might let you hop on~
101351.drop_descrip: Ahaha~! Are you seeing this, Commander? This sturdiness, this gorgeous paint job, and these special accessories hand-picked by yours truly! Muahaha! I am the true speed-star of this port!

399010.feeling4: After spending a lot of time with everyone else, I've experienced firsthand how difficult it can be to express my emotions clearly... such as joy... and love...
399010.propose: I never knew that having my feelings be reciprocated could be so overwhelmingly joyful... Milord, p-please don't look at me... I'm so happy that... my face must look strange...
399010.detail: Milord, w-welcome... I wasn't able to prepare much for your arrival... but would you like some tea?
399010.feeling1: Had I known I would have to serve a person like you, I never would have manifested during this era...
399010.upgrade: Is this... the sensation of getting stronger? Thank you!
399010.battle: The battlefield is callous... Ibuki, advancing!
399010.home: Milord, if you are ever injured, please allow Ibuki to treat you with this mugwort liniment. There's still a lot left.
399010.mission_complete: Milord, there's a big pile of stuff over there... Um, are those the rewards then?
399010.feeling3: I'm cool, you say...? If anything, I am somewhat jealous of how everyone can always have a smile on their faces... In contrast, I simply do not know how to express my emotions...
399010.unlock: Was it your voice that beckoned me from my timeless slumber? This lowly Ibuki, though still in training, shall be yours to use as you see fit.
399010.feeling2: I would also enjoy a life of sitting atop the mountains, watching the clouds pass through the sky. But my current life here isn't so bad either.
399010.touch: You'd like me to put on a show? S-Sorry... in front of other people... I can't...
399010.touch2: Clear the mind, and purify the six roots... Eek! Mi, Milord...
399010.profile: Milord, are you interested in me...? Mm... this Ibuki, who was never born, and has no history or accomplishments to speak of... Um, my hobby is poetry, and I'm skilled in swordsmanship! Are you satisfied with that? Um, also, I'm not very good around people...
399010.main: Spending time alone with Milord... somehow... makes my heart pound... |Milord, if you have no further orders for me, may I go over there to meditate? |In order to hone my swordsmanship, I practice my strokes a thousand times every day... Don't worry, Milord, I already finished while you were gone.
399010.win_mvp: My skills are but party tricks, unworthy of such praise.
399010.feeling5: The mugwort on Mount Ibuki is said to symbolize love that burns quietly... F-For example, right now, Milord... can you feel Ibuki's heart?
399010.lose: Ugh... I must increase my training multifold.
399010.hp_warning: A fight with our backs to the wall? ... Exactly what I wanted!
399010.expedition: Milord, the comm... Um, whatever these are called. Yes, they're done now.
399010.mail: Milord, your mail... Huh? You'd like me to read it? B-but that's embarrassing...
399010.skill: The pinnacle of Ibuki... resides in this single strike!
399010.mission: We seem to have new missions. Would you like Ibuki to accompany you?

301058.detail: Now, I know that I'm not alone anymore... because you're here after all, Commander...
301058.home: Commander... shall I rub your shoulders?
301058.login: No matter where you go, Ayanami shall always walk three steps behind you. Commander... shall we go?
301058.unlock: I'm still... your Ayanami... though I'm not very used to this outfit... Commander, does it suit me?
301058.touch: Commander, I like cuddling with you like this... It feels nice.
301058.touch2: This feels... a bit weird after all... But, if you like it, I don't mind...
301058.main: I'm not sure... I understand the meaning of these clothes... but since you'd like me to wear them, I don't mind... |Everyone was staring at me so excitedly... I'm not used to this... |
301058.win_mvp: Commander, as long as you're by my side, I won't lose.
301058.feeling5: I enjoy being with everyone, but... I'd also like to spend more time alone with you, Commander...
301058.drop_descrip: I'm still... your Ayanami... though I'm not very used to this outfit... Commander, does it suit me?

207050.feeling4: Truthfully, even though I'm a Lady of the Royal Navy, I sometimes want to have a bit of fun too. A side of me that I can't normally show except to people close to me like Illustrious... Doesn't that make you want to get closer with me?
207050.propose: I, Formidable, hereby dedicate my life to the love of my Commander, through good times and bad, rich times and poor... This is quite long, so I'll omit the rest~ Now then, Commander, it's your turn. I know it's a long vow but you are not to skip a single word ♪
207050.detail: ?! ... Ah, I was just doing a bit of tidying up. Please, come right in.
couple_encourage: Illustrious, my dear sister, what would you say to a spot of tea after this?
Victorious, my dear sister, have I comported myself well today?
207050.feeling1: I'm afraid I've contracted a disease that gives me a dreadful headache when you're nearby. Would you mind going someplace else?
207050.battle: Ladies of the Royal Navy have many virtues, but mercy to enemies is not one of them!
207050.home: Hmm~♪ Hmm~♪ C-Commander! I am p-pleased that you have returned!
207050.mission_complete: Commander, please don't forget to review the list of mission rewards.
207050.feeling3: My big sisters Illustrious and Victorious, like so many other ships you've gathered here, vouch for what a great commander you are. Now come, let this cake be a symbol of our new friendship. Take a bite, won't you?
207050.unlock: Good day, Commander. I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. Pleased to make your acquaintance.
207050.feeling2: Commander, is there something required of me? If you have a moment, why not join me for a cup of tea?
207050.touch: I must admit, Tirpitz is quite the hard nut to crack.
207050.touch2: Commander, is this the appropriate way for one to behave?
207050.profile: I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. I operated in the Mediterranean for a time, crossing swords with a certain Veneto. Thereafter, I found myself all across the Seven Seas. While my service record is not particularly impressive, I feel I made a small contribution to the war effort.
207050.main: Commander, if you're not making any progress on your work, why not take a break? I've prepared tea and crumpets.|No harm in taking a rest while the Commander's dist– Heavens! Victorious! G-good day. Do you have some business with the Commander?|On the day of my launch, hmm... What a shame... though I didn't do it on purpose... Well! All water under the bridge now, isn't it?
207050.win_mvp: What a magnificent victory! Let us press the advantage.
207050.feeling5: Commander, good day to you ♪ Shall we share another cake today? The maids have prepared a dreadfully sweet treat for us! Hmm...? I decided to let my hair down a bit more for you, Commander. Hehehe, I wonder if you'll find me just as captivating a Formidable as I was before?
207050.lose: Why you miserab- Ahem! You are truly worthy adversaries, but next time victory will be mine!
207050.hp_warning: You are all to redouble your efforts!
207050.expedition: Commander, the commission is complete. Shall we go to the harbour and greet the team?
207050.mail: Commander, I'm leaving the mail right here. Please don't forget to review it.
207050.mission: Commander, please don't forget to review the mission list I prepared for you.

301570.feeling4: Y-You'd like to watch my kagura dance? B-but, I still have a lot of practicing to do... Fusou said that rehearsals are just as important as practice...? I see! I... I'll do my best!
301570.propose: O gods, thank you very much for allowing me to meet Commander. I truly am blessed right now! So, um, Commander... though I'm still inexperienced, please take care of me!
301570.detail: Hyaa! C-Commander, when did you get here?
301570.feeling1: Commander, I wonder if you've been cursed...
301570.upgrade: C-Can I truly become stronger like this?
301570.battle: My s-skirt is gonna get blown away!
301570.home: Commander, you're safe! Thank goodness... my prayers were heard...
301570.feeling3: Aww.... m-my hair's all messed... Fusou's not here either, what should I do... Hm? You'd help me comb my hair? Thank you very much, Commander!
301570.unlock: I was guided here by the gods... Ah! M-My name is Harutsuki! Pleased to meet you!
301570.feeling2: Back then, my sisters and I were all scattered to the winds... But, we are finally reunited again. It's a miracle...
301570.touch: Commander? Would you like to try the sakura mochi that I made?
301570.profile: I am the ninth ship of the Akizuki-class destroyers, Harutsuki. Due to various circumstances, I wasn't able to do much, but... I'll make up for it this time, Commander!
301570.main: O gods, please bless this port so that everyone may come home safely. |Yoizuki may seem cold, but she's very nice and is always thinking of everyone else! |Good luck! I'll... be supporting you!
301570.win_mvp: Surely this must have been the gods' blessings.
301570.feeling5: C-Commander, please accept this! This is a protective good luck charm! "Marriage tie?" What do you mean...? C-Commander... you're a big bully...
301570.hp_warning: O gods, please give me guidance...!
301570.expedition: Commander! E-Everyone has come home safely!
301570.skill: O gods, please watch over us!
301570.mission: C-Commander, umm... there are still missions left...

399011.detail: I'll have to thank Houshou for this lovely kimono...
399011.home: The snow is coming down outside... Milord, let me get an extra sweater for you.
399011.login: Milord, shall we go outside together?
399011.unlock: Milord, it's starting to snow... If it suits you, please take shelter under Ibuki's umbrella.
399011.touch: Is there someplace you'd like to go, Milord? Of course I'll accompany you.
399011.touch2: Um, Milord, your hands are cold...
399011.main: Achoo! ...I'm cute when I sneeze? D- don't make fun of me...|This is... real snow... beautiful...|Aren't there some big festivals in the wintertime? I guess you could say... I'm a little interested... only a little!
399011.feeling5: The winter in my timeless slumber was silent and cold. But here, at Milord's side, I feel only warmth... Milord, would you... take my hand?
399011.drop_descrip: Milord, it's starting to snow... If it suits you, please take shelter under Ibuki's umbrella.

301059.battle: It will be all right, Commander... Believe in me...
301059.unlock: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be pampered a bit...
301059.main: Commander, I feel like I can work a bit harder when I'm with you...|Being with everyone makes me happy... so I want to be able to stay together...|Commander, if you leave me alone... I'll be hurt...
301059.win_mvp: If it is for everyone's sake... I am willing to become the "Demon."
301059.drop_descrip: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be spoiled a bit...

499010.feeling4: Ahhh... The feeling of tearing apart enemies with gunfire... and breaking them into a million little pieces... I can't get enough of it... You know how I feel, don't you, Commander?
499010.propose: Thank you so much. But listen, I finally understand now. What filled the void in my heart wasn't slaughter on the battlefield or love, it was the hatred known as "envy"... Commander, I love you just as much as I deeply, deeply, DEEPLY hate those other girls... THEY WILL PAY!
499010.detail: Commander, do you have any interests outside of work? If you're okay with it, why don't we relax together?
499010.battle: *Giggle*... You saw me, and now you're trying to flee...? Do you really think you can flee from ME?!
499010.home: I want to pummel some enemies, too~ *Giggle*... The more of them you sink, the more you prove your worth, after all~
499010.login: This place is so peaceful. Everyone's so nice, too...
499010.mission_complete: Let's give our all on the next mission, too.
499010.feeling3: It is our destiny to kill one another on the battlefield... So, wouldn't you say it's normal to revel in the killing just a little bit?
499010.unlock: I never thought I'd end up here... Hello, I am Roon. I don't know this place very well, so could I ask you to give me a tour?
499010.feeling2: How I'm faring at the base? Perfectly fine. Although... isn't it a little too peaceful here...?
499010.touch: Please open your mouth, Commander... *Giggle*, do you like it? Have I gotten better at cooking?
499010.touch2: Hm? Do you want a hug, too? Okay~
499010.profile: I am Roon, the Iron Blood cruiser. In a far-off world, I never existed beyond the drawing board... But that aside, I've seen it, Commander... Deep within your heart, there's something that resembles me...
499010.main: Every time I see something beautiful get squashed on the battlefield, I just... Aahhh...|I want to do something to soothe your mind. But... what should I do...|What my hobby is? Perhaps something like "granting sweet release"?
499010.win_mvp: Not only did you not sink yourselves upon seeing me, you even forced me to sink you myself... YOU WILL PAY!
499010.feeling5: *Giggle*, I get more fulfillment from being with you than from killing enemies on the battlefield... Is this the power of love? But then...
499010.lose: Aww... Did we fall prey to an ambush...?
499010.hp_warning: You dare hurt me...? YOU WILL PAY!
499010.expedition: Those commission girls must work really hard... Okay, everyone line up~ I'm going to give each of you a hug~
499010.mail: It's not any bad news, is it?
499010.mission: What might this next mission be? I'm getting a little excited.

106019.detail: Hmm? This outfit is more refreshing so, no issues!
106019.unlock: Commander~ I am Long Island~ I've changed? Ghosts don't cha... Huh? I seemed to have become a little more alive!
106019.touch: Lunch together? I need to finish assembling my plastic model, so, apologies, Commander!
106019.touch2: I am a ghost~! ...Still, it's not good to touch ghosts out of a whim!
106019.main: You know, Long Island the ghost has become boring... Now, I am Long Island the Jiangshi, jumping zombie!|Ehehe~ Commander, are you looking for your gaming handheld?|Com~man~der~! Huh? You really fell asleep? Hehehe~ What kind of pranks should I pull?
106019.drop_descrip: Commander~ I am Long Island~ I've changed? Ghosts don't cha... Huh? I seemed to have become a little more alive!

207051.detail: Are you done warming up, Commander? Right then, into the water with you♪
207051.home: I was simply waiting here for you. Don't think too much on it, Commander.
207051.unlock: A Lady of the Royal Navy exudes elegance even when wearing her swimsuit. Huh...? Y-you're not seeing it? Really... that's weird...
207051.touch: Huh? Illustrious?! Grr... You tricked me, Commander. Now you're in for it!
207051.touch2: Okay, I see how it is. The salty sea air has gotten you all frisky, Commander. Hehehe...
207051.main: Don't you find the atmosphere rather dreary...? What if we put on some rock... Er, something a little more stimulating?|Hmm, that would be Hood. Even in a swimsuit she's the picture of nobility. Of course, that's nothing I'm not incapable of...|Don't fret, Warspite. I wouldn't be able to swim without the Commander's help either!
207051.drop_descrip: A Lady of the Royal Navy exudes elegance even when wearing her swimsuit. Huh...? Y-you're not seeing it? Really... that's weird...

499011.drop_descrip: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...

101160.feeling4: Commander, you keep telling me I'm stupid, but you actually like me, don't you?
101160.propose: Hehe, so you've finally noticed how important I am? Have you? Do you understand that I'm irreplaceable and that just a glance of me makes your heart skip a beat? ... Commander, why are you touching my forehead?
101160.detail: Stop touching my ears! I told you already, they're real! I-I'll bite you!
101160.feeling1: Oh evil being who conspires against cuties... in the name of the moon, I will punish you!
101160.upgrade: My cuteness level has gone up even higher!
101160.battle: It won't be as simple as going back to the title screen if we get a game over~
101160.home: Were you thinking about how badly you wanted to come back and meet me~? Come here, I'll give a positively explosive hug! ... Hm? Fine... I'm sorry, I'll put away the dynamite... J-just hold on a minute~
101160.login: Let's hear your excuse for making the strongest and cutest cutie in the world wait for so long, Commander!
101160.mission_complete: Come on, come on! Give me a reward!
101160.feeling3: I am cuteness, and cuteness is me. Don't you agree, Commander? Yay!
101160.unlock: Yahoo! Commander! Aren't you charmed by how cute and risqué I am? Huh? W-who am I? ... Hahaha... My name is Benson... It's a pleasure to meet you...
101160.feeling2: Ahah! What's that tasty-looking snack you've got there?
101160.touch: Whoa! I actually fell asleep! Could this be because of that fabled super hypnosis thing?!
101160.touch2: Ah, I feel so hot... I'm burning inside!
101160.profile: Here comes Benson! I'm way cooler than Anderson. I'm a capital destroyer, and can move at speeds up to 35 knots! My anti-air defenses are just as impressive. I can't wait for you to see me in battle!
101160.main: I'm so cute! The cutest in the universe!|I'm telling you, Commander, Fletcher's house next door is full of people! Us girls need to help her out every now and then~.|If you don't talk to me enough then I'll stop being a bunny! Woof woof!
101160.win_mvp: Hoho! Even the most cunning fox couldn't best a rabbit like me!
101160.feeling5: Commander! Cutie Benson has come again! I've been stopping by too often lately? That's because you haven't been paying this super duper cutie Benson a visit, so you left me no choice~ I'm not lonely at all, I swear!
101160.lose: Oh nooo! You didn't see anything, Commander! Got it?! *Sob*... I failed...
101160.expedition: Commander, the commission's been completed! I'm going to have to punish you if you forget about those girls!
101160.mail: Mail for you, Commander! I didn't want to anyone else to peek, so I went ahead and took a look myself first!
101160.drop_descrip: Benson-class Destroyer - Benson, Hull Number DD-421!
101160.mission: A mission? No problem! Easy peasy! Bring it on, whatever it may be!

301319.detail: I doubt this fan will be of any use when it gets cold...
301319.login: Welcome back, Commander! How are you? Hungry? Then have a seat, I'll go get you something to eat!
301319.unlock: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~
301319.touch: Hm? Are you hungry? Or do you want me to fan you?
301319.main: I think this thing will be handy for drying clothes or futons out in the sun! Mhm, I think I'll test it right now!|Commander, look! There's a big "matsu" written on my fan! Mhm, I have to say I'm quite fond of it~!|Umm... have you heard about "work-life balance"? It's bad to rest too much, but it's not good to work too much either.
301319.drop_descrip: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~

106020.feeling4: Commander! I, Bogue, am requesting special training! The reason is, whenever I hear your voice, I lose my strength so I want to know how to prevent that... That's all!
106020.propose: ...Now I understand! You noticed my feelings, Commander, and you want me to continue my journey without regrets! I, Bogue, am truly happy to have met you!
106020.detail: Please keep my stats in mind!
106020.feeling1: Can you really make me stronger, Commander? ...I'm really worried...
106020.upgrade: My balls have become even faster!
106020.home: Commander, you are a real veteran! That was a learning experience!
106020.login: The best pitchers are always training. Yep!
106020.mission_complete: It's satisfying to be rewarded for achieving the objective! Commander, check out the rewards!
106020.feeling3: You always give me the right ideas, Commander! As expected of a great coach! I, Bogue the pitcher, will follow you for life!
106020.unlock: *inhale*...HAA! Nice one... Oh, apologies. You're the Commander, I see. Fast pitcher, Bogue, here for duty!
106020.feeling2: Someday, I hope to stand on the podium of the sea with your lead!
106020.touch: What's this? Training to resist against attacks?
106020.profile: I am pro baseballer, Bogue! Yep, my greatest record is 12 strikeouts in a single match! I wish to sharpen my skills by your side, and become the shining star of the Major League!
106020.main: With this ball, I can sink a submarine!|Commander, can you polish the B-25s?|Boring... You look tired anyway, Commander, so let's go and sink some subs?
106020.win_mvp: Hmhmm~ As I thought, I am the best pitcher.
106020.feeling5: Co-Commander. If I win in the next league, I- I'll tell you something important! S- So please wait for it! I will become stronger. Stronger than anyone!
106020.lose: Is this the end of the tournament...?
106020.expedition: Curveball~! Oh crap I broke the window... Ah, Commander, the commission squad is back!
106020.mail: Commander, it's a mail! Which championship is it from?
106020.drop_descrip: Bogue-class escort carrier — Bogue, Hull Number CVE-9!
106020.mission: A new goal? I will not back down!

303110.feeling4: Recently, I haven't been able to keep my composure during training.. Just from thinking about you, my form becomes sloppy. If I am like this, would you still want to keep me by your side?
303110.propose: For you to acknowledge me like this, Commander, is the greatest honor. From now on, this blade shall serve only you. Please continue to treat me kindly.
303110.detail: Small strokes fell great oaks, constant drops pierce through rock. Those who train through the most humdrum of days shall seize victory in the most critical of moments. That is my belief.
303110.feeling1: A sword has no eyes. It would be wise to avoid approaching me casually.
303110.battle: Please leave combat to me. I shall not shame my title of being "The Strongest!"
303110.home: I'm glad that you came back safe and sound.
303110.login: {namecode:66} standing by. What are your orders?
303110.mission_complete: Mission accomplished! Are we going to collect the rewards?
303110.feeling3: It might be pretty nice to just set aside my duties and have a relaxing conversation with you every once in a while, Commander.
303110.unlock: Are you the Commander? Please allow this lowly {namecode:66} to offer you what little strength she has.
303110.feeling2: Do you need anything? If not, I'm going back to work.
303110.touch: E-enemies?! Oh... It was you, Commander? Apologies - my eyesight isn't the best.
303110.touch2: Kyaa! You scared me... how shameless!
303110.profile: I am {namecode:66}, first ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers. I may not look like it, but I have already crossed through countless battlefields. Please place your faith in my firepower and armor, and be at ease.
303110.main: Even back in port, we must not lower our guard. Danger lurks around every corner.|Commander, not even you could withstand my blade.|Daily refinement means to continually strive towards your goals. Commander, may your focus never falter.
303110.win_mvp: Hm... Once again, I've cut a worthless object.
303110.feeling5: No matter how badly I'm injured, I will make sure to always return to your side. So... Commander, could you always stay with me as well?
303110.lose: I was careless... I definitely will not fail next time!
303110.expedition: Your fleet has returned from commission. Want to welcome them back?
303110.mail: Commander, there's new mail. Shall I bring it for you?
303110.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:66}.
303110.mission: New tasks have been assigned - would you like to confirm them?

100010.feeling4: Whee~! I'm flying! So~ high! Hey, don't move! You'll have to catch me if I fall!
100010.propose: As a simple Bulin, I'm meant to just help strengthen your other ships... But you gave me this ring... You're a strange one! I like you! Come, let's raise our hands together and say purin~ purin~!
100010.detail: Staring at me all day won't turn you into an expert!
100010.feeling1: You're pretty amazing to have gotten on my bad side! But I won't get angry just to appease you! Haha! Enjoy your emptiness!
100010.battle: Purin~! Don't stop until they kneel and cry!
100010.home: Let's run around and relax! Purin~!
100010.login: Righty tighty, Lefty loosey, Stay calm and Purin on!
100010.mission_complete: I'm just heading out to fetch your rewards, purin! I promise I won't break them!
100010.feeling3: I'll let you in on a little secret. My little sister keeps telling people that she's smarter than me. But truth is, she's dumber! I try to be nice and let her feel good about herself, like a big sister should. Ha!
100010.unlock: Purin~! The herald of good fortune has arrived! Are you ready? Raise your hands and follow me... Purin~ purin~!
100010.feeling2: My sister is so dumb. When people talk about our colors, it's not about our hair, it's about ra... rari... ah, now I remember! Reality TV!
100010.touch2: Purin~ purin~! (Prototype Bulin MKII continues to spin faster)
100010.profile: Hahaha! It's your lucky day now that you've met me! We can purin together from this day forward! What for? To make everyone stronger, obviously! How do you purin? Like this! Purin~! Purin~!
100010.main: Purin~! It's so big in here! There's so much room to run around!|Oh right, it's not my job to just run around, is it? Purin~!|Purin~? I'm too loud? Hmph, who cares what you think!
100010.feeling5: You're not an average commander if you managed to conquer my heart. But I won't be shy or blush! Instead I'll give you a growl! Graaaah!
100010.lose: So why am I on the battlefield anyway, purin?!
100010.expedition: Yaaaay~! Commander! The girls who went out on a commission have come back! Let's drill something to celebrate!
100010.drop_descrip: Prototype Bulin MKII. Can be used to limit break all Super Rare ships.
100010.skill: My drill is the drill that will pierce the heavens!
100010.mission: Purin~! The next mission has been chosen for you!

102120.feeling4: I don't really have anything going for me outside of my body, but you're still being so nice to me... Do you like my body THAT much? Even if you don't, it's not like I... No, I'll stop myself right there, because otherwise you'll just get carried away.
102120.propose: This is really embarrassing, so could we just get this over with... Y-you can do whatever you want when it's just the two of us...
102120.detail: Maintenance? Fine, as long as you don't do anything weird...
102120.feeling1: So that's who you are, huh, Commander?
102120.upgrade: I didn't really ask you for this...
102120.battle: All I need to do is get rid of these guys, right?
102120.home: Good work. What, are you not satisfied until I say something mean?
102120.login: Why do I have to wait for you here...
102120.mission_complete: What, you don't even want your rewards?
102120.feeling3: I think people are jealous of me because mine are bigger than theirs… But personally I wish they were smaller. When they're big, you know, it's pretty inconvenient...
102120.unlock: Brooklyn-class, Honolulu, reporting in. Hey, listen... could you stop staring at me like that? It's not like they're this big because I wanted them to be...
102120.feeling2: Do I really need to chat with you...? But I guess I don't have anything else to do, so I'll keep you company for a while.
102120.touch: Do you just go around touching everyone you see? Do you need anything?
102120.touch2: *Sigh*... If you're gonna be this direct then I don't even feel like getting mad at you...
102120.profile: I'm Honolulu of the Brooklyn-class. I've basically only ever served in the Pacific. I was damaged pretty bad once, but somehow I managed to make it... At least I was luckier than Helena...
102120.main: I don't seem very Hawaiian even though my name is Honolulu? Well gee, my bad...|Helena's always acting so gloomy... You should think of ways to make her smile too, Commander.|I was born with this personality. I don't hate you or anything like that...
102120.feeling5: ... Didn't I tell you they're not this big just because I wanted them to be? Well, if you like them that much... then maybe they're not so bad...
102120.lose: I don't want to go to Mare Island again...
102120.expedition: What are you waiting for... A commission's been completed!
102120.mail: Here, mail for you. What? I can at least do something this simple for you...
102120.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Honolulu, Hull Number CL-48!
102120.skill: This time things should go well...!
102120.mission: If you have the time to stare at me, how about you go finish your remaining missions?

301321.unlock: Commander, Merry Christmas~! I am on my best behavior today as well! Uuu... when is Santa Claus going to come? I'm sleepy...
301321.main: Santa... Claus...? Ah! I know this person!
301321.drop_descrip: Commander, Merry Christmas~! I am on my best behavior today as well! Uuu... when is Santa Claus going to come? I'm sleepy...

303112.detail: I may have lost to Miss Saratoga in sandcastle building, but I shall redeem myself in beach volleyball.
303112.home: Good work, Commander. ...What? Miss Saratoga is going to join Team Royal during the beach volleyball tournament? I see... a chance for payback has come!
303112.login: Of course I can sympathize with the others. In this kind of heat, it is important to get some rest. However, we mustn’t neglect our training!
303112.unlock: Commander, even I’ll get embarrassed if you keep staring at me like that... Eh? Why did I bring a volleyball? Did you not order me to bring it?
303112.touch: The younger girls are all so energetic... Commander, did you know you can tell their age by when they were launched?
303112.touch2: Don’t touch me! I’m working on a sand castle... it has to be at least 70% bigger than Sara’s!
303112.main: Miss Saratoga wants to challenge me? Fine. Swimming, volleyball... just name it. I’ll take her on.|Atago, did you bring my sunglasses?|Relax, Commander. I didn’t bring this kendo sword to hit you with. It’s because I heard that someone from the Royal Navy is going to be here. Heh, just kidding. It’s because Atago is scared of ghosts~
303112.drop_descrip: Commander, even I’ll get embarrassed if you keep staring at me like that... Eh? Why did I bring a volleyball? Did you not order me to bring it?

206031.unlock: I have... become a songstress~ ehehe... It would be nice if my song can reach Onii-chan...
206031.touch: Hehe... Onii-chan, do you want to listen to my song?
206031.main: Onii-chan, does a fancy dress like this look weird on me?|Ugean has grown up too *giggles*!|'Listen to my song!' Am I acting like a songstress? *giggles*|Sister Illustrious... do I seem more mature to you now...?
206031.drop_descrip: Unicorn... is now a songstress... *giggles* Unicorn's song has reached Onii-chan's heart.

203090.feeling4: *sigh*... What's more, when I went to bring this up with her, she just gave me a pat on the head and said, "Thanks, Sussex, but it'll be alright." So, nothing changed at all... Good grief, why do people have to be so difficult...?
203090.propose: At first, I was strict with you only because I wanted to ease the burden on my sister... but gradually, I began to hope that you would become the most distinguished person in my life... As of now, you've already become that person...
203090.detail: Shropshire can be quite a handful to deal with... But, I suppose since she's the type of person who won't ever let herself draw the short straw, you should just let her be.
couple_encourage: London, stay safe out there!
Shropshire, stay focused on the battlefield!
203090.feeling1: London is too much of a people-pleaser, and all her coddling seems to have turned you into mush.
203090.upgrade: Thank you. I'll continue to work hard on the next mission.
203090.battle: For the sake of not bringing shame upon the fleet, let us fight!
203090.home: There's a lot to report still, but for now, good work.
203090.login: Are you ready to begin working? Don't come running to me if you find out later that you're missing something.
203090.mission_complete: So these are the mission rewards! Commander, you're quite the capable one~
203090.feeling3: London is the type of person who would easily be deceived by a bad person, but still continue to smile despite knowing that... Jeez, just why does she have to have that kind of personality...
203090.unlock: So you're the Commander? Hmph! Let's make one thing clear: I'm not easygoing like my sister, London. I'll expect you to have your act together!
203090.feeling2: The way London always has that smile plastered on her face no matter who she's around just rubs me the wrong way.
203090.touch: Commander, your collar is messed up. And your hair too... Hold still, I'll fix it for you.
203090.touch2: Commander, sit right there! Good grief... I'll have to re-teach you some basic manners...!
203090.profile: Other than the coastal defence battle in the Mediterranean Sea and that one naval battle up north, I pretty much carried out all my missions normally... Well, there was that one time I needed serious repairs... b-but anyway! Since I'm here, I'll continue to put my best foot forward. Commander, I expect the same from you!
203090.main: Excessive kindness can become poison. One must be strict when the situation calls for it. |If you have time to gawk at me, you should get your work done first. After you finish, then you can, um... |... If you're tired, get some rest. I'm not saying this for your sake - it's simply better if you're ready to give it your all when the situation calls for it.
203090.win_mvp: Don't think that winning is the only thing that matters. There are still many things I could have done better.
203090.feeling5: At least I'll feel at ease leaving London in your care... No, you'll have to become even more distinguished, to the point that I won't be able to look away from you... huh? What did I just say...?
203090.lose: This was due to my failure as a leader. Don't blame yourselves, everyone.
203090.expedition: And that should be time... Commander, the commission team should be returning any moment now.
203090.mail: Please do not forget to check your mail.
203090.mission: Before acting, one must first consider the most efficient way of getting things done - you haven't forgotten, right?

302090.feeling4: Commander, should we go fishing today? Oh, there's work to do? I'll wait for you to finish then... Oh? No, it's fine! I'm more than happy to stay with you, Commander.
302090.propose: It's not for the other sisters in First torpedo squadron, but for me? Is that really alright? Ahh, this makes me happier than that one miraculous victory......thank you, Commander, I shall treat it as my most precious treasure.
302090.detail: Don't push yourself too much, Commander!
302090.upgrade: This isn't a bad feeling at all...
302090.home: Did everyone make it back in one piece?
302090.login: Welcome back. Want to try some fresh torpedoes?
302090.feeling3: I look trigger happy? I actually prefer being an escort more than I do engaging in combat...
302090.unlock: Hi, Commander... I'm {namecode:47}. What are you looking at? My horns? Don't mistake me for {namecode:44} or {namecode:45}...
302090.feeling2: What's wrong? If it's nothing then stay quiet, Commander.
302090.touch2: Want to have a taste of my torpedoes, Commander?
302090.profile: {namecode:46}-class light cruiser, {namecode:47}. I've spent most of my time in the First Torpedo Squadron. Although I look aggressive, I actually prefer other things like fishing and just cruising around... just like when I was at Kiska. Perhaps protecting others is a more suitable job for me.
302090.main: Commander, shall we go fishing? How about a game of chess?|My name seems a bit complicated, but it's actually easy to read. Why don't you try it?|Dress up? Oh... these socks are actually pretty easy to take off. Want to try yourself?
302090.win_mvp: I'm number one? Hm... I don't feel anything special...
302090.feeling5: I'm just a normal {namecode:47}... no one has ever cursed me to become a demon. If someone tries to hurt you though, Commander, I might just turn right into a demon!
302090.lose: Everyone, prepare to retreat... I'll cover the rear!
302090.hp_warning: Don't panic... wait for the right moment to strike!
302090.expedition: Commander, shall we return to port and do some fishing? The girls seem to be back from their commission as well.
302090.drop_descrip: Sixth ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:47}.
302090.mission: We're starting a new mission. Got it?

399020.feeling4: Hey, you've started getting just a bit into shape recently... Hmph, I suppose I'll acknowledge you've worked hard.
399020.propose: You're making that miserable face again. I just can't leave you be, huh... Listen, today is the day I will acknowledge your hard work... or, should I say, your talent! I, battleship Izumo, swear on my blade to walk with you, both in life and death.
399020.detail: If you've got time to stare at me then maybe do your work instead.
399020.feeling1: You lack what it takes to order me to swing this blade.
399020.battle: All ships, form up! Target: enemies in front!
399020.home: Look who's back. Time's precious, so start reflecting on your last sortie immediately.
399020.login: Late, as always. Just how long will you keep me waiting?
399020.mission_complete: Mission complete... Good lord, would you ever have realized it on your own?
399020.feeling3: *Sigh*... Why do you always make that miserable face, Commander? It's so miserable that... it makes me want to scold you...
399020.unlock: Battleship Izumo, reporting in. Are you the Commander? Sure don't look very reliable... Listen here: do anything to slow me down, and you won't hear the end of it!
399020.feeling2: This blade is my other half. Casually touch it, and you'll get hurt.
399020.touch: Commander, you don't have the free time to endlessly chat with me.
399020.profile: I'm battleship Izumo, of the Sakura Empire. I existed as a proposed Yamato-class design, although they didn't construct me... But if you look down me even slightly then prepare to taste one of my main cannon volleys.
399020.main: A blade requires careful maintenance. Isn't that obvious?|Sisters... eh. The Izumo class consists of just me, so I guess I'm a bit jealous.|Become stronger, Commander. Once you become strong enough to protect everyone... Once that happens, I...
399020.feeling5: The path of my blade is one of constant solitude... or so I thought. Hmph, maybe being with you... isn't so bad after all.
399020.expedition: Commission complete. Why don't you go on one yourself, sometime?
399020.mail: Here's a letter. It's rude to the sender to not read their letter thoroughly. Don't you agree?
399020.skill: Feel the wrath of my blade!
399020.mission: What are you planning to do about these unfinished missions?

303114.detail: A balanced school life is a part of the responsibilites here. Surely, I will develop valuable and translatable skills through the process of going to school.
303114.battle: I'll show you why they call me the "School's Strongest!"
303114.login: Woah! C-Commander? When did you get here? I-I'm sorry, I'm still not ready yet...
303114.unlock: Hmm... school life, huh? It's a fairly fresh experience for me. Would it be fine to pin my hair up like this? What do you think, Commander?
303114.touch: This Woofy strap here? Atago gave it to me and said it'd help me look less uptight. Jeez, I'm not uptight at all...
303114.main: Commander, even if you're at school, you can't slack off too much! |What clubs am I interested in joining... I wonder if there's a kendo club... |This uniform was supposed to fit, so why is it so tight... C-Commander?! What are you staring at!?
303114.win_mvp: Phew... I suppose that's a good warm up.
303114.drop_descrip: Hmm... school life, huh? It's a fairly fresh experience for me. Would it be fine to pin my hair up like this? What do you think, Commander?

103080.feeling4: But, I'm totally over it. I've found something even more important than being a big sister... *sparkles* Commander, rely on me more and more, okay~
103080.propose: Commander, just being able to exert myself for your sake is enough to make me happy, but for you to reciprocate my feelings like this... This is truly the greatest treasure I could ask for. Thank you.
103080.detail: Heyyo~ Commander, you look awfully bored~
103080.feeling1: I'm getting a little pissed off... I know I said you can rely on me more, but...
103080.battle: I won't let you harm the people who are important to me!
103080.home: Commander, you made it back without a scratch on you! Well done, well done!
103080.login: Commander, you can totally rely on me more!
103080.mission_complete: Here, the rewards have arrived~ Commander, you're pretty awesome~
103080.feeling3: I get along with my sisters very well, and like them a whole lot... But sometimes, I just can't help thinking... what if we were called the Astoria-class instead...
103080.unlock: Yo, Commander! I'm Astoria, eldest sister of the New Orleans-class! If you're ever having any troubles, you can always come talk to me~
103080.feeling2: I'm not as nice as you take me for...
103080.touch2: Ah... wait... Jeez, Commander, you jerk!
103080.profile: Heyyo! I'm Astoria, the eldest sister of the New Orleans class! Why am I not the nameship? Um... it's kind of a long story, hehe... But that doesn't make me any less of a big sister. Commander, you can rely on me, that is if you want to~
103080.main: I'm not very smart, so I'll pass on the complicated stuff, but when it comes to life advice, I'm your gal! |New Orleans sure matured into a fine big sister. What a gal! |Commander, even though you're very knowledgeable, I'm sure there's some stuff that not even you know~
103080.win_mvp: Hehe, I'm pretty capable, aren't I~
103080.feeling5: Love is equal? ... Ehehe, you're always thinking about me, that makes me very happy~ However, here's what you don't understand: if you truly like someone, then these kinds of things don't matter at all.
103080.lose: Oh my, looks like we lost... Commander, let's get out of here~
103080.expedition: Commander! The girls have returned from their commission~ let's hurry up and welcome them back!
103080.mail: There's new mail~ Comander, you're quite the popular one~
103080.drop_descrip: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Astoria, hull number CA-34.
103080.skill: Even I can get serious when it's do or die!
103080.mission: Sitting for too long is no good. After you finish your work, why don't we go for a change in pace?

102121.detail: Y-you want to eat lunch together? Really? I bet you're just teasing me. Or are you... just hoping to get a taste of Helena's cooking?
102121.home: Don't say you'll "see me after school"... O-or else I'll just stay behind...
102121.unlock: If everyone's focusing on the teacher, they probably won't stare at me from up front... As for the umbrella, it's... I know it makes me stand out, but I don't want people to stare at me from behind either...
102121.touch: It's small, but it's the only umbrella I could find. S-so, when 2 people are sharing it... i-it's only natural they'd have to stand so close together...
102121.touch2: I-I don't have anything going for me besides my bust anyway...
102121.main: I made a friend at school. He's brown, cuddly, and doesn't say a word, though...|There's nobody who's like you at school. Nobody who sometimes makes me laugh, sometimes makes me cry, and sometimes... Gosh, what am I saying...|nil
102121.drop_descrip: If everyone's focusing on the teacher, they probably won't stare at me from up front... As for the umbrella, it's... I know it makes me stand out, but I don't want people to stare at me from behind either...

399021.detail: My name has connections to classical dancing...? I-I see...
399021.battle: I'll remind ya, in case ya forgot...! I'm the battleship Izumo!
399021.unlock: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!
399021.touch: ... Drunk? Me? I've only had a few... *Hick*
399021.touch2: Commander, are you insinuating you want a swift kick?
399021.main: Dancing and my sword are much alike. Untold hours of learning and practice are for a single moment of brilliance...|Commander, if I really captivate you so... will you be able to finish your work?|Savory delicacies and mature festivities... I say why not enjoy the New Year and let loose for once? Hahahah!
399021.win_mvp: How stunning; how gorgeous – to my eyes, the sight of this battlefield is worth ten thousand ryo.
399021.drop_descrip: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!

101290.feeling4: Have you ever tried making your own candy? It's fun! Here, try some of mine!
