207060.feeling5: Commander, if you are tired you can always rest in my embrace. Eh? Didn't you say yesterday that was the best way for you to recover?
207060.lose: Next time, I'll scout out the enemy before we attack!
207060.expedition: Commander, after your commissions are complete, you should... uh... hm... collect your rewards!
207060.mail: I'll put the tea here... Mail? Ah, yes! There's new mail for you!
207060.drop_descrip: Courageous-class aircraft carrier – Glorious, Hull Number 77.
207060.skill: May victory and glory be ours... hopefully!
207060.mission: Rest up and then finish your missions in one go!

301590.feeling4: Actually, even though I don’t care that much and I have confidence in myself, for the sake of asking… do you think I’m independent enough?
301590.propose: Commander, you’ve finally realized my greatness. To be frank… my ears are not twitching. I’m not that happy, shut up, let’s continue the ceremony!
301590.detail: O you mean this family emblem? I designed this myself, plus the clothes. I won’t accept any other comments except for “its cute”.
couple_encourage: 17th Destroyer fleet ready to take out the enemy!!
301590.feeling1: Stay away from me, stupidity is contagious.
301590.upgrade: Thank you… my ears are twitching? Impossible, I’m not that happy at all.
301590.home: You’ve worked hard today, please get some rest.
301590.login: So slow, are you like a turtle who’s stumbled onto the battlefield?
301590.mission_complete: The mission rewards have been confirmed, I’ll leave the labor work of transporting it here to you.
301590.feeling3: {namecode:128} and {namecode:127} are both so whimsical and wandering around. Those girls sure don’t have the temperment of being in the Navy. They still need to lean on me, being their big sister. Such a headache...
301590.unlock: So it turns out to be you, are you the Commander of the 17th Destroyer fleet from today onwards? You seem so ordinary. I am {namecode:19} class {namecode:142}, show me what you got, Commander.
301590.feeling2: My fan? Its military issue, not some ordinary fan. It’s used by Admirals, so don’t underestimate me… hehehe. Hmm? I said nothing.
301590.touch: Don’t poke me unstoppingly, are you a monkey?
301590.touch2: This type of things should not be tolerated, right? In that case, die...
301590.profile: The 17th Destroyer fleet have been together for most of the time, and we participated in all sorts of sorties and operations for almost the entirety of the war. In the end I was with {namecode:70}-sama as we both made our last stand… to the end. So I don’t care about those little things.
301590.main: That {namecode:128} girl, as my little sister she always acts superior to {namecode:127}, even more than I do, darn… | If only we discovered Tusk, then {namecode:70}-sama would not… sigh, forget it, what’s important is the present |Official documents? Let me see… hmm… ahh I see I see...
301590.win_mvp: We won… naturally, what’s there to gloat about?
301590.feeling5: What, I just asked offhandedly, you sure are opinionated… forget it. I’ll still listen to what you got to say. Just you wait, one day I’ll impress you.
301590.lose: Damn, give me… victory. Win or lose, that’s the way of life in the Navy.
301590.expedition: The commission fleet has returned, did you forget?
301590.mail: You’ve got mail… hmm? You read it, I didn’t really focus on what was written, don’t mind me.
301590.mission: I’ve organized all the missions… say what, you want me to clear them as well?!

202201.detail: No matter what clothing I wear, I am still your maid and live only to fulfill your expectations, my honourable Master.
202201.home: There is no greater happiness than your safe return, Master. Would you like to gather everyone to have tea?
202201.unlock: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.
202201.touch: Oh, my Master who has intoxicated me with passions so, it is an honour to have been chosen as your dance partner.
202201.main: Every single maid dreams of being able to stand beside her master in such a dress... Please forgive me for my presumptuousness... |This dress seems ill-suited for combat... but since it is your wish, Master, I shall humbly carry out your will. |This necklaces suits me well...? Thank you for praising this unworthy maid, my honourable Master.
202201.feeling5: Whether it's under the swirling lights of the ballroom stage, or in the smoke and explosions of the battlefield, there will never be anything more radiant than you in my eyes. My honourable Master, please allow me to gaze upon you and be at your side, always...
202201.drop_descrip: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.

301591.detail: You should know that I designed this outfit just by seeing the family crest here. Do you think it looks good?
301591.login: Merry Christmas. I suppose I'll let you take it easy today.
301591.unlock: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!
301591.touch: Santa Claus? ... Hmph, I graduated from that fairy tale long ago.
301591.main: {namecode:143}, stop frolicking around like a little kid, and don't pull on me either! Ugh... what am I going to do with you? |I still have to prepare presents for the three stooges... Jeez, can't they be a bit more considerate towards their big sis normally? Oh well, I suppose that's how it should be. |It's snowing... Hmm? It's not like I particularly want to play in the snow or anything, but if you want to so badly, I suppose I can tag along.
301591.feeling5: Look here, Christmas nowadays is a holiday that you celebrate with those who are important to you. You came here knowing that, didn't you? Me? I... don't particularly object...
301591.mail: Another greeting card for you... Curse you, what a normie.
301591.drop_descrip: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!

102060.feeling4: Are you fond of assertive big sister type characters? That is to say... someone like me...
102060.propose: Thank you... From now on I'll... What? You'd prefer it if I took the initiative and gave it to you instead? Y-you have a point... Okay then, should we do it again from the start?
102060.detail: Ah, Commander's looking... I have to behave like a big sister!
102060.feeling1: Sometimes I'm happy that I'm not actually your big sister...
102060.upgrade: Let me handle things from now on!
102060.battle: I'll show you what the tons-of-guns doctrine is really worth!
102060.home: That's the Commander I know. No problem for you at all, right?
102060.login: Commander, if you ever run into a problem, please tell me!
102060.mission_complete: Our mission rewards have arrived. I'll give my share of the rewards to my little sisters.
102060.feeling3: The bigger the better, don't you think? ...Hey! What are you staring at?! Gee, sorry for not being big enough, I guess!
102060.unlock: I'm the anti-aircraft cruiser Atlanta. Kept you waiting, huh, Commander? But from now on you can rest easy and let me handle everything!
102060.feeling2: Being a big sister isn't just about looking like one, you need to have the personality of one as well. That's why you can depend on me all you want~!
102060.touch: Mgh, don't touch me like that... My big sister image would be ruined!
102060.profile: I'm the anti-aircraft cruiser Atlanta... I was the flagship of the 10th and 11th Atlantic cruising fleet and I've taken part in nearly every military operation in the Pacific. Even the President has given me praise!
102060.main: Not being a flagship sure is more peaceful...|San Francisco was terrible to me! Just once is tolerable for accidental friendly fire, but she shot me well over ten times!|Shooting down aircraft is my specialty. Want me to teach you how to do it, Commander?
102060.win_mvp: All targets eliminated. Requesting new mission!
102060.feeling5: ... Huh? You want me to take the initiative? O-o-o-o-of course, I don't mind! I-I mean, I'm your big sister after all, so it's my job to guide you!
102060.lose: Argh, this is bad... My big sister image is ruined...
102060.expedition: Commander, the commission's done. Are we gonna go welcome the girls back?
102060.mail: You've got new mail! I wonder if any of the messages are from my sisters...
102060.drop_descrip: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Atlanta, Hull Number CL-51!
102060.mission: So, does this mean you're leaving all your unfinished missions to me, Commander?

102124.detail: Wh-what are you staring at me for... Is it weird to have fun at a festival now...?
couple_encourage: Louis... if you make me look dumb again then I really will get mad...
Rest easy, Helena! I'll assist you!
102124.battle: Let's get this over with quick, I wanna go back to the festival...!
102124.home: Do you want this...? Here, take it...
102124.login: I'll say this now: I don't like festivals in any... Ah, you know what, never mind! Just come with me, okay?!
102124.unlock: Come on, Louis, the goldfish stall is this way! ... W-why are you giving me that weird look like th– Wait... Eeeek! C-Commander?! When did you get here?!
102124.touch: Seems there'll be a fireworks display by the harbor... Commander, how about we go there on our walk?
102124.touch2: Don't make excuses... I know you did that on purpose...!
102124.main: Stupid Louis... She just went "I'd rather not be kicked by a horse" and walked off... Let's just forget about her... Could you lend me a hand, Commander? I want one to give to Helena...!
102124.win_mvp: Can we go back now, Commander?
102124.feeling5: *Sigh*, why can't I ever keep my composure in front of you... "What am I murmuring about"...? N-nothing! I didn't say a word...! Dummy...!
102124.lose: After all that trouble putting this on... This sucks...
102124.drop_descrip: Come on, Louis, the goldfish stall is this way! ... W-why are you giving me that weird look like th– Wait... Eeeek! C-Commander?! When did you get here?!

101421.drop_descrip: I am the courier of the night. In other words, it's my job to bring stuff straight to you, Commander. Here you go, this jack-o-lantern is for you.

303128.battle: Commander, please allow your big sister to take care of anything that stands in your way. Ehehe...
303128.home: Surely you must be tired. Come take a nap in big sister's lap~
303128.login: Commander, you didn't go to sleep that long ago. Did you miss big sister that badly~?
303128.unlock: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~
303128.touch: My, Commander, you're as spoiled as ever~ Here, come to big sister~
303128.touch2: Dar~ling, if you continue like this, I won't be able to hold back any more~ Hehe... just kidding~
303128.main: Even though I would be more than glad to allow you to feast your eyes upon me forever, you do need to get your work done~ |What should I cook today... Commander, what would you like to have? |Commander, you're just too cute~ I just can't get enough of you~
303128.win_mvp: As expected of my wonderful commander~
303128.feeling5: I've calmed down compared to before? Well, that's because I know that you'd never leave my side, hehe~ Well then, come into my loving embrace~
303128.drop_descrip: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~

103020.feeling4: You can always rest on my lap if you get tired, Commander. Don't worry, I won't play any tricks on you. ... Hm? I've always been this kind to you!
103020.propose: It's a promise, Commander! Every day from now on you'll hang out with me and do the stuff I enjoy. Like surfing, beach volleyball, and... scuba diving, I guess? Of course, I'll hang out with you and do all the stuff you enjoy, too~!
103020.detail: Sometimes good things happen when you're just coasting across the sea.
103020.feeling1: Commander, that look in your eyes kinda creeps me out...
103020.headtouch: Your hand feels just like Pensacola's...
103020.upgrade: Us pretty girls need to take care to maintain our good looks.
103020.battle: Those aren't allies up ahead. Ready all weapons!

103020.login: Commander, want to go swimming together?
103020.mission_complete: Can we go join the party now?
103020.feeling3: Commander, don't you ever get bored of lying around on the beach? Why don't we play some beach volleyball? Sun burn? No worries, Pensacola has already rubbed me down with sunscreen.
103020.unlock: Commander, I'm Salt Lake City, a heavy cruiser! You think I'm exposing too much? Well, I gotta keep a close eye on my waist, you know?
103020.feeling2: Helena, could you go find something interesting with that radar of yours? Wait... that's San Diego? Great, let's go play in the water together!
103020.touch: Oh, it's you, Commander. I thought it was Pensacola...
103020.touch2: Hey, don't do the same stuff Pensacola does...
103020.profile: I'm Salt Lake City, second ship of the Pensacola-class. That's right, I'm a genuine heavy cruiser. My armor's thin because of that treaty thing, but my firepower holds up. Although, I participated in lots of battles in the Pacific and survived to the end of it, so maybe armor isn't that important. The battle of Attu Island? Luck is a power of sorts too, you know? ... No, no, I'm not arguing. Anyway, do you really want me to wear as much as Laffey does?
103020.main: If you don't know how to swim then I can teach you, Commander.|Shell Kiska Island? Ahaha... that'd be a new experience for me.|Enterprise is too strict. Please don't be like her, Commander.
103020.win_mvp: This time it wasn't just all luck!
103020.feeling5: Welcome back, Commander! I was just about to finish drying your laundry. I cleaned up the books and other stuff that was lying around. How's it look? The tidiest it's ever been, right? And dinner will be... Hm? Why am I doing all this? Well, you know... just preparing for what comes later!
103020.lose: Wuah! I'm out of armor-piercing shells... damn!
103020.expedition: Whew, those girls went out on a commission in this blazing heat? They even completed it, too. Must be awful out there~
103020.mail: New mail for you. Oh my, is this a love letter? ... Hmm... Okay, now where's the trashcan?
103020.drop_descrip: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Salt Lake City, Hull Number CA-25!
103020.skill: The best defense is a good offense!
103020.mission: Who cares about missions, let's party!

105130.feeling4: Lately, my smile has become more natural? Emm, huh (scratches head), I was recently trying to find a new hobby. While I was searching, I realized that being with you is not so bad… (whispers)
105130.propose: Wait wait! We’re doing “that”, right? Is this your new way of teasing me!... Damn, you bastard, I’m not sure if I should cry or laugh about this...
105130.detail: Hmm, you want to know how well I fight?
105130.feeling1: You are too weak, it’s no fun playing with you, go practice some more.
105130.upgrade: It feels so good to become stronger.
105130.home: I’m glad that you didn’t get hurt—— What?! I don’t have feelings for you!
105130.login: Welcome back... how does my smile look? (Forcibly smiles)
105130.mission_complete: Go grab the reward yourself, I’m not interested.
105130.feeling3: No, no, that’s not right. If we do it this way, won’t it end much the same like in the past? … Don’t try so hard? You sometimes say stuff like that… Hmm? That was a good smile from me just now?
105130.unlock: Hello, Commander, I am Washington... my sister told me that I cannot be so rough once I join the fleet, so I am practicing my smile. Darn, why must I listen to her...
105130.feeling2: What must I do to possess a good smile... think about the things I like? If so, I feel very happy even at the thought of winning against South Dakota... muahahaha...
105130.touch: Don’t touch me as if you’re trying to be intimate with me.
105130.profile: North Carolina class ship no. 2. I am Washington! The thing I like to do the most is to destroy my enemies. Recently, I am practicing on my smile. —— Battle record? I don’t really show off with such things, all in all, how’s my smile?
105130.main: My smile looks beautiful? You jerk... oops, keep smiling, keep smiling. Thank you for your compliments. | Hey, that rigid South Dakota is still the same. Commander, you see, I am cuter than her. | A true measurement of friendship is their actions and not their words, I don’t like people who are rhetorical in nature.
105130.win_mvp: Sure enough, I am happiest when all the foes are annihilated~
105130.feeling5: I couldn’t help but smile when I saw you, this is the first time that I’m feeling this way... although, I also have other feelings rushing towards me. I suddenly want to see your expression when you are bullied by me—— Commander, stay with me for a while. (Laughs)
105130.lose: Oh, I will not forget you!
105130.hp_warning: I won't let go of victories to my enemies!
105130.expedition: Your memory can’t be worse than mine, right? The commission fleet has returned, won’t you go greet them?
105130.drop_descrip: North Carolina class battleship— Washington, hull number BB-56.
105130.skill: Out of my way. I'm ready to fight!
105130.mission: A new mission? Haha, now my blood is boiling.

302109.detail: I look even cooler now when I don't say anything? Whatever... have it your way...
302109.battle: There are people waiting for me... so I refuse to lose!
302109.login: Commander, you're back. Huh? I just happen to remember what your footsteps sound like.
302109.unlock: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.
302109.touch: Maybe I should go practice using this naginata or something...
302109.main: Recently, Mikuma has been telling me that I have more self-esteem... Not sure about that one though, I don't think I've really changed... |Secretary ship duties? Well, I still think I'm not really cut out for it compared to the others... but if it's what you want, I'll keep doing it. |Commander, be honest. What do you think about my new outfit after the retrofit? Um... if you like it, I suppose we can keep it like this...
302109.drop_descrip: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.

206041.detail: The Elders haven't been shy about complimenting my figure, though I can't help but feel a little bit embarrassed...
206041.login: Commander, what would you say to a stroll on the beach?
206041.unlock: Even though I see the ocean every day, changing into this swimsuit gives me a totally new outlook on it. How about you, Commander? Don't you feel at ease?
206041.touch: Commander, is this pose okay? How about my expression? Hehe, all right then, make sure you get my good side.
206041.main: Taking in the ocean, feeling the sea breeze, letting the sounds of the waves lap against my ears... I feel completely at peace here.|Coming to the beach with my Elders, and of course with the Commander, to spend a day off is so delightful.|Commander, Elder Hermes has been talking about this "Summer Duel Tournament" that's about to begin. Why don't we go watch together?
206041.feeling5: Commander, let's go to the beach together after sunset and watch the stars. I'll show you my constellation. And then we'll have... a chat.... sound good?
206041.drop_descrip: Even though I see the ocean every day, changing into this swimsuit gives me a totally new outlook on it. How about you, Commander? Don't you feel at ease?

302110.feeling4: I'm always willing to support my sister, but owing to her somber personality... I don't think anyone but you can truly guide her, Commander...
302110.propose: Sorry for taking so long, Commander. Huh? I should call you "darling"? Umm... D-darling... This feels a little awkward, but it's something I should slowly get used to. Now, I hope we will be together for many long years.
302110.detail: My... horn? If it makes people remember me, then I believe it's not all that bad.
couple_encourage: Mogami, try not to stray too far from me.
302110.feeling1: I've gotta warn my sister about how untrustworthy you are...
302110.upgrade: Your kindness is highly appreciated. I swear to repay it one day.
302110.login: Welcome back. Let's try to get a lot of work done today.
302110.mission_complete: I have completed my inspection of the mission rewards, Commander.
302110.feeling3: All Mogami-class cruisers were part of Cruiser Division 7, but because Kumano and Suzuya were launched later than me, it was I who had to look after Mogami. And for that reason, they aren't as close to her as I am.
302110.unlock: My name is Mikuma. I'm Mogami's little sister. If... if you don't mind, could you please look after her? She has a bit of an unusual personality, you see...
302110.feeling2: Pardon me, Commander, I'm occupied with the task you gave me... Okay, how may I help? Communication? Yes, of course, communication is important.
302110.touch: I'm standing by. Please give me your orders.
302110.touch2: ... Commander, please be wary of accidental discharges from my cannons.
302110.profile: I am Mikuma, the second ship of the Mogami-class. I collided with my sister in Midway, but I don't resent her for it. On the contrary: she... Ah, forgive me for changing the topic so suddenly... I shall do everything I can for the fleet, so please give me your orders.
302110.main: My sister is... probably sitting somewhere, alone, lamenting the past again. Commander, would you please excuse me for a moment?|A secretary should be the Commander's right hand. Please don't hesitate to give me orders.|I was the first heavy cruiser to sink in the war... Oh, never mind, it was nothing important.
302110.win_mvp: This is nothing to get thrilled about!
302110.feeling5: Jealousy... you say? It's never been on my mind... As long as I have my dear sister and my dear Commander... everything will probably be okay... I think?
302110.lose: *Gah*...! This will serve as a lesson...!
302110.hp_warning: Don't panic! We still have a chance!
302110.expedition: A commission has finished, Commander. If you're occupied at the moment, please send me in your stead.
302110.mail: Here is the letter that arrived today, Commander.
302110.drop_descrip: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number two – Mikuma.
302110.mission: I have organized the mission rewards, Commander. Could you confirm them, please?

107049.detail: C-Commander?! I-I-Is my bridge, really that beautiful?
107049.battle: Everyone, it's time to put what you learned to use!
107049.home: Commander, you've grown but you haven't changed much. Alright, here's your reward~
107049.login: This child seems fine... This one is recovering well... Ah, welcome back, Commander!
107049.unlock: The modernization that had never happened has finally been completed! From now on, I, Ms. Ranger, will continue to teach as well~
107049.touch: Yeah yeah, Commander is totally not good without a Teacher here... Yup, can't help it~
107049.touch2: Commander, can you help a teacher out here a little?... Eeek! ....Really?...
107049.main: A weapon may be powerful, but if it can't be used properly, it won't be completely effective. It is the teacher's job to teach you how to use them! Physical education? I-I'll teach that again!|I've only improved a few times before, and they were just small enhancements. Now that everyone is stronger, I can start getting some work done.|Commander? I believe in you, so I'm letting you study on your own while I work on my planes. I'll get angry if you avoid your study this time, alright?
107049.win_mvp: If you engage in some special training with me, you'll withstand fatigue for a longer time, Commander! ...Eh? Why are you looking at me like that?
107049.drop_descrip: I didn't realize I could still become more powerful! I'll work harder from here on out to teach everyone how to fight!

101039.detail: Fwaah... Commander, I need to take another nap, so I'm leaving the rest to you...
101039.unlock: Commander... I've been cocoooned up in my room for so long that I've started to metamorphize... Eh? It's because of the retrofit? Phew... thank goodness. Well then, guess it's time to go back to my room.
101039.main: Mmh... just staying together quietly like this... might be pretty nice too.|Wear my clothes properly? Eh...? Don't wanna~ More importantly, care for an Oxy Cola, Commander?
101039.drop_descrip: Commander... I've been cocoooned up in my room for so long that I've started to metamorphize... Eh? It's because of the retrofit? Phew... thank goodness. Well then, guess it's time to go back to my room.

301600.feeling4: General, let's play a game! Huh?! You've got work to do?! You really do? Do you want me to help? Then how about a massage? ...Hooray! I love you, General!
301600.propose: General, if anyone starts being mean to you then tell me. Hamakaze and I will go and get revenge on them for you. We're here for you, because we're all friends!
couple_encourage: Hamakaze, follow my lead!
301600.feeling1: Hmph! I'm done playing with you! Hamakaze, Tanikaze, where are you?
301600.upgrade: I am Isokaze, the leader of Destroyer Division 17!
301600.battle: I will lead the charge into batt... Hey, stop! Wait for me!
301600.home: You make me proud, General! Hey, uh, listen! I have a report for you! You see...
301600.login: General! It's time to charge into battle!
301600.mission_complete: General, our mission rewards are here! How much koku did we receive?
301600.feeling3: Western Army, attack! Fire on the Eastern Army! Our next move will be... Oh no! Hideaki was lured away! That's unfair, General! Darn, now I'm... *Sob*...
301600.unlock: All units, attaaack! ...Wait a second, where am I?! Oh, I know you! Urakaze-sama said you're... the general! Hmph! I'm Isokaze, the one destined to become a general that will make the whole world tremble in fear!
301600.feeling2: How I know so much? Urakaze-sama taught me everything about the warring states! She's really smart! But Hamakaze is still my best friend in the end! Heheheh~
301600.touch: General, give me a piggyback ride! We must charge into the enemy stronghold!
301600.profile: I am Isokaze of DD17! In the past, you see, I've worked with Hamakaze, Urakaze, Tanikaze... oh, and Yukikaze! My service record stands second to none! And that's why you should put me in charge of your missions!
301600.main: General! Come play warring states with me! You can be... Ieyasu! I'll be Mitsunari!|Hamakaze! Tanikaze! Let's depart! We're heading for the capital!|Urakaze-sama, my coat has been torn again... Fix it for me!
301600.win_mvp: Urakaze-sama, can you see my glorious victory?!
301600.feeling5: General, Urakaze-sama seemed angry at me and said I've started being cold to Hamakaze! But I still want to play with you... So come on! Let's go play together with Hamakaze!
301600.lose: Hamakaze, Hamakaze where are you... You have to save me!
301600.expedition: Our target: the base's docks! We must welcome back the commission team! Giddy-up, General!
301600.mail: General, I have a letter for you!

102190.detail: My dream is to one day be as pretty as my sis, St. Louis!
couple_encourage: H-hello! I'm H-Huh... Lena!

102190.upgrade: Commander, I'll help rub your back~!

102190.mission_complete: The mission rewards are here? Good job, Commander!
102190.feeling3: Commander, this hairstyle is really popular right now. Um, I still think I prefer this other one though better though... Which do you prefer?
102190.unlock: How should I do my hair today~? Huh? Wh-who are you? Why are you in my room? Huh? This isn't my room...? Eh? Ehhhh...?!
102190.feeling2: Jeez, Commander, how many times have I told you not to just barge into a girl's room?! ... Huh?
102190.touch2: Commander, all the girls will hate you if you do stuff like this!

Even though I seem to have come to a weird place, my big sis, St. Louis, taught me that a proper lady must remain calm at all times. You don't seem to be a shady person, so I guess I'll be your care.
102190.main: Big sis is just like a model, always changing into all kinds of clothes... B-but, if everyone thinks her clothes are cute, it's probably not too bad... |Huh? Who's that blonde-haired boy always surrounded by everyone? Um, I... I'm not particularly interested or anything... |Commander, do I look cute today?

102190.feeling5: I wonder why... my heart always flutters when you help me do my hair... It's totally different from when big sis does it... Hopefully, I'm not sick or something...
102190.hp_warning: Wh-what should I do, what should I do?!
102190.expedition: Commander, big sis told me before that nobody likes tardy people.
102190.mail: Huh... there's new mail? Commander, would you mind getting it yourself? I'm... having a bit of a bad hair day...
102190.mission: Commander, what do you think about the idea of wearing this hairstyle out to a mission?

10400011.login: Jeez, Commander~! This isn't just "sorry I'm late" levels of tardiness anymore! If you showed up any later, I would've just left without you! Fine, let's head to the festival right away!
10400011.mission_complete: Mission complete! Let's take these funds over to the festival and have a blast~!
10400011.unlock: The clothes from the Sakura Empire are so stylish! Commander, since it's a rare occasion, let's go take a look around! Ah, of course, don't forget to run the reel~♪
10400011.touch: If you think you can make a girl happy just by patting her head, you'd be wrong! Don't go around doing this stuff with everyone, got it?
10400011.main: Ahhh~ those candied apples look so good! But, I don't think I'm able to eat... Huh? Wait, if I'm here, then maybe... Ah- Yuudachi-chan already ate them all!? |If I'm already wearing a Sakura-style outfit, I also should match it with a set of animal ears! Benson-chan, lend me yoooours~! |I have to admit though, it's really hard to move around in a yukata... That's right! Prinz-chan, teach me the secret to fighting in this outfit~!

301601.detail: General, I want my red envelope!

301601.drop_descrip: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!

301090.feeling4: I cannot sleep well without my sisters by my side... T-that is not to say I am lonely! I-it is because I am concerned about them!
301090.propose: A promise that binds us for eternity... I understand! Then I shall show you my true right eye, right this mo... T-there is no need for it? All I need to do is close my eyes instead? Re... really...?
301090.detail: T-the reason I sleep with the lights on is because... i-it is not because I am afraid!
couple_encourage: Together we shall shine a light on the darkness!
We will always be together!
301090.upgrade: As the oldest of my siblings, I must work even harder!
301090.home: Commander~ Did you bring back any shiny items? ... Hm?! N-not at all, I am not asking simply because I want such things!
301090.login: My name is {namecode:11}, I am the ninja who will banish all the darkness in the world! ... Whoa! Commander, w-when did you get here?!
301090.feeling3: Commander, do you perhaps wish to see my true right eye?
301090.unlock: I am {namecode:11}, the oldest ship of Destroyer Division Six! Well met, Commander. I sincerely hope you will let me rebuild Division Six! ... Huh?! You do not permit the formation of destroyer divisions?!
301090.feeling2: I am a little worried... about {namecode:13} and {namecode:14}...
301090.touch2: S-should you touch me there again... then I will not be able to restrain myself!
301090.profile: I am {namecode:11}, a special-type destroyer! Destroyer Division Six consisted of me and my sisters! I was the first to be built and the first to be sunk! The Battle of Guadalcanal? I-I was trying to cast my light on the enemy! I was by no means scared of them! ... Ahem, you shall witness how strong I truly am... that you will!
301090.main: Sometimes I do not understand what {namecode:13} and {namecode:14} are trying to say...|Can {namecode:12} find her way here on her own? It has me somewhat worried...|W-w-what! Anyone would be shocked from suddenly seeing a person's shadow cast in the light in the middle of the night!

301090.feeling5: We Division Six destroyers have always been together! And... um, surely you will be together with me forever as well, Commander?
301090.lose: Damn... I-I shall get you next time...
301090.expedition: We may use my searchlight to find our way home! Huh? ... You have no need of it? R-really...?
301090.mail: New mail for you! Uh... I will read it out loud for you!
301090.mission: The ocean at night is a little scary... N-nay, I am not scared! B-but may I propose we do missions during daytime? You must agree, right?!

205020.feeling4: How do I put this... I'm considered to be one of the older girls, yet my body is like this... It might be unbecoming of one my age to compete with the younger girls, but I wanted to at least be attractive to you… What is a lady meant to do…
205020.propose: Finally the day has come! It looks like my efforts were not in vain... Let's go, Commander, I'm prepared for this. Officers, draw swords!
205020.detail: Don't be blinded by statistics. Victory depends on far more!
couple_encourage: Do you want to race this old lady?
Unmatched by any? *Sigh*...
Elegance does not belong on the battlefield.
Your Majesty, please look forward to my performance in battle.
Youngsters, follow me.
205020.feeling1: Would you please not act like we're close...
205020.battle: I would never let the commander's enemies escape!
205020.home: Whew, not a bad fight. Let's rest for a while.
205020.login: As long as I'm here, we can deal with any enemy, no matter how far they are.
205020.mission_complete: Missions give out rewards once you complete them. Don't forget that!

205020.feeling2: Commander, want to hear about the history of the Royal Navy? Maybe I should tell you something about the generals who used to accompany me.
205020.touch: Body contact...? I don't hate it...
205020.touch2: Just so you understand, I'm definitely not that sort of, erm...
205020.profile: Elizabeth-class fast battleship, Warspite, reporting in. I hold the record for the longest ranged hit on a moving target. I've come close to being defeated quite a few times, but I managed to cheat death every time. This must be my fate.

205020.feeling5: Well, enough of that. I'm Warspite, the one who spites war. Hmph! However, whosoever tries to take the Commander away from me will first have to face my cannons!
205020.lose: My damage control isn't functioning?! I've lost control of my steering wheel as well! Why now, at such a critical moment?!
205020.hp_warning: So this is how harsh the battlefield can be.
205020.expedition: Commissions? I suppose I do miss running around on errands... Let's go. We need to welcome back those hard workers!
205020.drop_descrip: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!
205020.mission: Accept your new mission and then get ready to head out, Commander!

107050.feeling4: Can I believe in you, Commander...? I mean, can I believe in myself this time...? I want... to try...
107050.propose: I had fallen into the darkness. It was you, Commander who gave me light and a helping hand which pulled me out of it. That's why this time, I, Yorktown, will give you my name. The name that shoulders the burden of liberty and peace...
107050.detail: It's alright if you don't remember me...
couple_encourage: Just because you speak like an adult doesn't mean you are one!
What a long overdue reunion!
Spread your wings and fly, Enterprise!
Commander, do you like to spoil your girls?
8 Talents? We're a pretty lively bunch!
107050.feeling1: So you truly will leave me one day...
107050.login: Greetings, Commander. If there's a problem, please leave it to me.

107050.feeling2: I want to maintain the current superior-subordinate relationship, Commander... Don't mind me...
107050.touch2: Are you truly prepared to leave your mark on someone like me?
107050.profile:
Lead ship of the Yorktown class aircraft carriers, Yorktown. 
Abandoned...? It wasn't their fault, but I do not have the courage to reach out for light from that darkness. Will you leave me, Commander? Or will you guide me by my hand...?
107050.main: This eagle really likes being with me, but is it alright for me to feed it...?|Commander, please do not confuse 42 with 24, no matter what|If there's time, maybe you should spend it with my younger sisters... I'm fine on my own
107050.win_mvp: If victory can bring peace, then I...!
107050.feeling5: Yes. I believe in you, Commander, as well as myself and the present day... The light beyond the darkness... I think I've finally found it

Commander, I hope this is not some perverse hobby of yours.
Let me witness your "justice."

202080.touch: Pest- I mean, Master, what requests do you have? I beg your pardon, that was a slip of the tongue.
202080.touch2: I do hope you have this same kind of strong spirit on the battlefield.

I've basically only fought against Iron Blood, having witnessed the demise of Scharnhorst, and participated in the hunt for Bismarck and Tirpitz. However, I underwent repairs throughout the end of the Second Great War and was unable to sortie. If there's nothing else you'd like to know, I would like to head back now.
202080.main: "Master, I love you." Please believe me, I put at least 30% emotion into those words. |Master, if you wish to take a nap, please tell me ahead of time. I will make sure you don't oversleep, with this gun. |Belfast dotes on you too much, Master. At this rate, I'm afraid that you will turn into a useless lump of driftwood.

202080.hp_warning: So, you pests have a few tricks up your sleeves...

couple_encourage: Everyone~ Charge with me!

101360.feeling2: Commander, if you want my help then just say so~

101360.touch2: Commander, you’re really bold… then let us skip ABCD and go directly to EFG tonight… haha, blushes, just kidding! (Wiggles tongue).

101360.skill: The one and only Hobby, full of enthusiasm~

303140.feeling4: Commander, there is nothing that makes me happier than being able to satisfy you.
303140.propose: Um, Commander, I never dreamt that you'd reciprocate my feelings, but... if this is your sincere desire, then I shall accept it. Commander, would you please seal our vows by helping me put this ring on?
303140.detail: Um, do I ever get bored...? Not particularly. Even if I'm not really doing anything, I enjoy getting to spend time with you, Commander.
couple_encourage: I'll be in your care again~
Let's give it our all!
303140.feeling1: Commander, let's try to do our best?
303140.upgrade: Thank you very much, Commander. I shall use this power for your sake.
303140.battle: Fleet status confirmed... prepare to open fire!
303140.home: Good work out there on your sortie. I'll handle the reports, so please take this time to get some rest.
303140.login: Welcome back, Commander. I've taken the liberties of preparing your documents. Um... would you also like to have some refreshments?
303140.mission_complete: We've done it, Commander! That's another mission done without a hitch!
303140.feeling3: Commander, what would you like to have tonight? Um, you'd like me to decide? In that case, would you like vegetable cream stew or pork cutlets?
303140.unlock: I'm Maya's sister, Choukai. I'm so glad to meet you. Um, by the way, we seem to have met before somewhere...
303140.feeling2: Commander, why don't you rest for a bit? Um, you'd like to hear me sing? Hmm, in that case...
303140.touch: Shall we go for a stroll before the sun goes down?
303140.touch2: C-Commander, if that is what you so desire, then...
303140.profile: I am the fourth ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Choukai. As the former flagship of the 8th Fleet, I took part in many campaigns. Commander, you can entrust any task to me!
303140.main: Commander, you're truly a kind person... |Commander, you should pick a day when you're not too busy to come look at the dandelions with me. |Commander, are you not well rested? As a matter of fact, I've actually been hard at work learning how to give massages, just to prepare for this moment! Here, don't be shy~
303140.win_mvp: Let's triumphantly return home in high spirits!
303140.feeling5: Commander, I'd do anything for you. Um, you'd do the same for me? Ehehe... that makes me really happy~
303140.lose: I can... still fight! I don't want to lose anyone ever again...!
303140.expedition: Military commission, complete. Rewards, received... Aye! I've recorded everything!
303140.mail: Commander, allow me to read the content of this letter to you.
303140.drop_descrip: Takao-class heavy cruiser number four – Choukai.
303140.skill: My kindness... is reserved for my friends only!

301350.feeling4: Commander~~ {namecode:34} sis and {namecode:33} sis are all bffs. I don’t care, I want to hug you, Commander!
301350.propose: Wahahaha, I made it just in time, Commander?! So, so it is me, right? It must be me, right?! If it is me, then you will not be wrong by picking me, Commander!
301350.detail: Commander, bad news! There’s a cockroach, please help me get rid of it!
301350.feeling1: Ack, the Commander is here, run!
301350.upgrade: Commander, I don’t think I’ve gotten smarter at all, what should I do!
301350.home: Oh no, Commander! I wanted to help sort out your paperwork, but now they’re all blown out of the window by this sudden gust of wind!
301350.login: Ahhh, where’d you go Commander? I was scared all by myself!

301350.feeling3: Commander, quickly come help me~ I’ve lost something again!

301350.feeling2: Commander, c-can you please help me look for something?
301350.touch: Wahahaha, incoming submarine!! … huh? It’s the Commander.
301350.touch2: Commander, how come after telling my sisters what you did, they all came rushing over to you?
301350.profile: I’m {namecode:137} from the 30th Destroyer Division. Hmm… where is everyone... I'm good at both defense and offense. What’s more, I am the most hard-working destroyer among my sisters. Hey Commander, while I was introducing myself, I seem to have lost my card!
301350.main: Although submarines are terrifying, but I’m not afraid of airplanes! |Oh no, Commander, my torpedo is missing!! Hmm, it’s behind me? |Commander!! Just now when I ran over to you, the flower vase fell to the ground, was it haunted?

301350.feeling5: Commander~~ What should I do, all I think about is you, am I sick?!
301350.lose: Sigh, Commander, I want to go home...
301350.expedition: Alert Commander, my sisters sneaked out without permission and I just saw them return! Huh, it was for a commission? O that’s right!
301350.mail: Commander, a new batch of mail has successfully flown out! What should I do?
301350.drop_descrip: The fourth ship of {namecode:33} class destroyer — {namecode:137}

I really dislike submarines, but I should be fine as long as we deal with them carefully~

101110.touch: Mmm, I feel the justice coming from you!

101110.main: Become a friend of justice with me!|Justice is justice~!|My sonar shows... it looks like your heart is beating extra fast, Commander!
101110.win_mvp: See? This is the real strength of the Little Beavers!
101110.feeling5: In the stories I read, the hero always goes back to his normal life after defeating evil with his partners. I have to say, I feel a bit sad reading an ending like this...
101110.lose: I'll be back! Justice will prevail! *Sob*...
101110.expedition: A commission of justice has just been completed!
101110.mail: Your mail? Of course! We need help from others if we want to make this world a just one. Reply as soon as you can!
101110.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer - Charles Ausburne, Hull Number DD-570!
101110.skill: Accept your punishment in the name of justice!
101110.mission: Commander, let's finish it in one go! Now is the chance to deliver swift justice!

101174.drop_descrip: I'm done changing... how is it? Today, I’m supposed to call you “valued guest?” Um... I don’t really get it...

302140.feeling4: Hmm, I feel a little guilty over always making you come with me... Is there anything you'd like to do? We'll do it together, of course!
302140.propose: You can stare as much as you'd like. Hehehe~ From now on I will use my brains and brawn to serve you, my sweetheart whom I love so much!
302140.detail: Commander, would you like to study together with me?
couple_encourage: I want to shine as gloriously as you, my sisters!
302140.feeling1: My sisters chose you because you just let them mess around without being scolded? How strange...
302140.upgrade: With your support I can work even harder!
302140.battle: My sisters, please look forward to my performance in battle!
302140.home: There's nothing better than getting to come back home. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?
302140.login: Welcome back, Commander! I'll try to be the best secretary you've ever had!
302140.mission_complete: You've cleared another mission! You're so brilliant, Commander! I'll need to work just as hard!
302140.feeling3: What are my hobbies? ...I don't really have one in particular. But I enjoy reading and training... Oh, would you like to train together with me? Heheheh~
302140.unlock: Nice to meet you, Commander! I'm the light cruiser Naka! My sisters are better known than me, but I swear that one day I'll be even more famous than them!
302140.feeling2: What I do on my days off? Well, I get up and do morning training, I read for an hour, I do target practice for 2 hours, and then... Basically, I make full use of my vacation days! I have to work really hard to become stronger, you know?
302140.touch: Hum hum~♪ Oh, sorry, am I disturbing you in the middle of work...?
302140.touch2: Eek! ...Please, Commander, try to stay focused on your work while in the office!
302140.profile: I'm Naka, Sendai-class light cruiser number three! Due to certain circumstances, my construction was delayed, I was redeployed to place after place, and my service record as the flagship of Desron 4 isn't much to brag about... but that's okay! I'll still work my butt off to try to surpass my sisters!
302140.main: If it looks like there's nothing for me to do, would you mind if I did a little training on my own? I won't get in the way of your work!|Jintsuu is wise, Sendai is strong... but I'll work my way towards both brains and brawn! ...Ahahah, though I'm not sure if I can actually do it.|If you're tired, would you like me to give you a good relaxation tip? I actually know quite a lot about it~
302140.win_mvp: Compared to my goal of surpassing my sisters, this is no big deal at all!
302140.feeling5: Huh? Are you saying you've been waiting for a chance to go on a date too? Heheh, in that case~ Why don't we do it, Commander?
302140.lose: Oh no! Commander, we should retreat immediately! Jintsuu said we shouldn't make meaningless sacrifices!
302140.hp_warning: Everyone, stay calm! Let's change our strategy!
302140.expedition: I think a commission has been completed. We should go and say thanks to the returning team!
302140.mail: Commander, I have mail for you. I picked it up on the way back from my training.
302140.drop_descrip: Sendai-class light cruiser number three – Naka.
302140.mission: I reorganized the mission list for you! Here, please choose one!

301629.unlock: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Oh wow, a b-butterfly?! It really is a butterfly! Is this for me? Thank you, Commander!
301629.touch: Wah! This time I'll poke you in return! Poke! Poke poke~!
301629.touch2: Ah, I see! It's my turn now! Poke poke... Scratch scratch... Can I nap while you give me a piggyback, Commander? ...Zzzzz....
301629.main: I really wonder... What might Urakaze-chan and Isokaze-chan be doing right now...|Something good is going to happen today, Commander.|You're a very warmhearted person, Commander.
301629.drop_descrip: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Oh wow, a b-butterfly?! It really is a butterfly! Is this for me? Thank you, Commander!

201070.feeling4: I don't mean to boast, but I'm good at concealing my emotions. Are you saying you don't dislike emotionless girls? ...I see. You are a pervert, Commander.
201070.propose: Commander, are you getting ready to head outside? ... What are you worried about? You think we're heading to the police station? What an undependable adult. Hah... There's a more important place to go, isn't there?
201070.detail: I'm happy that I'm so treasured by you, Commander, but please don't have any weird expectations. Yes, weird expectations.
201070.upgrade: You do have strange expectations of me, don't you Commander?
201070.home: Commander, looking at me with eyes full of expectations will not cause me to give you candies, you know? You're an adult as well, aren't you?
201070.login: I was thinking you'd be back soon since you think about the fleet...
201070.mission_complete: Are you so lazy that you don't even want to collect the rewards?
201070.feeling3: There used to be 4 Single Barrels. Lil' A and Lil Y were retired because of submarine fighting, so now I'm left with Lil' B and Lil' X... I feel... a little bit lonely
201070.unlock:
Good day. I'm B class' Bulldog. ...I'm an adult so please do not judge me by my looks. I hope you aren't an adult who does that, Commander. 
I'll be in your care.
201070.feeling2: The fleet? Hmm... I can't say that I like it, but I don't hate it either...
201070.touch: What is it? If it's your personal needs, Commander, I'll have to refuse.
201070.touch2: Lil' B! Lil' X! Target the Commander!
201070.profile: I, Bulldog, am the youngest of the B class. My accomplishments were the acquisition of encoded transmission machines, codebooks, and the witnessing of the signing of the surrender treaty. If you are not an idiot, Commander, you should know the worth of such accomplishments.
201070.main: Are you an idiot, Commander?|The best thing I can do is submarine subjugation|Commander, if your hand is on my head for more than 3 seconds, I'll bite down on it, you hear?
201070.win_mvp: This was a given. Please don't touch my head like I'm a child.
201070.feeling5: Commander, you are an idiot and a pervert, but I've never said that I hated people like them before, you know? ...But to make someone smaller than you say such things, you are truly a dumb pervert.
201070.lose: Sometimes we win, sometimes we lose. It's not such a big deal. ... Tsk...
201070.expedition: Commander, have you forgotten when you took the commissions?
201070.mail: You are low on [communication power] but please, read your mails properly
201070.drop_descrip: B-class destroyer ー Bulldog, Hull Number H91!
201070.skill: Lil B, Lil X, I'm counting on you
201070.mission: If you need the secretary to even notice the progress of your missions, then you are truly an idiot.

202221.home: Good work, Commander. Today, would you like to try some tea from the Dragon Empery?
202221.login: Welcome back, Commander. Today, I'll be visiting the girls from the Dragon Empery to learn a bit more about their customs. Would you like to come with me?
202221.unlock: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.
202221.touch: For a Royal maid like myself to don the attire of the Dragon Empery... isn't this what cultural exchange is all about?
202221.main: Commander, even if you're just eating a pork bun, please make sure to use a serviette. |Etiquette is closely linked to culture, so it's no surprise that there are many differences between the Royal Navy and the Dragon Empery. |The girls from the Empery said that they'd be willing to teach me a few New Year's greetings. Once I've learned them, I'll be able to give you some blessings!
202221.drop_descrip: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.

301631.detail: I wonder if I can find Arashio here at school...?
301631.login: It's time to go to school again... Commander, want to walk with me?

301631.main: How nice it'd be to go to school with Arashio... |Mr. Kitty always likes to rub against peoples' legs. |*yawn*...It feels nice to take a nap during class, but... I probably shouldn't, right?
301631.drop_descrip: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.

301120.feeling4: Commander, no matter where you go, I will always be with you. ... However... I don't think I can... leave the boundaries of this screen...
301120.propose: Commander... please feel at ease. I would never abandon you. Even if you've had enough and run away, I will always, always be waiting here for you.
301120.detail: Commander... it seems you're always holed up in your room...
couple_encourage: {namecode:12}...? Sorry, I thought you were someone else...
Destroyer Division Six... departing!
301120.feeling1: Commander, no matter what you may become, I will always be with you.
301120.upgrade: Phew... I'm glad that didn't hurt as much as I thought.
301120.home: Welcome back, Commander. Even if you didn't "acquire new characters",I will always be here.
301120.login: Is that... you, Commander? I can't believe you're logging in at this time of day... shouldn't you be doing something else?
301120.mission_complete: This month's bonus pay won't be postponed into the next month.
301120.feeling3: A shared sorrow is one made half, and shared joy is one made double. So please feel free to talk to me about anything.
301120.unlock: Are you the commander...? You don't seem very reliable... Ah, sorry, my self-introduction. My name is... {namecode:14}.
301120.touch: Commander... could you pat my head?
301120.touch2: Commander... there's no medicine that can fix you.
301120.profile: I am... the Sakura Empire's {namecode:11}-class type III destroyer, {namecode:14}. As the youngest of my class, I participated in a lot of battles in the World War. But I prefer escorts, transports, and rescues over combat. ... Commander? Would you like to have your head patted too?
301120.main: Commander, your biggest flaw is how kind you are.|{namecode:40}... she's helped me quite a lot...|"Salvaging" is my specialty!
301120.win_mvp: ... I'M the MVP? ... Is this fleet... doing okay?
301120.feeling5: Commander, it's terrible for your body eat junk food all the time. How about cooking your own food once in a while? Hm? Don't worry, I'll taste test it together with you!
301120.lose: Phew... Commander... you're very good at running away...
301120.mail: You have mailophobia? ... You don't have to be scared, I'm here with you.
301120.skill: If only everyone were here with us...
301120.mission: If you leave your missions unfinished forever... then you'll end up having to do this bad thing called "overtime".

102070.feeling4: I'm not afraid of having nightmares anymore... b-but can I still sleep together with you, Commander...?
102070.propose: ...Mhm, I have faith in you, Commander... I told the people in my dreams that I've found happiness and would do my best to live on for their sake as well... I'm truly... truly happy right now...
102070.detail: The... old injury to my foot? Well... my foot's still a bit stiff, but I won't ever let myself drag everyone else down...!
102070.feeling1: Don't come near me! ...Sorry, I think you're a little scary, Commander...
102070.battle: Everyone... look after yourselves... and watch out for those mean submarines...
102070.home: I'm really hoping this war will end soon... Once it's over, let's all go someplace together...
102070.login: C-Commander... I'll always be w-waiting for you here...
102070.mission_complete: I don't need any rewards... just being here with everyone is enough for me...
102070.feeling3: Commander, can I go to bed with you again tonight? ... I feel very safe when I sleep next to you...
102070.unlock: I-I'm Juneau... I'm a cruiser... I'm scared of pain... *Sob* And I'm scared of you, Commander...!
102070.feeling2: I... often have nightmares about five brothers whose faces are all blurred, and they tell me to come with them... It's really scary...
102070.touch: Pl... please be gentle... I'm very susceptible to pain...
102070.profile: I-I'm Juneau, an Atlanta-class anti-aircraft cruiser... Because I have high anti-air capabilities, I was assigned to a Task Force, but I'm actually scared of getting shot... Unfortunately I couldn't make it back home from Espiritu Santo...
102070.main: *Eek* Commander?! Y-you scared me...|I want to be brave... But it's really hard...|Commander, have I annoyed you in any way...?
102070.win_mvp: Phew... I almost got hit... *Sob*... I don't care about being the MVP... I'm just trying my best so I can come home in one piece...
102070.feeling5: Now when I dream about those five brothers... I can see their faces clearly, and they bless me with their smiles... But somehow it was so sad it almost made me cry... *Tearful sobbing*... Can I really live happily together with you, Commander? It's not just a dream, right...?
102070.lose: That hurts! ... I can't feel my left foot... Someone come save me....!
102070.expedition: Umm... Commander... there's a commission that's been completed...
102070.mail: Commander... excuse me... here's your mail...
102070.drop_descrip: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Juneau, Hull Number CL-52!
102070.skill: Me too! I-I'll give it my best shot!
102070.mission: What? A mission? I don't mind as long as we aren't fighting submarines...

301121.detail: Mr. Commander, after you swallowed {namecode:14} up... you must be ready to sortie.
301121.login: ...{namecode:14}’s heartfelt wish, has it been communicated? …Mr. Commander...

301121.touch2: Mr. Commander, have you heard {namecode:14}’s heartfelt words? You’re really amazing Mr. Commander!
301121.main: Are you hungry… Mr. Commander? |Are you trying to find {namecode:14}, Mr. Commander? {namecode:14} is right in front of you. |Mr. Commander, you’re always so gentle...
301121.drop_descrip: It doesn’t matter if {namecode:14} becomes Mr. Commander's dessert… but if {namecode:14} cannot be found, Mr. Commander will feel so devastated, perhaps he won’t be able to command the fleet… so… please! Please convey {namecode:14}'s heartfelt wish to Mr. Commander——

301122.login: I was beginning to think that you forgot about our plans, Commander.

301122.main: Commander, I'd like some taiyaki. Is that okay? |It feels unexpectedly nice to walk around without my shoes... Commander, why don't you try it too? |Commander, you can go check out everyone's yukatas if you'd like. I'll look around by myself first.
301122.feeling5: Commander, I know I'm super cute and all, but you'll develop social anxiety if you constantly cling to me and ignore everyone else. Since I'm also super responsible, you should go to the festival and enjoy the company of others.
301122.drop_descrip: I usually go to festivals with Ikazuchi, but this would be my first time going with you. Hmm? Where should we visit first?

103030.feeling4: Smiling? I guess it's true that I rarely smile... I'm a pretty stubborn girl, and I don't have many friends... Hm... If you like girls who smile, then I'll try to do that every now and then...
103030.propose: You finally realized it, didn't you, you dense man... But to be fair, I never had the courage to put it into words either... A-anyway, from now on, let's work together as dense partners in love, shall we?
103030.detail: My armor's gotten thicker, but it feels like I'm more exposed than before...
103030.feeling1: I'm getting distracted here, so do you think you could be quiet for a bit?
103030.upgrade: Thank you. I'll have you rewarded for this later.
103030.battle: The battle horn has sounded! C'mon, let's go!
103030.home: Nobody got left behind, right? Then the fleet's safely made it back.
103030.login: With proper training, I think we could make quite the team, Commander.
103030.mission_complete: Rewards have arrived. You should check them out.
103030.feeling3: I have a buddy who's a bit noisy and little sisters who are pretty rowdy, so having a friend like you who's rather quiet feels pretty unusual...
103030.unlock: Hm? Oh hey, Commander. If you can accurately predict where I'm gonna show up, then maybe we're in sync with each other... If only Hornet and I could be like that... *Sigh*...
103030.feeling2: I'm not really the talkative type, but if you're still willing to be my friend, then maybe...
103030.touch: Um, I'm a... little ticklish right there...
103030.profile: I'm Northampton, a Washington Treaty cruiser. I participated in the Doolittle Raid and the Battle of Midway, and I've earned 6 battle stars. I regret not being able to bring Hornet back home in one piece...
103030.main: You'll start to calm down if you just sit and listen to the waves...|Houston, you're too loud! Pipe the hell down!|Hold on, I'm thinking about something...
103030.win_mvp: I never thought I'd be able to do something like this...
103030.feeling5: ... Someone I love, huh? Well, there is someone, but I don't think I can say their name just like that... Hey, Commander, aren't you a lot like me? Hornet always tells me I'm not good at adapting to new things, and neither are you...
103030.lose: I knew we couldn't win that easily...
103030.expedition: Hey, you have a commission that's been completed.
103030.mail: Commander, I've left your mail on the desk.
103030.drop_descrip: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Northampton, Hull Number CA-26!
103030.mission: Looks like that mission hasn't been completed yet. Let me handle it!

105140.feeling4: Another way to live other than fighting? I... do not know what to do, Commander. I have always lived like this... Can you teach me?
105140.propose: I feel warm when you're by my side, Commander. Your goals bring me the drive to fight. I become happy when I hear your words... I once offered you my shields. From now on... I give you my heart.
couple_encourage: Don't just focus on firing. Keep surveying the area!
Sorry, I might have to bother you again.
Enterprise! Victory is now!
Kaede's Legion... Nice name!
105140.battle: Come at me with all you got!
105140.mission_complete: Commander, the mission rewards have arrived.
105140.feeling3: I exist to help you achieve your goals, Commander. Other than that, I have no real value... A skirt? I've never worn something so fluffy before.
105140.unlock: I am South Dakota, Commander. I shall become your shield and protect you from all cannon fire.
105140.feeling2: Your will is my command, Commander.
105140.touch: I'm ready to move out anytime.
105140.touch2: If this is what you want to do...
105140.profile: Battleship of Eagle Union, South Dakota. When it comes to battlefields, I wish for you to not leave my side. I will protect you, Commander. 'The Strongest Shield'? Vain titles are worthless. There's meaning only in being useful.
105140.main: In the darkness, my will was tempered. I fear nothing.|As long as I am of use to Commander, I am fine with handing my credit over to others.|Those who stand as Commander's enemies, are enemies all the same.
105140.win_mvp: Partial victories aren't worth celebrating, Commander.
105140.feeling5: So this is your perspective, Commander... I choose how I live, was what you said... This time, I fight not for my duty, but for the sake of your smile, Commander.
105140.lose: I am sorry, Commander... It's a shame...!
105140.expedition: The commission teams are back... If it is necessary, send me off as well.
105140.drop_descrip: South Dakota-class battleship –  South Dakota, Hull Number BB-57!
105140.mission: Commander, please do not forget about completing the missions.

308030.feeling4: Although we can't become close friends that easily, at least we're making some progress... I suppose time will take care of the rest. Commander, thank you so much for your help. As a reward... *kiss*
308030.propose: Commander, I'm sure that you will be able to create that world... where everyone can smile from the bottom of their heart... As for me, I can't think of anything happier than being with you right now.
308030.detail: I love the serenity of the night. Nobody ever notices my presence.
308030.feeling1: Does this fleet exist only to wage war...?
308030.battle: I'll let the rest of you handle the anti-sub.
308030.home: Commander, are the conditions of the waters suitable for me to carry out my activities?
308030.login: Commander, submarines will die if you take them out of the water. I-I was just kidding...
308030.mission_complete: These mission rewards... there's nothing that can be brought underwater...
308030.feeling3: "A journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step?" Hmm... I suppose I can start by saying hello to her...
308030.unlock: I-58, reporting in. I usually like hanging out in the water by the docks, so you know where to look if you need me~
308030.feeling2: Now that we're all on the same team, I'm going to have to learn to work with Indianapolis... but that sister of hers, bleh... Ugh, maybe I'll just go for a swim instead...
308030.touch: It's important to warm up before diving. Commander, let's do some exercises together.
308030.touch2: I mean... I'll admit they're on the small side... but that makes it more hydrodynamic!
308030.profile: Type-B Mod 2 cruiser submarine, I-58. Yup, that's me. I was born towards the end of the war, and participated in several missions. Before the end of things, I managed to sink Indianapolis. Even though it was a great achievement, it's not like it ultimately made a difference...
308030.main: It's not like I'll die if I'm taken out of the ocean, but I definitely prefer being in it. *blub blub* |Commander, when it comes to swimming, which stroke is your favorite? Crawl? Butterfly? Breaststroke? |There are a lot of miraculous things in the ocean. Want to go on a dive with me and experience it for yourself?
308030.win_mvp: Is that all you surface-lubbers are made of?
308030.feeling5: It's hard to let go of the past... but Commander, you've rewritten everyone's futures, to one where we can all move forward together. Commander, I can't be prouder of the fact that I fell for you.
308030.lose: I've been found, huh... Next time, I've got to be sneakier...
308030.expedition: I wonder what's going on up there on the surface... Ah, Commander, your commission fleet has returned.
308030.mail: Commander, there's new mail... Ah, sorry, I just left the water so I got it wet...
308030.skill: Can you predict where I'm going to attack from?
308030.mission: New missions? Is there something that I can do?

101240.feeling4: C'mon, why are you pulling on my cheeks... I was faking my smile? No, that was a sincere smile! Couldn't you tell?
101240.propose: What is it, Commander? ... Close my eyes? Haha, are you trying to get back at me for my pranks? Okay then... *Closes her eyes* You're so dumb, thinking you can... H-huh...? Is this what I...
101240.detail: Look, Commander, I won't level up just from you staring at me.
101240.feeling1: Wait a bit... I'm just tidying up... I won't play any more tricks on you, Commander. Are you happy now?
101240.battle: Maybe I'll fight for real this time~

101240.mission_complete: Oh, these are rewards~ I was just about to throw them away~
101240.feeling3: You don't seem to be too angry about my pranks these days... It's making me feel a bit lonely. Hm? No, I'm not trying to be cocky!

101240.feeling2: Oh? You fell in love with me at first sight, Commander? I don't fancy anyone who is that shallow...
101240.touch: Don't you find this hobby of yours a bit strange...?
101240.touch2: ... You'd better be ready when you're going to sleep tonight, Commander!
101240.profile:
I'm Sims, the name ship of the Sims-class. 
Commander... don't even think about mentioning the Battle of the Coral Sea in front of me. It instinctively makes me want to pull pranks on people~
101240.main: You know, I've got a little sister called Morris. She's just so fun to tease~|Try to find out how many surprises I've got in store for you, Commander!|Come on, let's play! Ahaha! Tickle tickle!
101240.win_mvp: Aww, you were so close to beating us~ Heehee~!
101240.feeling5: Let's flip a coin, Commander. If it's heads, you have to say "I love Sims" once... Wait! Ah, you caught me. It's heads on both sides!
101240.lose: I would rather have stayed home and pranked the commander...
101240.expedition: A commission will be finished in five minutes~! *grins devilishly*
101240.mail: Someone's sent you a love letter! ... Oh, never mind, I read it wrong!
101240.drop_descrip: Sims-class destroyer - Sims, Hull Number DD-409!
101240.mission: Don't forget your missions while you're dealing with my pranks!

301381.login: Commander, good afternoon... Huh? It's not...?
301381.unlock: Huh...? Where am I...? What time is it...?

301381.drop_descrip: Huh...? Where am I...? What time is it...?

408030.feeling4: My true feelings are the most important...? I... want to be of service to you... because you're always so nice to me...
408030.propose: The most fortunate time in my whole life was when first I met you, Commander... If we're together, I'm sure I'll be able to gain some more luck. I'm kind of... excited about that.
408030.detail: Pennies are said to bring good luck, so I saved a bunch in my piggybank... but that didn't seem to do much for me...
408030.feeling1: It's just my luck to run into a commander like you...

Not bad, huh. |According to legend, a mythical beast called the "Nian" comes out during the Lunar New Year. It can be warded off by setting off a lot of firecrackers. |I heard that it's customary in the Dragon Empery to hand out "red envelopes" during the New Year. Should I prepare some for the Union girls?
107062.drop_descrip: So this is the traditional attire of the Dragon Empery? Hmm... it fits quite well. Oh? Custom-made bow and arrows… Interesting, let's see how far these arrows can fly.

105080.detail: Commander, I will do my best to meet everyone's expectations
105080.feeling1: Commander, I'll go play on my own now~

105080.feeling2: You don't know if you can be friends with someone unless you tried to make them. Commander, wanna hang out together?
105080.touch: This is comfy. Every time big sis scolds me, she comforts me with this afterwards as well.
105080.touch2: Wait-... Commander! Where are you touching? Big sis wouldn't do this!

105080.main: I feel different from big sister? That's not true. She might not look it but she's actually kind|Ah~ Big sis didn't say much today... Wha! N-nothing at all!|Ah, where did my undies go? Eheh
105080.win_mvp: Aaah... that was a great workout
105080.feeling5: Tennesee said to me, 'You must be careful who you choose as a partner.' 'Once you do, tell me', she also said. Well, if it's you, Commander, she won't say a word, I think...
105080.lose: Oof... Big sis will lecture me for sure!
105080.expedition: Commander, the girls from the commissions have returned. Let me do one next time, please~
105080.mail: It's new mail. Wanna open it up right away?
105080.drop_descrip: Tennessee-class battleship –  California, Hull Number BB-44!
105080.mission: Commander, don't forget to do your missions!

301141.detail: It's cold? It doesn't feel cold at all to me!

301141.touch: Shiratsuyu, Shigure, let's have a snowball fight!

301141.drop_descrip: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!

201210.feeling4: Commander, you see, I want to be confessed to under the legendary tree like in comics~ and stuff...

201210.detail: Commander, you care so much about me... I'm so very happy!
couple_encourage: Witness the power of the J-class!
Let's work hard for the Commander!
Kaede's Legion, fight!
201210.feeling1: Commander, if you don't behave yourself, I am going to start disliking you. You hear me?
201210.upgrade: Hehe, your care is very heart-warming, Commander!
201210.battle: This seems like a good way to kill time!

201210.mission_complete: Commander, Commander! Let's go check out the rewards!

201210.touch2: Kyaa~! Commander, perverted behaviour is bad!
201210.profile:

My sisters and I sisters were part of the Narvik battle and the evacuation of Dunkirk! I had a little trouble along the way, but I fought until the very end!

201210.win_mvp: Am I amazing? Oh you shouldn't have~ But, please learn how to do a better job praising me!
201210.feeling5: Being together with you makes me so happy, Commander~ Ah, I made a boxed meal. Do you want to try some?

301143.detail: Commander, look, these are my spoils of war! Ahh, I'm so glad that there's so much delicious meat to chow down on at the banquet!
301143.home: Awoooo! This skewer is so yummy! Nnh? Commander, want a bite? Here's a piece for you!

301143.touch2: Commander! I'm gonna get super mad!

301143.drop_descrip: Commander, look at me, look at me! What do you think of my new outfit? If you like it, wanna give it a feel?

107063.detail: Commander, are you doing well? Live long and prosper!
107063.feeling1: Maybe I should just hit the road and never look back...
107063.home: Good work out there! Go ahead and take a break while the others are being inspected.
107063.login: Ah, you're here. I'm ready to go whenever you are. Oh, can't be forgetting my helmet!

107063.touch: Would you also like to see my trusty steed?

107063.mail: Commander, there's an incoming message from fleet command.
107063.drop_descrip: Happy Anniversary! Commander, celebrate to your heart's content today! I'll be praying for our continued victories!

102140.feeling4: I used to think commanding was just about giving orders from a comfy room while sounding like a bigshot... But after seeing it for myself, now I understand. You have a tough job, Commander.
102140.propose: Big sis told me to follow my heart. Which is why I'm here: to follow my heart. Are you following yours, Commander?
102140.detail: Big sis! ... Oh, it's you. Need something?
couple_encourage: ... I won't embarrass you, big sis!
102140.feeling1: Guess my big sis can't tell good and bad people apart...
102140.upgrade: I'm one step closer to my big sis...!
102140.home: Well done. You should get some rest.
102140.login: So, you're back. I'll take my leave, then. It's too crowded in here for me.
102140.mission_complete: Rewards, eh... Guess this is part of my job. I'll go get them.
102140.feeling3: My big sis is... strong, cool, has a golden smile, and she could probably beat anyone in a fight... I want to be like her one day.
102140.unlock: You're a commander? You don't... look reliable. But my big sis works for you... I've no choice, then. Montpelier, reporting for duty. I don't really care whether you give me orders or not.
102140.feeling2: I don't get why my big sis chose you. But I trust her intuition.
102140.touch: ... Huh? If you've no need of me, don't call for me.

102140.feeling5: I don't just blindly listen to everything my big sis says. I listen because she's always right... And I finally get why she chose you. It's because you're outstanding.
102140.lose: Big sis... I'm sorry... I've stained the reputation of the Knights of the Sea...
102140.hp_warning: Big sis told me... to never give up!

102140.mail: I left your mail over here.

couple_encourage: Who would I work best with...

308050.hp_warning: L-Looks like I've drawn too much attention...
308050.expedition: What's the commission of the composition team... Umm, I mean, the composition of the...

307028.drop_descrip: To hold one's hand and grow old together with him... If it is to be with you, then it won't so bad.

couple_encourage: U-boats, it's our time to shine!

408050.feeling5: True, I can't guarantee I'll be speedy when I dive... but no matter what, you'll be mine, Commander! Especially your heart! Hahah!
408050.lose: Oh nooo...! Ahaha... How the heck could we lose...
408050.hp_warning: Mein Leben! Better perform emergency maneuvers...

201212.detail: Don't worry, guys~! I've already packed all your favorite foods!

901010.feeling4: I think I'm starting to get it, but maybe not... But, I'm so glad that you're patient enough to teach a dummy like me. Thank you, Commander!

couple_encourage: Forbin, shall I take the lead?

901010.unlock: Eh? Who are you... Ah! Right, you're the Commander! I'm the L'Adroit-class destroyer, Le Mars! A pleasure meetin' you!
901010.feeling2: To be an outstanding knight, it's not enough to just have the strength to protect others. You must also become wise through learning! But... I always start dozing off when I'm studying... *yawn*
901010.touch: My shoulders were starting to get stiff too... Thanks a ton, Commander!
901010.touch2: Th-this place also needs a massage? Um... it feels a little strange...
901010.profile: Back then, I wasn't able to fulfill my duties, but... Commander, this time, I'll show you what I'm capable of!
901010.main: Commander, I'll teach you some stretches for those long days!|Being a commander sure is tough, isn't it? Having to micromanage this and that... 901010.feeling5: Even though I still don't quite understand this stuff, there is one thing that's certain - when it comes to learning things about you, Commander, I function twice as well!
