301148.detail: I dunno why, but wearing this makes me feel like I'm always by your side!
301148.battle: *Woof*! I won't let you lay a finger on the Commander!
301148.login: Commander! Heheheh~! I knew it was you just from the way you smell!
301148.unlock: Look, Commander! Isn't this kimono thing all, like, red and white and cool? I dig it! ... But what occasion is it for?
301148.touch: Commander! Did I do something praiseworthy?! Heheheh~! Pat me, c'mon!
301148.main: Commander, you busy? If not, can we play? We can play whatever you want!|Oh yeah, I tried making some food for you the other day, but I ended up wrecking the kitchen...|When there's nobody to fight, just gazing at you keeps boredom away... Doesn't keep sleepiness away, though...
301148.feeling5: I don't get complicated stuff, but I know that I love you, Commander! Anyone who dares to try messing with you will first have to argue with my cannons!
301148.lose: Commander... It's impossible to fight while wearing this stuff...
301148.hp_warning: You shredded my cherished clothes... Now you've made me MAD!
301148.expedition: Commander, the commission team's back! ... Where's my headpat? C'mon, I want one!
301148.mail: Commander, here's your mail! Hope I didn't get the wrong letter...
301148.drop_descrip: Look, Commander! Isn't this kimono thing all, like, red and white and cool? I dig it! ... But what occasion is it for?

103100.feeling4: You don't act the same towards everyone? Then how come whenever you look at me, your face is always so gentle... Why is that?
103100.propose: Even though being with my sisters is already a lot of fun, as long as you're with me, I feel like we'll have even more fun! So, let's continue getting along!
103100.detail: Wanna space out and stare at the clouds?
103100.upgrade: What's the point... of getting stronger anyway?
103100.home: Welcome back, Commander. There are some interesting-looking clouds in the sky today...
103100.mission_complete: Commander, why don't you let me take a nap as a reward instead...?
103100.feeling3: Commander... you're sure nice to everyone...
103100.unlock: I'm Vincennes of the New Orleans-class... Commander, don't you want to take me home?
103100.feeling2: Quincy is always busy helping other people, so she never has time to space out with me...
103100.touch: Commander... can you guess what I'm thinking right now?
103100.touch2: Woah?! Commander, what are you doing?!
103100.profile: I'm Vincennes, New Orleans-class heavy cruiser number 7. I've been to lots of places and given it my all in many battles... The last one I remember was at Savo Island...
103100.main: Because my sisters like to take care of everything for me, my primary responsibility is spacing out. |My sisters gave me way too many snacks... Commander, wanna help me out? |So bored... Commander, let's do something together... like spacing out...
103100.feeling5: Now I like to observe your expressions instead of watching the clouds... Commander, your face when you're having fun, when you're worried, when you're in a pinch, or when you're surprised... they're all so interesting...
103100.hp_warning: I... I can still keep fighting! Probably...
103100.expedition: The commission fleet's back... Looks like spacing out time is over...
103100.mail: Looks like there's new mail... but it's too far away... Don't wanna go...
103100.drop_descrip: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Vincennes, hull number CA-44.
103100.mission: Surely... it wouldn't hurt to skip a few of these missions...

301660.feeling4: It's gotten quite late... But I really enjoyed chatting with you! Say, don't your shoulders get stiff from sitting down all day? Would you like a massage?
301660.propose: Commander, I won't say anything indecent, but there's one thing I want to tell you... Umm... I'll always be there to support you. Your side is the place where I truly belong.
301660.detail: I feel a little sad when I see planes in the air... But it's okay, that's all in the past. What's more important is keeping my chin up and smiling. Right, Commander?
couple_encourage: Destroyer Division 8, let's all stick together now.
Asashio, I'm right by your side. Don't be scared.
301660.feeling1: Oh, Asashio? There there, there's nothing to be afraid of... You'll have to excuse me, I need to stay with Asashio.
301660.upgrade: Now it'll be easier for me to avoid getting hurt. Thank you, Commander.
301660.battle: Everyone, try to avoid getting hurt if you can...
301660.home: Stellar work, Commander. Would you like to rest your head in my lap?
301660.login: You don't find my appearance odd? I feel the best way to greet someone is with a smile!
301660.mission_complete: A mission has been completed. You did a great job, Commander!
301660.feeling3: Did you have another nightmare? Aww, relax, Commander, everything will be okay.
301660.unlock: Destroyer Arashio, here to join your fleet. I'll provide everyone with the support they need~
301660.feeling2: I'd like to get to know you, Commander. *Giggle*, what should we start with?
301660.touch: Mmh... I try not to think about why we all got separated. Besides, we got to reunite here, so let's instead live our lives happily ever after.
301660.touch2: Eeeeek! ... Is this truly necessary to become an adult?
301660.profile: I am Arashio, the fourth Asashio-class destroyer. I was part of Destroyer Division 8 along with Ooshio, Michishio, and of course Asashio. Lastly... I hope I can stay with everyone this time around.
301660.main: Asashio and I have always been together. Yup, we even sleep in the same bed. She's so quiet when she's sleeping.|We might not always be able to stick together, but we'd never leave anyone behind... That's why this place feels like home to me.|I've made you some tea. Take your time to savor it. By the way, is my tea-making ability to your liking?
301660.win_mvp: Why, I'm the MVP...? Hmm, this might not be so bad.
301660.feeling5: We're all to ourselves now. My heart's been thumping for some time now... Commander, could we huddle up next to each other, just for a little while?
301660.lose: There's no need to worry, we'll win the next time!
301660.hp_warning: You must remain calm in the face of danger. Don't worry about me.
301660.expedition: Commander, I believe the commission team has returned. Let us head over to receive them.
301660.mail: You've received mail. Shall we go see what it is, Commander?
301660.skill: I'll keep everyone out of harm's way.
301660.mission: New missions have appeared. I'll gladly help you with them, Commander.

201213.drop_descrip: Tada! We’re all wearing the same uniform! It’s super cute, isn’t it? Heehee, I’ll be wearing it the entire time I’m on duty, so make sure to visit!

101310.feeling4: If I always stay in my room then I won't get to see you much, Commander... Hmm, what should I do...
101310.propose: *Groans*... How long is this ceremony going to last... I want to go back and sleep... Don't you agree, Commander?
101310.detail: Zzzz... Oh, C-Commander? Are you gonna say that I've been slacking off too much and now I have to sortie?!
couple_encourage: Helena, keep an eye out for what's hidden under the water!
101310.feeling1: I'm never leaving my room... Never!
101310.battle: ... We came here to win... right?
101310.home: W-welcome back, Commander! ... Hey, listen, can I leave already?
101310.login: I'm different from you, Commander. I'd prefer to just stay here and not go anywhere else...
101310.mission_complete: Commander, since we're done for now, do you think I could...
101310.feeling3: C-Commander, if you're free, then how about coming to my room and playing some games...?
101310.unlock: I'm Nicholas, the first Fletcher-class ship to be launched... I'd rather stay at the base than head out to battle... You don't mind, right?
101310.feeling2: I'm not sleepy... I just can't open my eyes.
101310.profile: I'm Nicholas, DD-449... Although my hull number is at the bottom of the list, I was actually the first Fletcher-class to be commissioned and launched... I mainly provided fire support, and... I contributed to the sinking of Jintsuu and the rescue of Helena, but I don't have much else noteworthy to my name... If there is nothing else you want to know, can I go back?
101310.main: Sakura Empire torpedoes... that's scary stuff...|Commander, how about you learn from Helena and just leave me to my own devices?|I really don't feel like training... not at all...
101310.win_mvp: Guess I'm the MVP... That's unusual.
101310.feeling5: *Yawns*... Well, if I stay in your room, I can look at you and sleep at the same time, Commander...
101310.lose: I-I really should've never left the base...
101310.expedition: The commission team is back... I'm heading back now too...
101310.mail: We invented email for a reason...
101310.drop_descrip: Fletcher-class destroyer – Nicholas, Hull Number DD-449!
101310.mission: It's not like we HAVE to finish our missions... right?

307032.detail: I may be in the Morals Committee, but that doesn't mean I want to become a fusspot.
307032.login: I think Hiryuu is in her rebellious age... She won't wear the clothes I picked out for her, and she won't walk to school with me... As her sister, it's making me feel a little bummed out.
307032.unlock: I am Souryuu of the Morals Committee. Our goal is to maintain public decency, increase student motivation, and... *Ahem*! Anyway, please allow me to oversee the school's moral codes!
307032.touch: I've been talking to Hiryuu less, yet her mood hasn't improved at all... S-she's not going to run away from home, is she?!
307032.touch2: All planes, prepare for takeoff! No, wait, prepare to strike!
307032.main: Please don't joke like that. My disciplined, respectful, dependable, good-mannered, and very well-raised little sister would never end up as a dirty delinquent!|Hiryuu's in her rebellious age... *Sigh*... Perhaps it's best to leave her alone for a while...|I have my planes monitoring every nook and cranny of the school. I recommend you don't do anything that would oppose school conduct.
307032.expedition: She welcomed back the commission team, just like always... She is at the point of her life where she wants to spread her wings and be free...
307032.drop_descrip: I am Souryuu of the Morals Committee. Our goal is to maintain public decency, increase student motivation, and... *Ahem*! Anyway, please allow me to oversee the school's moral codes!

301150.feeling4: Getting pranked by me is a lucky thing on its own, you dunce♪ Although I do like that about you.
301150.propose: You just can't be left alone, Commander... Worry not, I will stay by your side and take care of you forever♪
301150.detail: Stupid Commander! Look at me again and I'll bite you!
couple_encourage: Monkey Corps {namecode:15}, attack!
Hm? I'm not a monkey?
301150.feeling1: I curse you with bad luck! You idiot!
301150.upgrade: Mhm, making me stronger is a smart decision.
301150.battle: Let's give a warm welcome to our foolish enemies~!
301150.login: Commander! You're late! Go get ready~ I've been waiting for you.
301150.mission_complete: *Tsk*... If it weren't for the rewards then who'd bother with these jobs...
301150.feeling3: Luck comes when you least expect it, you know? For example, like this! (Shigure jumps) ... Commander, maybe you caught a glimpse of my underwear just now~?
301150.unlock: I'm {namecode:17}, a {namecode:15}-class destroyer. I don't wanna brag, but I've got the Goddess of Luck watching over me~ Heheh, it's about time people acknowledged that luck is also a part of one's strength♪
301150.feeling2: You want good luck? It's not something you can just get.
301150.touch: Stop touching me! Don't blame me if something blows up!
301150.touch2: Commander, let's play a game. I'll give you 5 minutes and if you haven't been caught by the police at that point then I'll withdraw my report~
301150.profile: I'm {namecode:17}, ship number 2 of the {namecode:15}-class. I worked pretty hard in the First Fleet before I was reassigned to the Second Fleet and participated in the fated Battle of Leyte Gulf... I was the sole survivor, but I'll never forget the bravery everyone showed in that battle... {namecode:79}... {namecode:78}... how I miss you...
301150.main: It's so peaceful... How about we play a game of luck?|The gods seem to really love me, so hurry up and shower me with compliments♪|You don't look too good. How about a torpedo to cheer you up?
301150.win_mvp: That was a good fight, considering how they suck♪
301150.feeling5: Heheh, silly Commander, you can rely on me as much as you want. I'll do anything you want~! As long as you love me like this, I'm yours♪
301150.lose: N... Not bad... You'd better remember this!
301150.hp_warning: We're gonna lose? That can't be~!
301150.expedition: Hm? Guess it's time. Heheh, I don't even need to actually head out, for as long as I'm in the fleet, bountiful rewards are guaranteed♪
301150.mail: I brought you your mail~ Now guess which hand I'm holding it with♪
301150.skill: I am {namecode:17} of Sasebo! Watch closely!
301150.mission: Huh? Work? Geez, it's ALWAYS about work...

205050.feeling4: Commander, so you're learning how to cook? Hmm, colour me impressed. I look forward to trying the dish that you're making for me.
205050.propose: They say that "the quickest way to one's heart is through their stomach," but you've managed to win over both at once. Commander, shall we share all our meals together from now on?
205050.detail: My standing within the Royal Family? Hmm... If I had to draw a comparison, I'd say "Knight Commander" would be the most fitting... Hahaha...
couple_encourage: Wales, you'd better not suddenly leave me again!
York, let us shatter our enemies together.
205050.feeling1: I favor those of character, and those who can cook. Commander, you are neither.
205050.upgrade: Hmm... I suddenly feel like having a lavish feast.
205050.battle: Let us go forth and plant our banners!
205050.home: Commander, did you thoroughly enjoy the battle?
205050.login: Commander, did you already partake of supper?
205050.mission_complete: Supper tastes best after the day's missions are all complete. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?
205050.feeling3: How's that, commander? Are you impressed by my cooking abilities? Here, have as much you desire. Seeing you enjoy my food pleases me.
205050.unlock: So this is my new battlefield. Ahh, how I've long awaited this... By the way, are you my commander? You are in the presence of King George V – do use me well.
205050.feeling2: By the way, Commander, are you a good cook? Hmm? Despite my appearances, I've spent many hours honing my skills to sate my own appetite.
205050.touch: Why do I have a mountain of snacks before me? Isn't it obvious? One cannot move on an empty stomach.
205050.touch2: Ohh? I wasn't aware that you possessed such audacity, Commander.
205050.profile: The nameship of the King George V-class battleships is none other than me. I served as flagship for my country, leading the fleet into numerous battles including the fateful encounter with Bismarck. After getting a brief taste of that thrill, I have been craving to cross swords with her once again... But I digress - is there anything else you'd like to know about me?
205050.main: Commander, this fleet only functions because of you. Don't get sloppy on us. |Wales and Yorkie? It's a bit of a shame that they don't act more like cute little sisters, but I am glad that they have strong personalities. |In my eyes, there is no leader in this world more worthy of my loyalty than Her Majesty, Queen Elizabeth. Does that make sense to you, Commander? |The Royals' cuisine is all bland? Hogwash. That's just an unfortunate stereotype.
205050.win_mvp: Make no mistakes. I shall ensure both victory and the safety of all my comrades.
205050.feeling5: My greatest hobbies in life are food and fighting. While I am more than capable of fighting alone, dining by myself is quite difficult and lonesome. To be able to find someone who can share both of these things with me is truly a joyous thing.
205050.lose: Do not be demoralized. Neither victory nor defeat are decided by a single battle.
205050.expedition: There's some commotion by the port...? Oh, it seems to just be the commission team returning.
205050.mail: A letter, huh? Now then, is this a challenge, or a love letter?
205050.drop_descrip: King George V-class battleship – King George V.
205050.skill: The glory of the sun that never sets shall not fade!
205050.mission: New missions, eh? It would be ideal if we got something a bit more challenging.

201214.detail: ♪~What kind of lunch should I pack today~
201214.home: Good job out there! Hey, Zed! Save the report for later, and let Commander rest first~!
201214.login: Welcome back, Commander! Don't I look super cool today? Ehehe~♪
201214.touch2: Jeez, no lewding! How many times do I have to repeat myself?
201214.main: Little Bel and Belfast somehow feel like... mother and child?|Which club should I join...? Cooking club? Knitting club? Nnnh... I just can't decide!|Juneau, are you going shopping with the others later? Aww, let me come too!

301151.detail: You thought I wouldn't bite you just because you complimented my swimsuit? *Hiss*
301151.battle: Oxygen torpedoes: prepare for simultaneous launch!
301151.unlock: Stupid Commander, I'm not a damn submarine! Do you wanna get hit in the face with an oxygen torpedo?
301151.touch: Don't touch my ears, I'm ticklish there!
301151.touch2: Wahh! You scared off the fish I'd caught with my tail! Commander, you idiot!
301151.main: I'll just absorb some seawater with my tail, and then... Pow! Oh dear~ You're totally drenched, Commander~|{namecode:79} gave me this little rose! If you thought I'd give it to you, think again!|{namecode:79}, just ignore that stupid Commander, come play beach volleyball with me!
301151.drop_descrip: Stupid Commander, I'm not a damn submarine! Do you wanna get hit in the face with an oxygen torpedo?

105019.detail: Commander, want to go horseback riding together? It doesn't matter if you don't know how, just hang on to my waist!
105019.battle: As long I am here, there's no way we can lose!
105019.home: Young'un, want to experience a bridal carry for yourself?
105019.login: Nevada, always ready for your orders!
105019.unlock: Heh, with this, I won't be outperformed by those fancy greenhorn battleships. Young'un, from now on, just leave everything to Nevada here!
105019.touch: So, you fancy a dance with the devil? As you can see, I'm ready to up the ante. Young'un, what are you going to wager?
105019.touch2: Commander, can I... change my wager?
105019.main: That Oklahoma, she's ain't so wet behind the ears anymore. Soon she's gonna be all independent. |Though fighting can't eliminate every problem in the world, it certainly can eliminate most of those who would cause problems. |Commander, I've got your back, so you can keep charging forward!
105019.win_mvp: Your offenses are weak, your defenses are feeble! Your reactions are slow, and your movements are sluggish! Come back when you've trained more!
105019.drop_descrip: Heh, with this, I won't be outperformed by those fancy greenhorn battleships. Young'un, from now on, just leave everything to Nevada here!

301152.drop_descrip: Oh my. Commander, you must be pretty lucky to bump into me here, hehe~ Since you're here, you can have the privilege of being my escort tonight. Now, be grateful~♪

103101.detail: I like dreaming. There are no missions... or fighting... or sorrows...
103101.touch: Astoria... don't shake me please... Zzz...
103101.touch2: Zzz... Ahh... donut monster... not right there... Commander, save meee... zzz....
103101.main: In my dreams, everyone can play together happily... |Zzz... the donut monster... is gonna catch me... zzz... |Mr. Meowy got so big... zzz...

202110.feeling4: Phew... I've finally found you, Commander. Actually... Aaaah-- Who the heck! Who left the banana peel here!
202110.propose: Hmhm, I'm fine with sharing some of my money-luck with you. ...The gold? No! That belongs to the Belfast Foundation!
202110.detail: I'm not going to give these to you no matter how much you stare at me.
couple_encourage: I didn't think I'd get a chance to fight with Belfast!
Sheffy, I'm counting on you!
Newcastle, let's talk about Bel sometime!
Echo, dear, do take care!
202110.feeling1: Since it's Commander, I have to be even more careful... *stare*...
202110.headtouch: Thanks! I'm feeling a bit more energized.
202110.upgrade: It seems like I've become luckier!
202110.battle: Wh-Wh-What to do?? First let's retre... I mean, intercept them!
202110.home: I made cookies! Please have a taste... They taste the same as Bel's? Well, we're sisters, after all!
202110.login: Ah! I'm not doing anything weird! I'm just transporting gold bars into the room!
202110.mission_complete: I seem to have forgotten about something... Well, whatever!
202110.feeling3: I've been lectured by Bel again... Forgetting to lock doors when going out, and turning off the tap... What the heck! She's totally not like a little sister!
202110.unlock: This is my turn, you might say! I am 'her' older sister, Edinburgh! In a sense, I am the 'most accomplished' light cruiser!
202110.feeling2: Everything goes well when 'that girl' does it, so it should be fine if I'm a little clumsy, shouldn't it?
202110.touch: Hey!! Don't touch that! It's gonna fall!
202110.touch2: Commander, a lady would never hide her gold bars there!
202110.profile: I am the lead ship of Edinburgh class of the Royal Navy. Sometimes it is stressful having an overly capable little sister... I took part in the pursuit of Bismarck and Scharnhorst, as well as many patrol missions in Atlantic, North sea and Mediterranean. In the end, I sunk with all my gold due to Ironblood torpedoes...
202110.main: I want to be as elegant as Hood but, well...|Eeeh! ...Bel, where are you? I forgot my keys again...|Hmhmm~ Even Scharnhorst had to turn tail and run away when she saw me!
202110.win_mvp: Crushing the enemies with elegance... That, is the elegant Ediburgh of the royal family!
202110.feeling5: Commander, want to have a walk together before it gets dark? Yes, don't worry. The lights were switched off, and the windows were shut. Everything's OK! ... W-what? ...Wh-Where did the keys go?!
202110.hp_warning: Gh... At least let me protect the gold...!
202110.expedition: When it comes to military commissions, I'm a pro!
202110.mail: Commander, there's a new ma... Wh-What? Where's the mail? Where did I leave it... ??
202110.drop_descrip: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Edinburgh, Hull number 16!
202110.skill: No matter how thick the armor is, it can't win against the power of gold!
202110.mission: You have to finish your missions properly!

101311.detail: I need to control my sleepiness when treating people on the battlefield. *Yawn*... I'm working on it...
101311.login: Medical staff are valuable and should stay in the back... Frontline duty? That stuff is Vestal's job...
101311.unlock: I love doing relief missions as a nurse... I don't need to go outside or take part in any training, I just need to look after injured people... What about treating them? No worries, they just need to rest and they'll get better.
101311.touch2: You must have suddenly gotten very sick...
101311.main: This syringe contains Radford's sweetie candy... It won't hurt... You won't feel a thing...|You don't feel so good, do you? Don't worry about me, just stay in bed and rest...|Some of my patients can be pretty problematic... That's when I just dump them on Vestal...
101311.drop_descrip: I love doing relief missions as a nurse... I don't need to go outside or take part in any training, I just need to look after injured people... What about treating them? No worries, they just need to rest and they'll get better.

301410.feeling4: Always telling me to wear my clothes... you're just like my mom... But I still like you, Commander. Almost as much as I like taiyaki... Okay, Commander, help me get dressed.
301410.propose: A promise...? Does that mean you'll help me get dressed? I don't really get it... I should really do it on my own...? Commander, you're weird... I'm fine with you helping me get dressed, I told you before...
301410.detail: Commander, I still have lots of taiyaki, so I'm fine.
301410.feeling1: Ahh~ *Nom* (Mikazuki doesn't seem to notice you.)
301410.upgrade: I ate... too much taiyaki... I'm stuffed...
301410.battle: That's the enemy... can we eat them?
301410.home: Ah... Commander, want some too? I've got more.
301410.mission_complete: Commander, does the reward include any taiyaki?
301410.feeling3: Clothes are so annoying... I hate getting dressed... I just want to eat taiyaki...
301410.unlock: Aahh... Hm? Hmm? Co... main... der? I'm Mikazuki. Want some taiyaki? You can have half of mine.
301410.feeling2: Commander, want to eat some taiyaki with me?
301410.touch: Commander, want some? I don't mind sharing.
301410.profile: I'm Mikazuki. I've got a lot of little and big sisters. We're all friends. I'm really good at escort and transport missions! Oh, and I love taiyaki! Do you want some too, Commander?
301410.main: I'm full... and sleepy... Commander, gimme a hug~|I like taiyaki filled with bean paste even in their tail fins.|Taiyaki looks like a fish... Fish live in the sea! Hm... the sea is on Earth! Earth is in space! Mm... so tasty!
301410.win_mvp: Isn't it about time for a snack?
301410.feeling5: "Only really close people should help each other get dressed"? Are we not close, Commander? I love you, Commander. Do you not like me?
301410.expedition: Commander, I'm heading out to welcome back the commission team! They promised they'd buy me some taiyaki!
301410.mail: Commander, what's this package for? Can I pack up my taiyaki?
301410.skill: You're not getting any of my taiyaki!

202111.detail: Hmm...this Alchemy is really mysterious, but once I mastered it, then Belfast’s trust fund will...
202111.battle: Tsk tsk, we don’t need her here. In any case, Belfast will always be by my side. Fleet, prepare for interception!
202111.login: This pendant is so cute, right?! I copied from that girl. Let's call her “Belfast”.
202111.unlock: Why doesn't she have to go to school with me...she says she’s a maid for the Queen? Well, me too! You can be a maid and school girl at the same time...tsk tsk---
202111.touch: Commander, wanna try my snacks? Ah~~
202111.touch2: Commander! C’mon out now will ya. I can't study this way…
202111.main: Belfast, wake me up before you wake up Elizabeth. Otherwise, she will criticize me for getting up late again... |Do I look like a child who’s so easily bullied? Hehe, but as elegant as I am, no wonder I am called a fairy. |Victory, let me rub your cheeks again, doing so always brings me good luck.
202111.expedition: Belfast, before you go to greet the girls returning from commission, could you brush my hair? It's a mess...
202111.drop_descrip: Why doesn't she have to go to school with me...she says she’s a maid for the Queen? Well, me too! You can be a maid and school girl at the same time...tsk tsk---

308060.feeling4: Ever since I sank Yorktown in the war, I've been getting occasional angry glances from Hammann... B-but aren't we all friends now? I mean hey, even Yorktown herself says she's let go of it!
308060.propose: F-finally you decided to open up to me... You did right to choose me... Ehehe... W-what's that mean?! YOU'RE the one not being honest here!
308060.detail: You want something from me, don't you? ... Well, even if you don't...
couple_encourage: Hammann, we're all friends now, you know!
308060.feeling1: I hate scum like you. Don't come near me ever again.
308060.upgrade: All right! I've become even stronger!
308060.battle: Let's go! We're hunting big game!
308060.home: Nicely done. Now sit down and relax.

Repulse, though this might sound quaint coming from me, you should try to concentrate a little more.
