10100081.drop_descrip: Commander, are you having a good time? Ehehe, I certainly am. It's not often that we get to relax like this. Why don't we head out and enjoy the breeze?

101380.feeling4: Recently, I had a strange dream. I dreamt that I wasn't on the battlefield, but instead taking a walk along the port, hand-in-hand with someone close to me... Wh-what's so funny?
101380.propose: S-so this is a promise ring... Really, I never could have imagined that this would happen to me... However, I'm truly, truly happy, from the bottom of my heart. Is this... the "love" that my sisters were talking about? Hey... don't laugh!
101380.detail: Just what are you looking at? You ought to hurry up and return to your post.
101380.feeling1: The incompetent will be weeded out by time. You are no exception.
101380.headtouch: What is... the meaning of this?
101380.upgrade: Strengthening combat effectiveness is also an important link when it comes to battle.
101380.home: I see you've returned at the scheduled time, Commander. However, you can't afford to take it easy just yet.
101380.login: Being punctual is a good habit to have, so please keep it up.
101380.mission_complete: Mission complete. However, your work doesn't end there.
101380.feeling3: "What do I plan to do after the war is over?" Hmm... I've never given this much thought, nor have I wanted to. However, why did you bring it up all of a sudden?
101380.unlock: I am the Fletcher-class destroyer, Kimberly. From today onward, I will be one of your subordinates. Pleased to meet you.
101380.feeling2: As long as we keep on winning, will we be able to bring an end to the war? Rather than searching for the answer to that question, it would be more practical to focus on winning the battles ahead of us.
101380.touch2: Do you want to pay a visit to the court martial?
101380.profile: I am the Fletcher-class destroyer Kimberly. I am normally tasked with escort and anti-submarine duties, so should the need arise, please do not hesitate to deploy me.
101380.main: If you are tired, please take a break. If you were to collapse, the command chain would follow suit. |For me, no matter where I am, or what I am called, I will continue to fight on as long as I live. |I was born for battle and died for peace. Other than this fact, I won't dwell on anything else.
101380.win_mvp: This is a fine example of tactical synergy. Let's keep it up.
101380.feeling5: After discussing things with my sisters a bit, I realized that if the war actually ended, I wouldn't know how to do anything else... Eh, you'd stay with me and teach me yourself... so there would be no problem? E-ehhh?
101380.skill: Let's put this needless battle to an end!
101380.mission: As a commander, it is only fitting that you complete these tasks.

305010.feeling4: Kagura? That is a dance dedicated to the gods... Ah, why don't I perform just for you, milord? I would be embarrassed if others found out, so please keep it a secret between us, all right?
305010.propose: May our love last as long as the Great Pines in Takasago and the eternal Tsubaki. May we bring glory to our family, our name heard across the land. These words are said with my highest respect. With this, Milord, you and I become one. Though I may be inexperienced, let us care for and love each other for the rest of eternity.
305010.detail: Milord, shall we have tea together?
305010.feeling1: Milord, might you be the reincarnation of a god of calamity?
305010.upgrade: Now, I can be of greater service to Milord.
305010.battle: Milord, those who stand in your way shall find no mercy by my hand.
305010.home: You've worked hard, Milord. Why don't you come to me and take a rest?
305010.login: Welcome back, Milord. Would you like to have your fortune told?
305010.mission_complete: Milord, not claiming your rewards is a bad habit.
305010.feeling3: Milord, you seem exhausted as of late. Too much work is bad for your health. Please come with me, and allow me to purify you of your fatigue.
305010.unlock: It is an honor to meet you. Milord, you must be the commander. I, {namecode:78}, have been waiting a long time for you. Surely, this is also the guidance of the gods. From now on, please allow me to serve youI
305010.feeling2: Milord, are you interested in the eight million gods of the Sakura Empire? It is fine if you aren't... I shall offer them your share of prayers.
305010.touch: Milord, please rest your head here and allow me to clean your ears.
305010.profile: I am the Sakura Empire's first super-dreadnought, {namecode:78}. In order to cleanse ourselves of the misfortune we were born with, my sister and I offer prayers to the gods every day. We will do whatever it takes to prevent another tragedy like Leyte Gulf from befalling us again. Milord, we would be most grateful should you lend us your aid.
305010.main: I believe that we can change our misfortunes, as long as we work hard and pray...|I'll be happy as long as {namecode:79} has a chance to grow up.|My main gun specializes in heavy firepower, but is enough to shake my entire body! It can cause me some trouble, every now and then...
305010.win_mvp: May thy lost souls return home in peace.
305010.feeling5: Milord, did you know that although a miko of the Sakura Empire must dedicate herself to the gods, she is not actually forbidden from romance? As a matter of fact, she is encouraged to find a husband in order to pass down traditions. Milord, what do you think about me?
305010.lose: Oh no... has my ammunition storage been cursed again?
305010.expedition: Milord, your girls have returned from commission. Shall we welcome them back together?
305010.mail: You have a new letter, milord. Please give it a look.
305010.mission: Milord, a new mission is available. Please take a look.

10100080.feeling4: I have some free time tonight, so I would be glad to help you with work. Afterwards, I'd like you to give me... U-um... forget I said anything.
10100080.propose: I've finally noticed my true feelings. Even if the battle here ends and I have to return to my original world... Commander, I... I want to hear what you have to say.
10100080.detail: It seems like someone has been captivated by my beauty.
couple_encourage: I'm so envious, White Heart. Your hitbox is so small.
Alright, let's go！
10100080.feeling1: I have nothing to say to you.
10100080.upgrade: My beauty has been sculpted even more.
10100080.battle: Let's deal with our enemies full-force from the start.
10100080.login: You sure took your time. Black tea is best enjoyed hot, you know?
10100080.mission_complete: What a tease... I want to see the rewards.
10100080.feeling3: Haven't you been relying on me a bit too much recently? No, it doesn't bother me... but if this continues, one can't help but to be concerned about your abilities as a commander.
10100080.unlock: I am the CPU of Leanbox, Green Heart. No matter who the enemy is, I will not hold back. Are you ready?
10100080.feeling2: If you are fine with me, you can ask me for advice at any time.
10100080.touch: This processing unit can't be taken off, you know. Ehehe, just kidding.
10100080.touch2: It's not a good idea to keep playing these distasteful pranks.
10100080.profile: I am the CPU of Leanbox, Green Heart. I have come from the world of Gamindustri. There's no need to be shy, you can come as close as you'd like.
10100080.main: Size is justice, don't you agree?|... Oh dear, my apologies. I was just thinking about the next guild battle.|Shall we have some tea?
10100080.win_mvp: Enemies like these are not enough to be my opponent.
10100080.feeling5: Commander...? Are you bogged down with work again? ... Guess it can't be helped. Let's go on a date after you're done. I'll make some special red tea for you.
10100080.lose: To think I would make such a mistake... I won't lose next time.
10100080.hp_warning: I won't let you off the hook so easily!
10100080.expedition: It appears that a commission has been completed. You should thank your girls for their hard work.
10100080.drop_descrip: I am the CPU of Leanbox, Green Heart. No matter who the enemy is, I will not hold back. Are you ready?
10100080.skill: I'll end you in an instant!
10100080.mission: If you require my assistance at any time, just let me know.

205062.mission_complete: You're still hammering away at those missions even during the New Year? You sure are hard-working, Commander.
205062.unlock: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?
205062.touch: Why are you staring at me? I'm... suave? Hehe, I suppose I should take that as a compliment.
205062.main: Commander, are you cold? You can borrow my coat if you'd like. Ah, don't worry about me, I'm fine. |Learning about the customs of the other nations is quite interesting. I feel like I get along better with the Sakura girls now. |I miss my black tea a bit, but I suppose "when in Rome, do as the Romans do." I guess I should fully enjoy the culture of the Sakura Empire.
205062.feeling5: To be able to experience a new culture like this, and spend the New Year peacefully... is like a dream come true. Commander, it's all thanks to you. As expected of the one I chose.
205062.expedition: Since it's the New Year, it would be sad if there was nobody to greet the girls returning from commissions. Don't you think so, Commander?
205062.drop_descrip: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?

202121.detail: The outfits of the Dragon Empery do have a certain charm. Perhaps I can give them a little recommendation to the rest of the maid team. What do you think?
202121.home: I baked this pastry for a certain Master who is so absorbed in work to the point of forgetting to eat. Please enjoy it.
202121.login: Welcome back, Master. I specially procured some different teas from the Dragon Empery. Which one would you like to try first?
202121.unlock: Hehe... Master, why are you so stunned from seeing me? I thought you perhaps wanted to see me in a qipao... was I mistaken?
202121.touch: Despite the fact that it is a holiday, I am still ready to sortie.
202121.touch2: I see, Master. The biggest drawback of this qipao is its ability to rob you of your self-control.
202121.main: A variety of culinary techniques and seasoning methods... the food culture of the Dragon Empery is truly eye-opening. |It's customary in the Dragon Empery for everyone to get together on New Year's to have a banquet? Ahh, so many people to serve... my maid's soul is trembling! |Only a few girls from the Dragon Empery have joined our fleet. Because of that, I can't afford to let them feel lonely.
202121.feeling5: Did you know, Master... all I can do for you is to learn from the cultures of the other camps in order to provide you with better service. But all this pales in comparison to all that you do for us on a daily basis, yet you take yourself for granted... What a lovable but also hateable person.
202121.expedition: Master, what do you think about handing some red envelopes to the hardworking girls still out on commissions?
202121.drop_descrip: Hehe... Master, why are you so stunned from seeing me? I thought you perhaps wanted to see me in a qipao... was I mistaken?

305011.detail: Commander, would you like to accompany me for a stroll?
305011.login: Commander, your luck has been very good recently. Surely, it must be because the gods are also happy.
305011.unlock: Yamashiro's always saying that I would look better in more trendy clothing, so she went out of her way to pick this out for me. Jeez, that girl... Oh, Commander? Does this outfit... suit me?
305011.touch: Commander, please accept this present. It was prepared specially for you.
305011.touch2: Commander? Even though it's a holiday, this kind of thing is...!
305011.main: Commander, if it begins to snow, please take cover under my umbrella~ |Perhaps I should return the favor and make something for Yamashiro to wear... Commander, what kind of outfit do you think is best? |The happiness we can enjoy right now is surely a blessing from the gods... No, it's because of your hard work, Commander.
305011.drop_descrip: Yamashiro's always saying that I would look better in more trendy clothing, so she went out of her way to pick this out for me. Jeez, that girl... Oh, Commander? Does this outfit... suit me?

10100071.drop_descrip: B-bastard! Where are you looking? I bet you're thinking I look like a kid! Eh....? They're just right? If Commander says something like that... I don't know how to react...

900043.feeling4: Those senpai are so sly! Just when I was about to overtake them, they went somewhere I could never reach! How unfair!
900043.propose: The melody of my flute is like a flowing river, requiring an inspiration that usually can only be found atop a mountain. Just being by your side, however, inspires me even more.
900043.detail: The melody of my flute is a requiem for the dead. Shall I play it for you?
couple_encourage: {namecode:96}, give it your all! I'll cover you!
Do you see my true power, {namecode:91}?
This time... I'll prove to you how powerful I really am!
I won't be able to protect you if you stray too far!
Where is the Queen of the Docks heading to?
900043.feeling1: I think I just saw a future in which you were cut down by {namecode:91}, Commander.
900043.battle: The perfected aircraft carrier, {namecode:95}, setting sail!
900043.home: The girls have returned safely to port, just like the Fifth Carrier Division always does.
900043.login: Intelligence is said to be a woman’s virtue, but that often puts me at odds with those senpai of mine. How troublesome~
900043.mission_complete: We’re not going to carry out our plans of attrition warfare? Tch~
900043.feeling3: Do I hold a grudge against the First and Second Carrier Divisions? Of course~ For them to leave us behind like that, wouldn’t anyone complain in that situation?
900043.unlock: As the flagship of the Fifth Carrier Division, I, Shoukaku, shall do my best to become as good as those esteemed senpai in the First Carrier Division, or something... *giggles* That was on purpose~
900043.feeling2: My sister {namecode:96} and I held on for two years during the darkest of times. If only our senpai could have worked a little bit harder.
900043.touch: Commander, would you like to hear me play my flute?
900043.touch2: Commander, come and indulge yourself in {namecode:95}'s tenderness.
900043.profile: I am {namecode:95}, the flagship of the Fifth Carrier Division. Because my super smart senpai went and got themselves all killed, I had to carry the flag of the Sakura Empire’s carrier divisions. Though I was more accomplished than them, for whatever reason, I was always considered weaker. Maybe it was due to my "lack of grace and speed" during my final moments... With that said, allow me to reintroduce myself. I am Shoukaku, the punching bag of the Sakura Empire. Please take care of me from now on~
900043.main: To always be dealing with those senpai from the First Carrier Division... Commander, you must have a really strong liver.|Though our relationship was once one of victim and perpetrator, I look forward to working with you, Lexington.|{namecode:96}, if you keep causing trouble for our Eagle Union colleagues, you’ll only get tempura for dinner tonight~
900043.win_mvp: The Glory of the 5th Carrier Divison is here! *giggles*
900043.feeling5: Commander, could you lend me your shoulder? Sometimes, even I want to simply clear my mind and rest. When I get like that, can I depend on you to be by my side?
900043.lose: Hiryuu-senpai may be willing to fight until the bitter end, but... that’s not my style. What a shame~
900043.hp_warning: Pump water to the other side! Hurry!
900043.expedition: This is all required to carry out the Circle Five Plan.
900043.mail: We’ve got mail from HQ, they told us to carry out the Decisive Battle Doctrine. Heh, just kidding~!
900043.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:95}.
900043.skill: This is the privilege of being the elder sister!
900043.mission: Let me take a look the mission... It’s not the Coral Sea? That’s too bad~

108030.feeling4: I've been feeling sick lately... I can't fight with the same flair as I used to when I think about you... That's it, it's gotta be your fault, Commander! ... Actually, I'm not so sure...
108030.propose: Whuah! Hold on a sec! Why are you hugging me out of the blue?! What are you doing?! You call this "weight training"? A-are you kidding me?! Everyone's staring at us, so let go already!
108030.detail: I'm no fish out of water that can't fight on the surface! It's no problem for me!
couple_encourage: Let's see who of us is the strongest!
108030.home: Commander, if you need the expertise of a submarine, just call on Cavalla!
108030.login: Morning! You're right on time today!
108030.mission_complete: Ooh! A boatload of rewards! Let's treat ourselves, Commander!
108030.feeling3: Sometimes, courage alone isn't enough... And that's when I need your strength, Commander! With your instructions, we can overcome anything!
108030.unlock: I'm Cavalla, the Eagle Union submarine! I'll make this fleet famous through glorious victories, so just you wait, Commander!
108030.feeling2: Fear of failure can be overcome by showing your courage!
108030.touch: Ahahaha~! Stop! Ahahah~! That tickles– ahahaha!
108030.profile: I was given a golden opportunity during my maiden voyage and sank a carrier! ... It was a pretty risky move, and it wasn't easy! But in the end, I came out on top! If you wanna hear the whole story, just ask!
108030.main: Could we make submarines stronger? By, for example... giving them stronger, better weapons or something?|It's so boring to just sit here and twiddle my thumbs... Give me something to do, Commander!|Whew! The breeze feels almost as good on land as it does at sea!
108030.win_mvp: You can thank Cavalla for this victory! Hehehe~
108030.feeling5: I had a dream where you carried me and walked around the port... It was really weird! But for some strange reason, it makes me feel happy... I wonder why...
108030.lose: Bah... This happened just cause the sea is so salty...
108030.hp_warning: I won't give up, no matter how bad it gets!
108030.expedition: The commission team has returned safely!
108030.mail: A new message has arrived! Wonder if it's from one of my submarine friends!
108030.drop_descrip: Gato-class submarine – Cavalla, Hull Number SS-244.
108030.skill: I've been waiting for this chance!
108030.mission: Do we get a boatload of rewards if we do these missions?

107071.detail: It's a party, you gotta eat a lot! What if you eat too much? "No problem, just work out and sweat it off later!" How's my Enty impression?
107071.login: Heyyy♪ Commander, I'm looking pretty hot tonight, huh?
107071.unlock: Congratulations! You did it, Commander! Now let's pop the champagne and celebrate! It's party time!
107071.touch: Is this dress gonna make you fall in love with me all over again? Ahahaha!
107071.touch2: Turns out I'm pretty different from my sisters, huh...?
107071.main: This one's Enty's, this one's Yorktown's, this one's Northampton's, this one's... oh, it's yours, Commander! Exactly one bottle. Pretty nice, huh?|So I have to dress up like this for the party? Aren't you worried I'm gonna be a fish out of water in there?|I'm not expecting anyone to call me the belle of the ball tonight. Not while everyone else is dressed up all pretty-like. What? You think I give up too easily?
107071.drop_descrip: Congratulations! You did it, Commander! Now let's pop the champagne and celebrate! It's party time!

102020.feeling4: You've been taking it pretty easy recently, Commander... *Sigh*... I guess some of the blame is mine to share... It's hard to be strict with someone I like...
102020.propose: To receive something so precious from a student... I should be ashamed to call myself a professional mentor... But you make me...
102020.detail: Make sure you ask me any questions if you're lost before we head out!
102020.upgrade: Now I can properly mentor you, Commander.
102020.battle: Please pay attention, everyone! This is a good chance to get some real combat experience~
102020.login: Hello, Commander. I've been waiting for you. Oh my, look at the time! Shouldn't we start the training now?
102020.mission_complete: Please don't forget to claim your mission rewards.
102020.feeling3: You want to know more about me? Hmm... you may be the first person to treat me like an equal. I'm happy about that, I suppose.
102020.unlock: I'm Raleigh, the Omaha-class light cruiser. Please sign this contract here... There we go. I'm hoping we'll make a good team from now on, Commander.
102020.feeling2: Commander, mature people like you need to pay attention on the job.
102020.touch: Please don't tug me like that... I'm not a kid!
102020.touch2: I'm not immune to getting angry, you know... Co-man-der!
102020.profile: I'm the training officer of the Omaha-class fleet - Raleigh. I'm going to be very strict with anyone who won't listen to what I say!
102020.main: Shall we begin our training, Commander?|For a beginner, every bit of training is very important~!|My name is Raleigh, not... that! Also, don't forget the "Ms."!
102020.win_mvp: You can't use the same trick on me twice!
102020.feeling5: You're calling me 'professor' in such an... interesting way when we're alone. Are you expecting to receive private lessons? You're just like a little kid, Commander...
102020.lose: Phew... That was close... I nearly...
102020.expedition: It's almost time, Commander. I'll go ahead and welcome the girls back from their commission.
102020.mail: Your mail has been sorted. Remember to read your messages thoroughly, please!
102020.drop_descrip: Omaha-class light cruiser – Raleigh, Hull Number CL-7!
102020.skill: Let me show you some textbook maneuvers.
102020.mission: Commander, please don't forget about your unfinished missions!

101061.unlock: I much rather cheer for my Commander than go to class...but no matter where I go, I will definitely give it my all! Commander, wait for me to come back as the top student of this school year.
101061.touch: These courses are too hard...Commander, can you tutor me?
101061.main: When you are overwhelmed by all this learning, go for a jog to relax yourself! If you're struggling with the material, then find a tutor. If that doesn't work, get special training...nothing can’t be solved through special training! The Commander has always been the best in my heart, so I have to be in his heart, too!
101061.drop_descrip: I much rather cheer for my Commander than go to class...but no matter where I go, I will definitely give it my all! Commander, wait for me to come back as the top student of this school year.

201099.unlock: Cute? Pretty? Is that all? Can't you expand your vocabulary a little? Jeez... Commander, you really should learn to whisper sweet nothings into my ear!
201099.touch: Commander, are you scared? Since there's no helping it, you can hold onto my hand.
201099.touch2: Stupid Commander! The standard for maturity isn't one's size!
201099.main: O-of course! As a full-fledged lady, you can trust me with anything! |Shouldn't you give a cute lady like me some preferential treatment? |Comet, dump that stupid commander and let me be your manager!
201099.drop_descrip: Cute? Pretty? Is that all? Can't you expand your vocabulary a little? Jeez... Commander, you really should learn to whisper sweet nothings into my ear!

900046.feeling4: Being able to see everyone's smiles at the banquet makes all the hard work and preparation worth it.
900046.propose: So this means... "We'll always be forever?" Thank you very much. I'll gladly accept it - however... If anything was to happen to us, I hope that you would consider yourself first...
900046.detail: Hehe~ Which do you prefer: matcha, or black tea?
couple_encourage: Are you still waiting for your sister?
900046.upgrade: Today's breeze feels more pleasant than usual.
900046.battle: Hehe, shall we go enjoy the festivities?
900046.home: Welcome back. The tea has just been brewed to the right temperature.
900046.login: There is nothing more relaxing than a banquet following a battle... By the way, Commander, I'm free after this...
900046.mission_complete: Hehe, shall we celebrate by holding a banquet tonight?
900046.feeling3: That Kirishima... She's actually quite the popular one...
900046.unlock: I am the Imperial Ship Hiei, second of the Kongou-class, reporting for duty. Commander, where shall we go next?
900046.feeling2: Ehehe~ Commander, is there something on your mind?
900046.touch: I can take you anywhere the ocean reaches.
900046.touch2: Hehe. Commander, have you not gotten enough sleep yet?
900046.profile: I am Hiei, the first Kongou-class battleship born in the Land of the Rising Sun. As an Imperial Ship, I witnessed the growth of our mighty fleet, and led our forces into the Battle of the Solomon Sea. Commander, have you finished your preparations? The banquet is about to begin.
900046.main: *Sigh*... Whenever Kirishima comes to a banquet, all those kids that tag along with her usually end up making a mess of things... |When it comes to warfare, wisdom and courage are equally important. We can't count on another miracle if we discard proper planning and rely on blind courage. |Commander, I'll be able to protect you, no matter the situation. Hehe, I am called an "Imperial Ship" because I have that capacity after all~♪
900046.feeling5: Commander, after tonight's banquet... will you be free? Hehe, please look forward to it~
900046.hp_warning: Commander... It's too early to give up just yet!
900046.expedition: Welcome back, everyone. Hopefully, none of you encountered any suspicious people?
900046.mail: Are all of these new letters? Thank you for your hard work.
900046.drop_descrip: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.
900046.skill: Be swept away by the raging waves!
900046.mission: Let's finish while we still have the momentum!

302200.feeling4: Me? I'm fond of interesting things. Such as... the act of toying with you, Commander... *Giggle*, you'll have to excuse me for that~
302200.propose: You have feelings for me, Commander? You wish to be with me forever? ... Why am I asking the questions here? *Giggle*, because, even for someone like me, wouldn't it be humiliating to have someone else take the initiative at moments like these...?
302200.detail: Ah, if it isn't you, Commander. I was just making a snack. Could you taste it for pois... I mean, taste to see if it's done?
couple_encourage: If you want to mess with Nagara, first you must tell me.
302200.feeling1: Even breathing the same air as you do is unpleasant, Commander~
302200.upgrade: Please, have faith in the skill of this Agano-class light cruiser.
302200.battle: Let's give it everything we have.
302200.home: Commander, fantastic work on the last sortie. May I offer you some hot tea?
302200.login: Commander, it's not yet time for work. Are you confident you didn't get the time wrong?
302200.mission_complete: Commander, if you keep tasking your secretary with collecting the mission rewards, your brain will eventually turn to mush. Although, it might be interesting if that happened... *Giggle*♪
302200.feeling3: Commander, why don't we have a chat? Yes, I'm curious as to what kind of person you are.
302200.unlock: Are you the Commander? My name is Agano. The pleasure is all mine, *giggle*... Never mind that, it was nothing. I'm eager to assume my position within your fleet.
302200.feeling2: I wonder what will happen today... *Giggle*, I'm looking forward to finding out.
302200.touch: These documents are for me... Hm? That's unusual? I like to keep business and pleasure separate, you see.
302200.profile: I am Agano, the lead ship of the Agano-class. My abilities as a light cruiser are first-rate, though my birth was just a tad bit late... Commander, it is a pleasure to be in your service.
302200.main: Commander, if you're tired, why not play a game of leapfrog and jump around in the office? It'll help improve your blood circulation~|Though supporting from behind the lines is easy, doing so for long periods makes me grow tired of it...|Commander, are you in need of some rest? Hm? *Giggle*, I just felt like asking. Stay focused and continue your work~
302200.feeling5: Someone who toys with the person they like... Are you familiar with anyone like that, Commander? *Giggle*, perhaps it's me~
302200.lose: How careless of me... I will undergo special training when we've returned. *Giggle*.
302200.hp_warning: Dear me, it seems things have gotten rather serious.
302200.expedition: Commander, the girls that went on a commission have returned. If you keep twiddling your thumbs, you'll miss your chance to welcome them back...
302200.mail: Are you sure this isn't a love letter from that girl you know? *Giggle*♪
302200.drop_descrip: Agano-class light cruiser number one – Agano.
302200.skill: They don't call me "state of the art" for nothing~
302200.mission: I went ahead and sorted out the new mission documents.

10100070.feeling4: Yo, Commander! Next time, let's go out somewhere! By the way, you have no right to refuse.
10100070.propose: This is... for me? Are you for real? I see... so you are. Understood, I'll accept your feelings. I'll become even stronger, so I can continue to be your shield!
couple_encourage: Hey, Green Heart! Get those giant Thunder Tits outta here, I can't even see in front of me!
Forward, everyone! Prepare yourselves!
10100070.feeling1: I don't want to see your sorry mug at all!
10100070.battle: Don't think you can go home just like this!
10100070.home: That was a pretty good battle, wasn't it? Let's keep it up just like this.
10100070.login: So damn slow... Ugh. How long are you gonna keep me waiting?
10100070.feeling3: Even though you're an unreliable commander, I still have some expectations for you.
10100070.unlock: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!
10100070.feeling2: Oi, where are you looking, you bastard? You don't need to answer, I already know! ...You think I'm cute? Flattery isn't going to get you anywhere.
10100070.profile: I'm the CPU of Lowee, White Heart. I have two little sisters. Although they are mischievous prankers and a handful to look after, they're still very cute. Next time, why don't we all play together?
10100070.main: How long do I have to keep waiting here? My tech is gonna go obsolete at this rate.|Am I angry? ... It's just how I talk, don't worry about it.|Don't worry. I'll protect you.
10100070.win_mvp: Did I hold back too much?
10100070.feeling5: Don't worry, I'll always be at your side. I'm not sure why but, I always feel like my chest is hot and overflowing with power.
10100070.lose: If you hold me back again... I'll end you.
10100070.hp_warning: You little shits are making me mad!
10100070.expedition: A commission team has returned. Why don't we welcome them back?
10100070.mail: Yo, the mail's here. Hurry up and take a look.
10100070.drop_descrip: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!
10100070.skill: I'm gonna beat you into tatters!
10100070.mission: Hurry up and take care of these missions.

408081.unlock: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.
408081.drop_descrip: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.

307060.feeling4: Whenever I feel irritated or lost, training always makes me feel at ease. Yes, I’ll definitely get stronger and catch up to that Grey Ghost one day.
307060.propose: E-eh?! Th-this is... I’m not misunderstanding you, right? Then... um, from now on, I’ll be in your care, dar... darling? Waaah! Shoukaku is calling me!
307060.detail: That Grey Ghost... I’d like to duel her just once.
couple_encourage: I'm fearless, as long as my sister is with me!
I don't know why, but I just find you terribly annoying...
That ties up the score. Next round decides the winner!
Uwah! When did you get here?!
I never thought I'd fight alongside the Grey Ghost herself!
307060.feeling1: Commander, would you like a taste of the anguish I experienced during the Battle of the Marianas?
307060.upgrade: As a perfected aircraft carrier, I shall not lose to anyone, not even to my seniors or to the Grey Ghost herself.
307060.battle: A never-ending swarm of enemies? I’m already used to it.
307060.home: I’ll need you to perform some maintenance on me. Ah, don’t forget about the planes either!
307060.login: Where are we going today? Pearl Harbor? Or perhaps the Coral Sea?
307060.mission_complete: Hmm... Seems like the situation has taken a turn for the better!
307060.feeling3: My fate always seems to be entertwined with Lexington’s... Ah~ Commander, please don’t tell Sara I said that. I can’t handle that girl.
307060.unlock: I am {namecode:96}, the last elite of the Sakura Empire’s Carrier Divisions. I can only be at my best when I am with my sister {namecode:95}.
307060.feeling2: Seniors and juniors... they’re all such a pain.
307060.touch: My least favorite food? Turkey, of course.
307060.profile: I’m {namecode:96} from the Fifth Carrier Divison, though I was assigned to the First Carrier Division at one point. Together with my sister Shoukaku, we became the last two elite carriers of the Sakura Empire. We triumphed in bitter battles against Lexington, Hornet, and even Enterprise. That’s right, I was even able to severely damage the Grey Ghost herself, although she proved to be luckier than me. My service came to an end when Lexington, risen from the dead, sunk me. In the end, I still completed my final mission and sank with no regrets.
307060.main: {namecode:95} is so cute when she’s embarrassed!|Keep fighting until the last arrow is broken! That is what it means to be an elite!|Wait, Grey Ghost, don’t run away just because you won! Let’s have a rematch!
307060.win_mvp: I am the auspicious crane, after all!
307060.feeling5: Commander, you make me feel just as if I am with Shoukaku. H-huh? That’s not it! I’m not treating you as my sister!
307060.lose: Am I going to be sunk... again...?
307060.expedition: If only I had more planes...!
307060.mail: So? Is it good news or bad news?
307060.drop_descrip: Second ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:96}.
307060.skill: As long as Shoukaku is with me~!
307060.mission: Is it time for a break? Commander, you should come try some of {namecode:95}’s cooking!

10100061.drop_descrip: It's good to take it easy and celebrate once in a while, but especially in moments like these, you can't afford to let your guard down. Commander, why don't we spar for a bit? Don't even think about holding back - come at me!

10100051.drop_descrip: Oh, Commander? Won't you join me in a short conversation? I'll tell you things about Planeptune. Oh, and I'm eagerly awaiting the day you come to Planeptune for a visit.

201100.feeling4: I was lonely when I left the countryside, but with you, Commander, every day has been fun. That's why this is my second home... It would be better if you can hold back on teasing me, though...
201100.propose: ... Eh, eeeeeeeh!!!! ...Ugh ...You're mean, Commander... N-no, it's not like there's anything worth getting happier than this! I-I'm about to cry
201100.detail: Uwee~ This is so embarrassing... Why do I have strike such a pose...
201100.feeling1: Com-commander is scary... I wanna go home...
201100.upgrade: Even though I've become stronger... I-I'm gonna hide behind my sisters...
201100.battle: Nnnggh... This is so scary~ But... there's fish and chips if we win! I'm gonna do it!
201100.home: Ehehe... Getting on the bed, rolling around~~ Eeeh! Commander~ Did you see that?! Awww...
201100.login: C-Commander... you've finally come~ This place is huge... I was lost...
201100.unlock: I am... I'm the C-class destroyer Cygnet... yes! For the sake of getting fish and chips, I will do my best!
201100.feeling2: Huh... Whaaaa~! Commander, why are you staring at me while I'm eating?...
201100.touch2: Commander... I don't understand... Why am I getting hotter?
201100.profile: I-I'm the C-class's Cygnet... Before I went abroad, I had always been in the Home Fleet... I may not look like it but... I'm good at fishing! Uh... I... I'll do my best!
201100.main: You're always so quiet, Commander. I'm sleepy. ZZZZ... Huh? I... I-I'm not sleeping!|What do I like...? I'm too embarrassed to say it... Eh? I-It's an order? I... I like to eat delicious meals|That girl's clothes are so beautiful... Eh? No no no! I-I'm just complimenting, s-s-so I don't think those clothes will suit me!
201100.win_mvp: D-Did I win? Eh? Eeeh?! I'm first place?!
201100.feeling5: Every day I am well-fed, and I enjoy watching you, Commander. ...Something more enjoyable? I've never thought about it... What? You'll show me something important next time?
201100.lose: *cries* Daddy... it's dangerous here... I want to go home...
201100.expedition: Co-Commander... the commissions are done. Ca- Can I greet them together with you?
201100.drop_descrip: C-class destroyer ー Cygnet, Hull Number H83!
201100.mission: Commander, it will be bad if you don't do your m-missions~

307061.drop_descrip: New Elite 1st CarDiv, Zuikaku, reporting for duty! Ahh, I've always wanted to give such a cool introduction! Shoukaku would definitely make fun of me if she heard it, but I wanted to try it while everyone is in a festive mood... Commander, what'd you think?

301179.drop_descrip: The newly-retrofitted Kagerou has arrived~ I won't let that sister of mine pass me up anymore! Commander, lead us forward towards distant shores!

10100030.feeling4: Did you enjoy that book I gave you? You did? I'm glad to hear that... Hm...? No, it's just that nobody's ever said they enjoyed my books before, so I don't know how I should react...
10100030.propose: ...! I never thought I'd hear you say those words. Maybe it was fate all along for me to come to this world and meet you. Of course I hope we'll always be together from now on.
10100030.detail: Would you like to read a book too?
couple_encourage: Ughh... I'll use those disgusting over-inflated balloons of yours as a cushion!
Let me finish them off!
10100030.upgrade: A level is just a number... Let me demonstrate how strong I really am.
10100030.battle: As long as you stay calm nothing can go wrong.
10100030.home: Great, now I can get back to reading my book.
10100030.login: Welcome back. Not much happened while you were gone.
10100030.mission_complete: How about we go retrieve those mission rewards?
10100030.feeling3: Oh, what a coincidence. I was just thinking I should come see you. Anyway, today I've got this novel for you to read...
10100030.unlock: I'm Blanc. Nice to meet you. Maybe you could introduce some intriguing books from your world to me...
10100030.feeling2: I'm writing a novel right now, would you like to give it a read?
10100030.profile: I'm Blanc, the CPU of Lowee. I guess my hobbies are to read and write novels. I'm currently working on a new one.
10100030.main: I could recommend you a book I like. Hm? There's no need for that? I see... That's a shame.|It's really windy today... Let's hurry up then, before it dies down...|Perhaps I should write about this world and make a book about it when I return to Lowee.
10100030.win_mvp: That was great for a warm-up.
10100030.feeling5: You're the only one who seems to enjoy reading my novels... Nothing makes me happier than that. I hope you'll continue reading them, too.
10100030.lose: I'm astonished they've cornered us like this...
10100030.hp_warning: I'm getting a little ticked off...
10100030.drop_descrip: I'm Blanc. Nice to meet you. Maybe you could introduce some intriguing books from this world to me...
10100030.mission: Have you checked out today's missions?

108031.detail: Some snacks for Albacore and a torpedo model kit for Dace... These convenience stores really have everything, don't they!
108031.login: I've been waiting for you, Commander!
108031.unlock: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!
108031.touch: No, Commander! You can't have my precious discounted chips!
108031.touch2: I bet you waited for me to leave school just to do that!
108031.main: IT'S A SUPER RARE! Holy mackerel! Commander, look! Hehehe~ See what I just got?!|I snagged myself a limited-edition Sara plushie! Aren't you jealous~? ... Y-you already own one? D-did they scam me?!|School life is a lot more fun than I expected! I might just be a natural scholar!
108031.expedition: A-are they the fabled Fantastic Forty Percent Off?! ... Oh, it's just the commission team.
108031.drop_descrip: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!
108031.mission: A mission? Is that my homework?

301380.feeling4: Recently, my sisters have started whispering things when they see us together... Huh? They're saying I must have a rough time working so hard? But, I'm pretty relaxed...
301380.propose: Huh? Why is everyone here? Didn't you all already know that Commander and I get along the best... so why?
301380.feeling1: Everyone warned me... not to get close to the commander...
301380.battle: Huh? We're about to start our attack?
301380.home: Huh? Didn't you guys leave just a minute ago...?
301380.login: Huh? Commander, when'd you get here?
301380.mission_complete: Commander, about the mission... Huh? You're already done?
301380.feeling3: Commander, please consort with me... Huh? That doesn't mean let's be friends?
301380.unlock: Commander? Oh, right... I'm looking for the commander here... Huh? You're the one?
301380.feeling2: Commander, I'm returning the candy that Mutsuki swiped from your office... Huh? You gave it to her?
301380.touch: Huh? Are you going to help me brush my hair?
301380.touch2: Huh? Is this... a symbol of friendship?
301380.profile: I'm Fumizuki, of the Mutsuki class. Like my sisters, I specialize in long-range transport and escort missions. Um, I'm Fumizuki, of the... Huh? Oh wait, I already said that...
301380.main: Mutsuki is always munching on candy every day, won't she get cavities...? |Uzuki lost something again, so I'd like to help her find it... Huh? It's already been found? |If... If you need my help with anything, I'll give it my best shot...
301380.feeling5: Commander, please consort with me... Huh? That doesn't mean "I like you" either?
301380.hp_warning: Huh? Am I in a pickle?
301380.expedition: Commander, how are the commissions going... Huh? You've already collected the rewards?
301380.mail: Commander, there's a love letter for you... Huh? It's not real? Just one of Minazuki's pranks?
301380.mission: Commander, um... about those rewards... Huh? I have to finish the mission first?

105090.feeling4: The Commander is willing to talk to someone as bad-tempered as me. Such a weirdo... I don't hate talking to the Commander, though.
105090.propose: Unknowingly I’ve slowly become more dependent on you, Commander. With the power of the BIG SEVEN, I shall protect you until my dying breath.
105090.detail: Commander... Can you take your eyes off me?
105090.feeling1: Commander, please… don’t come any closer.
105090.upgrade: Emm, as one of the BIG SEVEN, my powers are unquestionable. Although, timely enhancements are still a necessity.
105090.battle: I will not allow you to misbehave anymore... All guns, ready to fire a volley!
105090.home: Making sure everyone returns home safely is also one of my duties.
105090.login: Commander, you’ve rested long enough. When shall we weigh anchor?
105090.mission_complete: Commander, mission reward has been delivered.
105090.feeling3: Commander, why do you care about me so much? Many people are afraid of me and keep their distance from me. Perhaps I've been too used to this. But recently, I’ve suddenly felt... so lonely.
105090.unlock: Are you the one calling me? Well, I've been waiting for this day for a long. In the name of the BIG SEVEN, Eagle Union battleship Colorado, reporting in.
105090.feeling2: I’m proud of my BIG SEVEN title. Unfortunately the battleship era is closing, and a new wave of ships are arriving...
105090.touch: Commander, please don't touch the main gun that I was just using, you will affect my shooting accuracy.
105090.touch2: Shall I load the Commander into a 406mm gun and fire him?
105090.profile: I'm the lead ship of the Colorado class. In order to gain an advantage in the decisive battle, I'm the first ship to be equipped with 406mm guns. BIG SEVEN... is the most honored title for us battleships.
105090.main: Commander, although aircraft carriers are really powerful, but battleships are not obsolete. They are indispensable! |Amelia... She was a great woman, though she still cannot be found. Perhaps she is flying freely in another world... |My poor sisters were hurt on that humiliating day. One day, I will have those invaders pay for what they have done!
105090.win_mvp: Huh? Am I the MVP? Such a piece of cake for one of the BIG SEVEN.
105090.feeling5: The Commander's compliment after the end of each battle is something which I crave for. Commander, can you... praise me a little more?
105090.lose: This is not the end of the line...
105090.hp_warning: The bridge was hit? Damage control, now!
105090.expedition: A lot of oil and supplies have been shipped in. Looks like we got plenty of both for the next mission.
105090.mail: You’ve got new mail. There may be news from my sisters...
105090.drop_descrip: Colorado class battleship— Colorado, hull number BB-45
105090.skill: It's time to show you the true power of the BIG SEVEN!
105090.mission: Whether you need fire support or fleet battle, please give the order Commander.

203019.detail: I can always change back to my old outfit, but to be frank, I've always looked forward to being able to wear something like this. Your Excellency, would you like me to get changed?
203019.unlock: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?
203019.touch: What am I going to do with you... Well then, Your Excellency, please rest for a while. I'll prepare the snacks.
203019.main: I feel like my mood has been changing since I got my new outfit. Your Excellency, would you like to go for some dessert in a little bit? |Your Excellency, please do not forget the fact that I am still your secretary ship. Now, please focus and get back to your work! |Your Excellency, did you know that Sussex said that this outfit looks really pretty? You don't hear words of praise from her often, hehe~
203019.drop_descrip: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?

201101.detail: Hood gave this swimwear to me as a present but, how is it?... It's not inappropriate for me, right?
201101.login: C-Commander, welcome back~ Haa... Air conditioners are such wonderful inventions... Phew... This feels nice...
201101.unlock: Ooh... the swimwear that Hood gave me is a little tight... Huh? Play beace volleyball with Sara...? Am I... gonna win...?
201101.touch: Commander, are you going to take a picture of me?
201101.touch2: Wah! Commander, my... my swimwear is tight, so... please don't touch it, ok?
201101.main: Ah Hood, you are the most beautiful thing in the world! I feel a bit ashamed.... Hwe... This punishment is so embarrassing...|The barbecue party happens after sunset... Ehehe, I'm looking forward to that as well~|Sara's face darkened when she saw me... Do you think she dislikes me?...
201101.expedition: Commissions are done, and so is the grilled fish~ Here you go, Commander. How about it?
201101.drop_descrip: Well, the swimsuit that Hood gave to me is a little tight, don't you think? Want to play beach volleyball? Do you think... can we win?

301580.feeling4: You don't require my help, yet you keep me waiting by your side... Why is that? I don't quite understand...
301580.propose: This is how you've felt about me, Commander...? I've been slow to catch on, haven't I... But, do not worry, I pledge myself to you. I swear to always protect you, do exactly as you wish, and never again leave your side.
301580.detail: There is little I can do on my own. So, please, if I can assist in any way, don't be afraid to ask. I will help you.
301580.feeling1: I would prefer it if you'd stay away from me.
301580.battle: Be careful. Try to stay close to me.
301580.home: You must be tired. Should I prepare tea while you rest for a while, Commander?
301580.login: You have returned, Commander. I have already sorted all your documents.
301580.mission_complete: I have brought the mission rewards. These should be all of them.
301580.feeling3: I know that I can't always be by Harutsuki's side to help when she feels nervous. Yet, my body always acts on its own accord...
301580.unlock: I'm honored to meet you, Commander. I have come to assist you. From now on, I can help you with your work whenever needed.
301580.feeling2: Hm? I seem cold and distant to you? I've heard that from Harutsuki before... Oh, bother...
301580.touch: Do you feel tired? Shall I give you a shoulder massage?
301580.touch2: Commander, are you asking for a beating?
301580.profile: I am the Akizuki-class destroyer Yoizuki. I specialize in anti-air combat. If you ever have any problems, please tell me. I will solve them quickly for you.
301580.main: Why I help people? I feel I should; therefore I do it... Is that strange?|Some have mistaken me for a light cruiser... I wonder why... I don't look like one...|"Forcing myself"? Not at all. If I were, my help would only have the opposite effect.
301580.win_mvp: We have everyone to thank for this victory.
301580.feeling5: A "date"? What does that mean? ... It means we'll play together? Certainly, if that's what you wish. ... Why are you smiling? You're quite strange...
301580.lose: They tricked us... Everyone, retreat! I will watch your backs...!
301580.expedition: A commission has been completed. Splendid work.
301580.mail: Commander, I have left your mail here.
301580.mission: We have received a mission. Is it something I may take care of?

301181.drop_descrip: I heard that in the Dragon Empery, the Mid-Autumn Festival is a time to be reunited with your loved ones. Commander, are you going to go watch the moon with your favorite girl? ... You want to go with me? Saying that won't get you anywhere... Fine, Commander, as a token of my appreciation, I'll give you a 50% discount.

900186.feeling4: Why do I wear only one sock? That's a secret! If you're so curious, try taking it off~ Hehehe♪
900186.propose: Yeah... thanks. Even when we're not on the battlefield, we'll always be together... No, wait, cheesy lines like this are totally out of character for me! Anyhow, right now, I feel so happy!
900186.detail: You wanna get to know me? Sure thing. Inspect me to your heart's content.
couple_encourage: Hey, sis~ You really do need my support, don't you?
900186.feeling1: *Sigh*... So that's all, huh. I was wrong to get my hopes up.
900186.battle: Dang, guess I've got no choice! I'll show you the might of us Southerners!
900186.home: You're back~! I've been chewing on this gum so long it's lost all its taste.
900186.login: Another day of calm weather! Nice!
900186.mission_complete: Today's missions were a breeze! Total walk in the park!
900186.feeling3: Hm? You'd never have guessed that I'd be into ballet? ... What's that supposed to mean?! Laugh one more time and I'll punch you!
900186.unlock: Cleveland-class light cruiser number 2, Columbia! That's me~! Not the Columbia in D.C., the one in South Carolina! Geez, listen to me! Not the Columbia with Bogotá as its capital!
900186.feeling2: Commander, it's sunny outside, so why don't we go for a walk? It's unhealthy to stay indoors all the time!
900186.touch: Gee, thanks! You made my bubble pop!
900186.touch2: Commander, is it this star on my shirt you like? Or is it... what's underneath it~?
900186.profile: Hiii! It's me, the girl who scooted through the Pacific and earned 10 battle stars: Columbia! Hey, now, no need to sing my praises, go see Cleveland and sing hers instead! Need anything else? Alright, then I'll get back to patrolling.
900186.main: What tunes do I listen to? Good question. See if you can guess! ... Rock 'n' roll? Bzzzt, wrong!|Bleh, my sis snatched my sunglasses again...|Once this war is over, maybe I should give Eagle Union football a try...
900186.win_mvp: That was nothing special~ I do it all the time~
900186.feeling5: When I can't see you on my days off, I feel kinda lonely... Geez, look at you, making a girl say stuff like this! A-aren't you ashamed of yourself?! Jerk!
900186.expedition: The commission team's back! Aren't you gonna go thank them?
900186.mail: Aren't you gonna check your mail? There might be something nice in there.
900186.drop_descrip: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Columbia, hull number CL-56.
900186.skill: Don't blame me if you get hit!
900186.mission: I only just started chewing this gum, and we've already got a new mission...?

101382.detail: There are many differences between the Eagle Union and the Dragon Empery, but the one thing that doesn't change no matter where you are is everyone's desire for a better future.
101382.headtouch: C-Commander, the buns are going to get messed up...
101382.home: Every time I return to port, I feel a wave of relief wash over me. Is this what "home" is?
101382.login: There is a proverb from the Dragon Empery: "A day's plans begin in the morning." Even if it's not the morning though, don't you think it's important to start off on the right foot, Commander?
101382.mission_complete: Mission complete. Commander, want to take a break?
101382.unlock: When I change into clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but to reminisce about the time I spent there... Commander, which style of clothes do you prefer - Union, or Empery?
101382.touch: There's still a lot of work left to do... but don't worry, Commander! Let's knock it out together!
101382.touch2: Commander... you could go to jail for this, you know?
101382.main: My friends from the Dragon Empery told me about a lot of fascinating legends! Commander, do you want to hear them too? |Recently, I tried to learn the bamboo flute. Commander, want to give it a listen? |Ugh... calligraphy is really difficult...
101382.feeling5: When I'm with you, I feel energized and my productivity goes through the roof. Perhaps... this is your magic spell? Hehe~
101382.drop_descrip: While wearing clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but reminisce about those days... Hehe, Commander, do you prefer me in Empery-style clothes, or Union-style clothes?
101382.mission: If you put things off for tomorrow, you'll find that there's always another tomorrow. That's why you shouldn't put off today's missions for tomorrow.

401180.feeling4: Has my smile reached your heart, Commander? My smile belongs to everyone, but I can smile a little more just for you~
401180.propose: There's no higher praise for my smile than this~ Ehehe, just like always, I will smile for everyone in the fleet, and for you too, Commander!
401180.detail: Okay, Commander! Let's see aaaa... SMILE!
401180.feeling1: It doesn't look like my smile will reach your heart, Commander...
401180.upgrade: Now my smile can reach the hearts of more people!
401180.home: Nice work~! Replenish your energy with these snacks and my smile~
401180.login: Welcome back, Commander~ Have you smiled yet today?
401180.mission_complete: Way to go, Commander! We got so many rewards from that~
401180.feeling3: A smile is always good, but when cruelty makes someone smile... it's kind of creepy...
401180.unlock: Nice to meet you, I'm Z18! I'm the girl whose smile will reach everyone's hearts~
401180.feeling2: People feel sad and anxious when they lose, right? That's why I'll be there to cheer them up!
401180.touch: Do you need anything from me?
401180.touch2: You can't do whatever you want just because I'm smiling! Hmph!
401180.profile: I'm the second Type 1936 destroyer, Z18~! You can call me Hans, although it sounds a little boyish... Hm? I'm really different from other Iron Blood girls? Heheh, a smile makes all the difference~
401180.main: Everyone from Iron Blood are either obsessed with war or say a bunch of stuff that doesn't make sense... and my mission is to make them all smile!|I prescribe a smile to anyone who's feeling afraid~|I believe that, deep down, there's a smile in everyone's hearts! Anyone can smile once they know that!
401180.feeling5: Your smile has reached MY heart, Commander! It makes me feel so warm and happy!
401180.lose: I'll always smile, even when defeated~!

203020.feeling2: Do you need something? I'm concentrating on work right now, so spare me the sweet talk~

203020.main: I am a little nervous when I am alone with you, Commander, but since you are alone I'm fu... fully calm myself~|Com~man~der~ Help me~ Please, you are the only one I can count on~|Did you know, Commander? Sometimes, making small mistakes can make one seem cuter~
203020.win_mvp: You need not shower me with praises. Pay attention to others as well~
203020.feeling5: Please mind the time, place and mood when you do this, so I'm sorry! ... Ah! I don't mind the amount of times you confess to me~
203020.lose: Commander, clumsy girls have their charms as well, wouldn't you say? Heh-hey~

203020.mail: Commander, you have new mail~ Is it a love letter? It's a love letter, isn't it? Open it, open it!
203020.drop_descrip: London-class heavy cruiser – Shropshire, Hull Number 73!

405020.feeling4: The worst feeling in the world is not knowing whether to continue waiting or to give up hope. Commander, are you someone worth waiting for?
405020.propose: Ahh... so this is the warmth of one's beating heart... It's melting the cold and despair remaining within me. Danke sehr, Commander. The "Queen of the North" is no longer alone.
405020.feeling1: In the end... are you just another incompetent fool, unable to command me?
405020.upgrade: If you have no opponents, all the might in the world is meaningless.
405020.battle: Commander, I shall fight for your sake.
405020.home: Commander, you should show your face on the battlefield more often. If you stay behind your desk for too long, you may one day forget the meaning of life.
405020.login: Once you get used to waiting, you lose sight of what you were waiting for.
405020.feeling3: Those who have nothing to lose also have nothing to fear... But is this kind of bravery really anything to be proud of?
405020.unlock: I was imprisoned in the north for so long, unable to return home, and now you want me to follow you? ...Very well. It is up to you to show me the world.
405020.feeling2: I have already grown used to the cold solitude of the North. At this point, it's natural for me to have no expectations.
405020.touch2: I'll think of how to deal with you later.
405020.profile: It's a bit hot... Ah, sorry. I am Tirpitz. Because I was stuck in the north by myself for so long, people suddenly started calling me the "Lone Queen of the North." If you think it's a good nickname, then you do not fully understand... how soulless those words are.
405020.main: Big sister... Now that you mention it, I think I might actually have one... Ah... I've already started to forget.|Can you comprehend how it feels to watch the battlefield from afar, unable to do anything but lament the cruelty of war?|Strategic reasons? I was installed with cannons... but they were never meant to be fired. Ironic, isn't it?
405020.win_mvp: So this... is the taste of victory.
405020.feeling5: Ahh... I see. I thought I was used to the cold and embraced it, but that was just because I had forgotten the joy of human interaction and the warmth of being with someone... But now I remember...
405020.lose: So this is... the frustration that comes from failure and fear.
405020.hp_warning: No one would protect those who asked for their own destruction.

900044.skill: As long as Shoukaku is with me~!

201110.win_mvp: Hehehe, can the most cunning fox beat an old hound like me?
201110.feeling5: I like the Commander... *rubs* I really like the Commander... *Rubs* I like Commander the most *RUBS*...
201110.lose: Whew! I'm glad we were quick to escape!
201110.expedition: *Sniff* I think... I think the girls have finished their commissions~!
201110.drop_descrip: F-class destroyer ー Foxhound, Hull Number H69!
201110.skill: I'm not a fox, but a doggy!

201238.battle: Come! Raise thine glass to our love!
201238.home: Darling, what's the souvenir? A test? Could it be a fine wine, or maybe chocolates from a land over yonder?
201238.login: Darling~ Where shall we date on this eve?
201238.mission_complete: Mission complete! Next up, dating time~

201238.touch: Are you elevating your love for me?
201238.main: Cleaning is no task for a vampire! We can be lazy every once and a while!|I'm bored... Mine darling, how about a date?|Doth thou beseech the color of mine garmets today? Were thou not the one who dressed me on the morn~
201238.win_mvp: Flowers and salute fire for my love!

201238.expedition: Oh my darling~ Let us go and greet the maiden's upon thier return~
201238.mail: You want the mail? Then exchange sweet love letters with me~
201238.drop_descrip: Those who fall in love with vampires are bound to suffer seven times more than their infatuation. After all, love is a poison which leads to death.
201238.mission: Rather than missions, am I not more important?

801021.detail: Would you like some fresh fruit, Commander?
801021.battle: I hope... I don't get these clothes dirty...
801021.unlock: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?
801021.touch: I know the other knights went out of their way to pick this dress for me... but I'm not used to all the frills and whatnot...
801021.touch2: Eep! N-next time, I won't hold back!
801021.main: We don't usually get such fresh apples and tomatoes, so how about a mixed juice? It's good for your health! |No more fighting, no more wars... That's the peace that we're fighting to reclaim. |Commander, I heard that aromatherapy can help you recover from fatigue. Why don't you try growing some flowers?
801021.feeling5: If only this peace could last forever... Nay, as long as we work together, this won't merely be a dream. Right, Commander? Hehe~
801021.drop_descrip: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?

801020.feeling4: Commander, did you know that I've always had two dreams? The first was to become a worthy knight like my seniors. The second was to find someone worthy of swearing fealty to... I never expected that my second dream would come true first~
801020.propose: This I do swear - my sword shall be your shield, Commander. In return, please promise to guide me down the correct path... I don't ever want to experience that ever again...!
801020.detail: Hooh! Haah! Oh, great timing, Commander! Let's practice some swordplay!
couple_encourage: Le Mars, stay in formation!
801020.feeling1: If the knights found out that I had sworn fealty to a person like you... I don't know if they'd blame me or pity me...
801020.upgrade: My odds of victory have improved!
801020.battle: All right! I'll surely be able to win in this condition!
801020.home: Welcome back, Commander. Don't worry, nothing happened when you were gone.
801020.login: Hooo! Haah! Oh, Commander, let's do our warm-up exercises together!
801020.mission_complete: Don't let these mission rewards go to waste, Commander.
801020.feeling3: Why do I spend so much time training with the sword? Well, it's true that I don't plan on using it during sorties, but being able to keep myself sharp and in shape is surely an asset on the battlefield!
801020.unlock: I am Forbin, a squire from Iris Libre. I may not match up to the stature of my seniors, but please offer me your guidance!
801020.feeling2: There are all kinds of amazing people gathered here. There's just so much to learn... Ahh, I've gotta work even harder!
801020.touch: Commander, did you know that there are many different kinds of swords? For example, there are rapiers, sabres, flamberges, and so on...
801020.touch2: I didn't mean to draw my sword upon someone unarmed... I am very sorry.
801020.profile: I'm Forbin, a L'Adroit-class destroyer from Iris Libre. For various reasons, I was stuck in port for two years, but after returning to service, I was able to get a lot done and make up for some of that lost time on the battlefield.
801020.main: Iron Blood or Royal Navy, I don't care who it is, I just want to learn more about them! |When will I become as strong and cool as the knights? |I don't want my life to end without having accomplished anything... so this time, I'll give it my all!
801020.win_mvp: I'm one step closer to becoming a knight!
801020.feeling5: Commander, please believe in me. The only time someone will be able to hurt you is when the last shell has been spent and I am no longer able to lift my sword.
801020.lose: I swear... to take this defeat to heart!
801020.expedition: Commission complete! Next time, let me go as well. I swear I'll do better!
801020.mail: A letter...? Wonder if someone's challenging you to a duel...
801020.mission: Commander, I believe that it is your duty to complete these missions.

801010.feeling4: Familiarity with hardship and suffering cultivates an appreciation of life and death. At least that's what I think...
801010.propose: Finally... this day has come at last... Commander, you truly are my fated partner. I, Le Triomphant, willingly offer you my sword, my shield, and my body.
801010.detail: If you have any questions, feel free to ask away. I will respond to each one.
couple_encourage: Let us dedicate this victory to Commander!
801010.feeling1: So... I guess this is the kind of person that you are, Commander...
801010.upgrade: I feel strength rippling from my sword and shield... Commander, thank you.
801010.battle: In the name of Iris Libre, let us break their lines!
801010.home: That was a hard-fought battle, Commander. Would you like to have a cup of tea before you resume work?
801010.login: My, I see you've returned? What shall your orders be today? I am ready to accept any assignment - commission or sortie!
801010.mission_complete: Commander, here are the fruits of your labor.
801010.feeling3: In order to realize their ideals and ambitions, even family members may part ways and eventually meet each other on the battlefield... It's so tragic...
801010.unlock: Oh my, Commander, what a pleasure it is to meet you. I am Le Triomphant, an elegant large destroyer from Iris Libre, yours to command. The power of the Le Fantasque-class shall exceed your wildest fantasies.
801010.feeling2: Don't you think Noblesse Oblige is an elegant idea?
801010.touch: Commander, you'll be missing out if you treat me and my sisters as regular destroyers.
801010.touch2: Eek! To think that you're even faster than the Le Fantasque class... you're not one to be taken lightly, Commander.
801010.profile: I am Le Triomphant, a Le Fantasque-class Destroyer from Iris Libre. It is an honor to meet you. My sisters and I were in the 8th Light Division before the fateful Battle of Jutland. After that, our paths diverged...
801010.main: My sword and shield? Oh, they stop feeling heavy after a while. Well, I also am quite strong. |If I was with my sisters at that time... would things have happened differently...?|Whether someone is friend or foe... is not something set in stone.
801010.win_mvp: You'll find that the speed of the Le Fantasque-class is not easily matched!
801010.feeling5: Commander, as long as we're together, I feel like I can easily overcome any adversity... that's what I truly believe.
801010.lose: Sometimes... things like this can happen as well...
801010.hp_warning: The outcome... still isn't set in stone!
801010.expedition: Why don't you let me handle the next one? I'll get it done the fastest.
801010.mail: It feels nice to be celebrated by someone you don't know, doesn't it?

306059.detail: Don't look so sad... I'll keep growing. I'm sure of it!
306059.unlock: Commander, how do I look now that I've grown up? Are ya fallin' in love with me already? Mhm, ye definitely are~
306059.touch: Commander, do ye like my Shikigami? They ain't the bitin' type, I swear!
306059.touch2: I feel like I've definitely matured some! Commander, what do ya think?
306059.main: Commander, gimme a chance to prove myself!|Why does everyone treat me like a kid when I'm already all grown up?|Grown-ups need to play, too! Won't you play with me, Com~man~der?
306059.drop_descrip: Commander, how do I look now that I've grown up? Are ya fallin' in love with me already? Mhm, ye definitely are~

301200.feeling4: I tried too hard to be brave in Leyte Gulf... In the end I couldn't save anyone...
301200.propose: This is... proof of a sisterly bond?! Commander, you want to be my sister? ... I've got it all wrong?! But that's what {namecode:130}-chan told me...
301200.detail: The Leyte Gulf? I don't remember very much of it...
couple_encourage: I'm nothing like you!
This time, I'll only fire on the enemy...
O... Onee-chan...
301200.feeling1: ... I can't sleep with you next to me...
301200.home: Commander... *Yawn*... Today's weather is perfect for a nap...
301200.login: Zzz... Fiiine, I'll get up in a second... The sun... is so warm... Zzz...
301200.mission_complete: Your rewards won't disappear even if you don't collect them... I think...
301200.feeling3: {namecode:130}... I promise I'll help you this time...!
301200.unlock: This place is... Huh? Are you the commander?! Ahem! Destroyer {namecode:24}, reporting in!
301200.feeling2: Movies? They aren't really my thing...
301200.profile: I'm {namecode:24}, a {namecode:19}-class destroyer. Luck? Kure and Sasebo ships have that, us Maizuru ships do not. I was unable to save {namecode:130} in Truk, but when I was in the Leyte Gulf I came running to {namecode:62}'s rescue. In the end I couldn't save everyone... but in my dreams we're all still together...
301200.main: If only I'd tried harder when I was in Truk...|I like this place, I don't need to hurt any of my allies here...|{namecode:25}... {namecode:22}... We're all together again in my dreams...
301200.win_mvp: Hm? I'M the MVP?! What a lucky day!
301200.feeling5: Zzz... Commander... It's fine to take some time off and nap every now... and then... Zzz...
301200.lose: Where... am I? Who's shooting at me?
301200.expedition: Someone's come back... Is it lunchtime now...?
301200.mail: I don't really need a bedtime story...
301200.mission: A-a mission? I hope it won't be difficult...

102090.feeling4: Before I realized it, I'm the one who's leaning on your shoulder instead... but hey, that's fine. We can always just rely on each other.
102090.propose: Heh, I had a feeling this would happen! From now on, you can tell me anything. I'll take excellent care of you!
couple_encourage: Come on, fellow big sisters. Let's work hard together!
"Hao" do you do, folks?

102090.battle: I'm in a hurry... just come at me all at once, alright?

102090.mission_complete: Nice! We got some mission rewards!
102090.feeling3: Mm... I'm not trying to make myself look stronger than I am or anything, but honestly, I think there aren't many people like you who I can speak to like an equal...
102090.unlock: Pleasure meeting you, Commander! I'm Cleveland, a knight of the sea! Come on, time is money! We can't afford to take a break!
102090.feeling2: What is, Commander? Something troubling you? I've got lots of little sisters, so I'm used to giving them my shoulder to lean on. So if anything's got you down, just tell me.
102090.touch2: You can't do this sorta stuff in public, Commander...
102090.profile: I'm the big sister of the Cleveland-class... but I guess that's obvious from my name alone. I fought through the Battle of Renelle Island, the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay, plus many others, and I earned around 13 battle stars, so I'm pretty strong!
102090.main: Never regret the choices you make!|Why do you call me "Clevebro"?! I'm a girl, just like the others!|You know, I like trees. Let's grow a bonsai, Commander!
102090.win_mvp: Hehe, now this is what I'd call the fruits of my hard labor!
102090.feeling5: I feel like I've told you everything about myself... Time sure flies, doesn't it... I doubt someone who understands me the way you do will ever show up again. That's why I've...
102090.expedition: Hehe, it's about time we reap the rewards of that commission, Commander!
102090.mail: Some new mail just arrived. You sure are popular, Commander!
102090.drop_descrip: Cleveland-class Light Cruiser – Cleveland, Hull Number CL-55!
102090.mission: We've got a new mission! Let's finish it in one go!

301161.detail: Even though this dress perfectly suits Yukikaze the Great, it makes it hard to play on the swings... Urgh... what should I do?!
301161.battle: You thought this was just a regular swing set, but behold! Torpedo tubes!
