301161.main: Ahh, I can feel Commander's longing gazes... but alas! This swing set is for Yukikaze the Great, and no one else! Wa ha ha! Am I not downright evil? |My gothic dress? Heheh~ You might think I've gotten tired of hearing it, but... I shall allow you to praise the beauty of Yukikaze the Great! Haha! |Swinging around too much shakes around your brain and makes you stupid...? And the only way to fix it is to stay in one spot and work? Really?! Um, I suppose... it can't be helped then...
301161.win_mvp: If you think Yukikaze the Great is simply here for fun and games, you'd be dead wrong!
301161.drop_descrip: Wa ha ha! My "universal-as-long-as-there-is-a-ceiling" swing set is finally complete! Commander, are you jealous? Want to give it a try? Too~ bad~! This seat is reserved only for the noble and elegant Yukikaze!

306060.feeling4: Commander, did you prepare this meal for me by yourself? In that case, I'll be more than glad to dig in! Mm... thanks for the food! Eh? You'll continue to cook for me when I come back!?
306060.propose: From now on, no matter what perils we might face, I will protect you with everything I have! Even if I sink to the bottom of the ocean, I will not permit any harm to come to you!
306060.detail: Milord, we cannot survive unless we fight!
306060.feeling1: No matter where you are, the top brass is all the same...
306060.upgrade: Thank you very much, Milord! Shall we go run a lap to test my new strength?
306060.home: Don't break formation even when we head back to port! The glory of the Sakura Empire is in its meticulousness!
306060.login: A day off? Milord, my week only consists of Monday, Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday, and Friday!
306060.mission_complete: The mission rewards are here! A bagel? Is this a snack for me? Thank you, Milord. Well then, let's move out!
306060.feeling3: Commander, feel free to rely on me as you please. Should you will it, I will execute any command.
306060.unlock: Milord, I am called Ryuujou, a ranger from the Land of the Rising Sun! I shall lay down my seven lives to mete out justice in your name!
306060.feeling2: Milord, when it comes to war, victory is more important than good or evil!
306060.touch: Milord, please be careful. I am just as top-heavy as Illustrious.
306060.touch2: Eek!!! Oh, it wasn't Saratoga after all. However, you seem to be even more mischievous than she is.
306060.profile: I am Ryuujou of the Sakura Empire, a seasoned warrior who has served in the First through Fourth Carrier Divisions, and participated in campaigns in the Phillipines, East Indies, Aleutian Islands, and Guadalcanal. I don't look the part...? Th-that must be because of that one incident at Iwate that stunted my growth! Milord, just you wait. I'll show you the extent of my capabilities!
306060.main: Odango... these delicacies will cause my heart to waver, so... Um, I suppose I can reward myself a little.... Mmmh! So delicious! |When you're stressed out, you should go watch the fish swimming around peacefully in the aquarium. I'm not sure why, but it always calms me down. |I fight for a just cause! No matter who stands before me, I swear to give it my all!
306060.win_mvp: Despair... shall be your final destination!
306060.feeling5: Just being able to see your face before I sortie fills me to the brim with energy and makes me feel like I can't lose to anyone!
306060.lose: Ugh... my body is all beat up...
306060.expedition: Worldly things are of little significance! The only things that matter are spirit and resilience!
306060.mail: A telegram? Oh, it's not a combat report from Headquarters. I suppose there might be some value to reading it then.
306060.skill: As long as I am here, nothing shall stand in my way!
306060.mission: A new mission is here! Whether it's combat or training, let's knock it out at the speed of sound!

101259.detail: How long are you going to keep looking... I want to go see how Yorktown is doing...
101259.home: Good work out there... W-what! I'll give a decent compliment to someone who works hard, even if they're stupid!
101259.login: You're a full-blown pervert beyond saving if just seeing these clothes makes you so excited!
101259.unlock: I'm just wearing new clothes, so why should I have to raise my skirt like this? Huh? You want me to look more upset? You... you pervert!
101259.main: nil|As long as you promise to work hard, I'll stay with you for just a little longer... I guess?|nil
101259.drop_descrip: I'm just wearing new clothes, so why should I have to raise my skirt like this? Huh? You want me to look more upset? You... you pervert!

605060.feeling4: A little bird told me you're free, and I've got two tickets to the opera, so what do you say? I'd say you're due for something you haven't experienced before.
605060.propose: *Sigh*... The romantic vacation I booked was all for nothing... "With who"? With you, shouldn't that be obvious?! ... "Just ask me next time"? But I booked it just for you in the first place... F-fine, I will...
605060.detail: At last I can have a rematch with Warspite on equal terms. I've been waiting for this!
couple_encourage: Our battle isn't over yet!
Cavour, worry about yourself instead!
605060.feeling1: Seems you lack the mindset to be a worthy commander.
605060.upgrade: I've yet to hit my own limits!
605060.battle: As per the Commander's orders, we depart for the front!
605060.home: Triumphant once again, yes? It's written all over your face.
605060.login: You're right on time... Naturally. I'll admit your timeliness is the one thing I could learn from.
605060.mission_complete: On the topic of completing missions, does it even affect the war situation?
605060.feeling3: A little bit of harsh discipline is the right medicine for slouches who can't obey orders. "It's not that simple"? Well, I thought I was making a good suggestion...
605060.unlock: I'm Giulio Cesare, battleship of the Sardegna Empire. Prove to me your talent in commanding a fleet!
605060.feeling2: Cavour always stresses the importance of courtesy and diplomatic discourse, but I believe in simply speaking one's mind. Doesn't it sound dreadful to obsess over some idea of formality?
605060.touch: Mh... Mm? Sorry, I zoned out for a bit... Were you worried about me, Commander?
605060.touch2: If you plan on toying around with me, don't blame me when you get burned.
605060.profile: Memories that haunt me? None but that dreaded battle. I had to retreat from the Battle of Punto Stilo after taking a single hit... Things would've gone differently, had I only gotten to strike first...!
605060.main: Office work? Cavour is better at it than me... but I'll still do it. As any secretary should.|Commander, be decisive. Hesitation wastes time, and wasted time is gone forever.|A good leader doesn't micromanage or mediate, they issue clear orders and make firm decisions. Isn't that right, Commander?|Cavour, don't be so overly formal around the Commander! No one wants to be treated like an old-timer!
605060.feeling5: You can rest easy, Commander. For as long as I have your back, you can keep your eyes on the path ahead and continue moving forward. I'll take care of everything else for you!
605060.lose: Am I out of my depth...?!
605060.hp_warning: You won't break my spirit so easily!
605060.expedition: Isn't that the commission team? Why not go say hello to them, Commander?
605060.mail: There's a letter for you. Assuming it's no private matter, you don't mind if I open it, do you?
605060.drop_descrip: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Giulio Cesare.
605060.skill: All shall bow before my might!
605060.mission: You can honestly skip missions you'd rather not take on.

301630.feeling4: Commander, I'm at ease when I'm with you... But every time I think about Arashio, I get anxious again...
301630.propose: If there's one good thing that's happened to me, it's that I was able to meet you, Commander. Will you stay by my side until I fall asleep? Tonight... and tomorrow... and every night...
301630.detail: I'd like to stay here forever... But at this rate, I won't be able to find Arashio.
301630.upgrade: I think... it'd be better to mount another anti-air gun.
301630.battle: Anti-air preparations... is everything in place?
301630.home: There is nothing more reassuring than being here. Commander, don't you think so too?
301630.login: Welcome back, Commander. If you don't want to set sail right away, why don't you rest first?
301630.mission_complete: The mission rewards... can I use them to buy something to eat?
301630.feeling3: I had another nightmare yesterday. Commander, would you please stay with me tonight? That black abyss, not being able to see anything... I'm scared...
301630.unlock: I am Asashio. I've come to join this fleet in order to search for my missing comrade. Commander, do you also have someone who you could not give up on?
301630.feeling2: Every time I look out into the horizon, memories of that time come flooding back to me...
301630.touch: Don't worry, I... am not afraid anymore!
301630.profile: Asashio-class nameship, Asashio. Arashio and I, along with our friends, formed the 8th DesDiv. Though we were disbanded in the end, I strongly believe that we'll be able to be together again one day. Commander... do you want to help me find them?
301630.main: Dampier Strait? I don't really want to think about that place anymore... More importantly, Commander, can you install another anti-air gun? |Happiness is a full belly and a good night's sleep. |*Yawns* ...It's already so late, but Commander is still at it... Please make sure to take care of yourself.
301630.win_mvp: It seems that I accidentally did something awesome...
301630.feeling5: Commander, you're somehow always able to put my heart at ease. But recently, I've discovered something else that scares me... Commander, you'll always stay by my side... right?
301630.lose: If only I had upgraded my anti-air equipment a bit more...
301630.hp_warning: The situation... seems to not be ideal.
301630.expedition: Isn't it about time to welcome the others back?
301630.mail: Shall I go through the email for you? Maybe there's a letter from Arashio...
301630.skill: This time... I won't fail again!
301630.mission: Commander, your missions... Please show some motivation once in a while.

401200.feeling4: If you never tell others how you feel about them, they'll never understand. You get that, right?
401200.propose: Say, I heard there's a tradition in the East where couples will drink with their arms intertwined. Haha, come on, Commander! Don't be shy!
401200.detail: I'll make all your concerns go "poof!" How's that, Commander? Feel better?
401200.feeling1: The moment I saw you, all the fatigue from running kicked in at once. I'm out, time to rest!
401200.battle: I'm the flagship? Fine by me! Everyone, follow me!
401200.home: Good job! Let's go find some place to relax.
401200.mission_complete: Marathon, marathon! I'll definitely take first place this time.
401200.feeling3: What's wrong? Something bugging you? I promise you'll feel better if we go run a marathon together!
401200.unlock: Z20, Karl Galster, reporting in! Where's my welcoming party?
401200.feeling2: As long as you keep running, you'll leave behind all your hardship and anxiety. Commander, come find me any time you're feeling down.
401200.touch: Hmm? You want to go on a run with me?
401200.touch2: Hehe, how do you like my curves?
401200.profile: I am Z20 Karl Galster, Iron Blood Z-class 1936-Type destroyer, the sole survivor of the Z17 type destroyers. After being being handed over to the Northern Union, I was renamed "прочный." Being separated from my sisters and living alone sure was rough...
401200.main: Commander, let me teach you the right way to breathe while running. It's good for both attacking and retreating!|As long as I'm in a good mood, I can enjoy any scenery!|Protschny? Don't call me by that name!
401200.feeling5: You idiot... All right, stop blushing and stammering. I like you. So, do you feel the same way about me?
401200.lose: Oof... even I mess up sometimes... just sometimes~
401200.expedition: Ah, our friends have returned! Let's go welcome them back!
401200.mail: A letter for you, eh? I don't think I should be the one to open your mail.
401200.skill: Gotta smile during battle as well!
401200.mission: Let's prepare for the celebrations before we start~

307090.feeling4: Hrmmm... he's my slave, but those women won't stop throwing themselves at him... even though he's my slave... and clearly mine alone.....
307090.propose: This means you totally belong to me, and I shall give everything to you, right? Aha... hahahahaha! ...Slave.... I never would have imagined that owning you would make me so happy... Ahahahahahaaaa!
307090.detail: It's truly marvelous to be so loved and treasured by this slave. *giggle*
307090.feeling1: It seems I've been too lenient with you...
307090.upgrade: What a well-behaved slave you are~
307090.battle: I'm the only one allowed to bully this slave!
307090.home: Ah what a fantastic job you've done today, slave. Bravo! Bravo!
307090.login: If you sneak off without telling me one more time, I might just have to turn this place into a sea of fire.

605020.detail: That Veneto, she's not half bad for a fleet flagship... However, if she wants to move forward, she must learn from me. Hahahaha!

605020.main: There are two kinds of people in the world: those who are Littorio, and those who are not.|Isn't it lamentable, Commander? There are so many places in the world that yearn for light, but there is but one Littorio.|There is no denying that, though battleships once ruled the seas, aircraft have ushered in the beginning of a new era. This is a fact that not even I can refute.
605020.win_mvp: Trying to oppose me was your greatest mistake.
605020.feeling5: When you give to the world, the world gives back to you. So put your mind at ease. Pursue the object of your desire and grab hold of it. Because I, Littorio, deem you worthy.

401460.login: This world is so different that from what I was expecting. How interesting!
401460.mission_complete: Freedom and fortune only favor the hardworking.
401460.feeling3: Friendship, enmity, love, hate... these are things that I have never experienced prior to coming here.
401460.unlock: Are you the one who summoned me? I am... unfortunately, still without a name. You may call me Z46 for now though.
401460.feeling2: The journey to find a name has lead me to this place.
401460.touch: Being able to be touched is proof of one’s existence.
401460.touch2: If your desire is righteous, then why do your hands tremble?
401460.profile: Iron Blood Z-class destroyer, 1936-C Type. Four other sister ships were planned for construction, but only Z47 and I were built. I wasn’t even completed by the end of the war, and was scrapped without ever being finished. One day, I hope to be called not as Z46, but by a true name.
401460.main: I have experienced neither failure nor suffering. Consequently, I have accomplished nothing.|A name is not merely a label. It is also proof that one exists in this world.|The things I have yet to experience and understand are as numerous as the countless stars in the night sky.
401460.win_mvp: Am I too strong? Or are you all too weak?
401460.feeling5: To be needed, yearned for, trusted, and loved... "I" am a cloth dyed by your color. My beloved, please bestow a name upon me.
401460.lose: Go and boast to the world. Be proud that you have bested me even once.
401460.hp_warning: What doesn't kill you only makes you stronger.
401460.expedition: Waiting at the harbor for dispatched ships to return... is something I’ve ever experienced before.
401460.mail: Receiving mail is proof of the expectations and trust that people have in you.
401460.skill: The unworthy are fated to drown in this world.
401460.mission: Unknown beings and new acquaintances... let us sally forth to meet them!

502030.feeling4: Big sister told me that finding someone who can feed me is more important than finding someone I like. Since I like Commander and get plenty of food, there shouldn’t be any problems.
502030.propose: Does this mean that I should only listen to Commander from now on instead of my big sister? ...Make my own decision? Hm... then, I shall listen to both of you.
502030.detail: What are you looking at, Commander?
couple_encourage: Big sister! Do you want some buns?
502030.feeling1: Commander... are you one of those "bad guys" that big sister talks about?
502030.battle: Do I get any tasty food for winning?
502030.home: Whenever big sister is tired, the only way to make her happy is by giving her steamed buns. Do you want some, Commander?
502030.login: Commander, have you eaten yet? You can’t work on an empty stomach.
502030.mission_complete: So many rewards, Commander! Can we trade them for buns?
502030.feeling3: Big sister said I shouldn’t be alone with Commander... is it because she wants the buns all for herself? Then, I shall come visit Commander more often from now on!
502030.unlock: Commander? Big sister told me that commanders who can’t even put food on the table are no good. Can you support yourself? ...Then, how about me?
502030.feeling2: Big sister always says that we are too poor to have food in the pot, but every time I open the lid, there’s always food in there! What’s the deal with that?
502030.touch: Commander, do you also want a hug? I hug my big sister all the time.
502030.touch2: Big sister told me to beat up any bad guys that I come across. But what is a bad guy?
502030.profile: I'm Ning Hai, the first ship of the Ning Hai-class. Big sister told me to say this when I was introducing myself. Ah? I'm Ping Hai? That's right! Then... I'm Ping Hai, the first ship of the Ning Hai-class... I'm wrong again? This is so confusing...
502030.main: Socks? Big sister said we should spend less money, so we share one pair together...|Kung Fu? Big sister said we could earn some Coins by performing on the street, so I learned that too...|Pandas? On our heads? They're also sisters!
502030.win_mvp: Number one? Does that taste good?
502030.feeling5: I will be satisfied as long as I can be with Commander all the time, and just see my sister every now and then. Hmm? Big Sister would cry? Why?
502030.expedition: Commander, Commander! Big sister said that I have to tell you whenever a commission is finished.
502030.mail: Big sister says that checking the mail in a timely manner is a common courtesy! Commander, want to read these?
502030.drop_descrip: Ning Hai-class Light Cruser, Ping Hai
502030.mission: Big sister says that missions won’t complete themselves if I’m daydreaming. Does that mean they will if I practice kung fu?

202010.feeling4: We were distant sisters in the home country, so I'm happy now that we get to fight together in the same fleet. All of it is thanks to you, Commander.
202010.propose: Always be by your side... is it? I understand. If it's alright, I'll happily stay by your side~
202010.detail: Mmm. I'll leave it to you then, Commander.
202010.feeling1: Being unable to judge your distance with others is problematic, Commander.
202010.upgrade: I'm gonna work a little harder
202010.battle: Let's go, everyone. Be careful not to get hurt!
202010.home: Good work, commander. Is there anything I can help with?
202010.login: Oh my, Commander. Please take care of me today as well.
202010.feeling3: I'm thinking of taking a walk, but I don't have a companion... Commander, want to take a walk with me?
202010.unlock: Good day to you. I am Leander class' light cruiser, Leander. Actually, I have some differences from my sisters. Do you want to know what they are?
202010.feeling2: Oh, Commander, you're like a child. I can't leave you alone~
202010.touch: Hmm? Is there anything I can do for you, Commander?
202010.touch2: Sometimes... I have to endure things I don't like, huh...
202010.profile: I am the Leander class light cruiser, Leander. Me and my sister Achilles had worked hard around different countries. Please tell me about the things that I need to improve on. I'll do my best.
202010.main: Commander, are you tired? Do you want to lay on my thighs?|The place I used to live in was very warm|Aiiiiiiiiieeei!!!... Oh my... it's you, Commander-- Geez, you surprised me...
202010.feeling5: Thanks to you, Commander, the others have gotten along better every day... Right. What kind of gift do you want, Commander?
202010.drop_descrip: Leander-class light cruiser – Leander, Hull Number 75!
202010.mission: Commander, there are still unfinished missions.

304020.feeling4: Being able to see everyone's smiles at the banquet makes all the hard work and preparation worth it.
304020.propose: So this means... "We'll always be forever?" Thank you very much. I'll gladly accept it - however... If anything was to happen to us, I hope that you would consider yourself first...
304020.detail: Hehe~ Which do you prefer: matcha, or black tea?
couple_encourage: Are you still waiting for your sister?
304020.upgrade: Today's breeze feels more pleasant than usual.
304020.battle: Hehe, shall we go enjoy the festivities?
304020.home: Welcome back. The tea has just been brewed to the right temperature.
304020.login: There is nothing more relaxing than a banquet following a battle... By the way, Commander, I'm free after this...
304020.mission_complete: Hehe, shall we celebrate by holding a banquet tonight?
304020.feeling3: That Kirishima... She's actually quite the popular one...
304020.unlock: I am the Imperial Ship Hiei, second of the Kongou-class, reporting for duty. Commander, where shall we go next?
304020.feeling2: Ehehe~ Commander, is there something on your mind?
304020.touch: I can take you anywhere the ocean reaches.
304020.touch2: Hehe. Commander, have you not gotten enough sleep yet?
304020.profile: I am Hiei, the first Kongou-class battleship born in the Land of the Rising Sun. As an Imperial Ship, I witnessed the growth of our mighty fleet, and led our forces into the Battle of the Solomon Sea. Commander, have you finished your preparations? The banquet is about to begin.
304020.main: *Sigh*... Whenever Kirishima comes to a banquet, all those kids that tag along with her usually end up making a mess of things... |When it comes to warfare, wisdom and courage are equally important. We can't count on another miracle if we discard proper planning and rely on blind courage. |Commander, I'll be able to protect you, no matter the situation. Hehe, I am called an "Imperial Ship" because I have that capacity after all~♪
304020.feeling5: Commander, after tonight's banquet... will you be free? Hehe, please look forward to it~
304020.hp_warning: Commander... It's too early to give up just yet!
304020.expedition: Welcome back, everyone. Hopefully, none of you encountered any suspicious people?
304020.mail: Are all of these new letters? Thank you for your hard work.
304020.drop_descrip: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.
304020.skill: Be swept away by the raging waves!
304020.mission: Let's finish while we still have the momentum!

401461.drop_descrip: The bustling beach, clamoring with waves of joyfulness... experiencing this kind of summer is a first for me, but I don't dislike it...

206030.feeling4: I've been working hard, you know? ...Supporting big sister... taking on missions... transporting things... Am I a good girl? Am I a helping hand, big brother?
206030.propose: This... precious thing... Are you really giving it to me? I, Unicorn... will work hard... That's because... I like big brother a lot!
206030.detail: Big brother... do you want to know more about me?
couple_encourage: When it comes to supporting big sister Illustrious... I'll do it...!
206030.battle: Leave the rear support to me... I'll... do my best...!
206030.home: The fleet... returned safely... Good work, big brother. My lap is... alright, you know?
206030.login: Welcome back, big brother... Are we going to sortie for today as well?
206030.feeling3: When things become dangerous, Ugean will protect me-- It won't be dangerous because you are here, big brother? Ehehe. You are like my knight...
206030.unlock: I... I am... The Royal Navy's... Unicorn. ...Commander, can... can I call you... big brother?
206030.feeling2: This over here is Ugean. Ugean the Unicorn... is my friend... Ehehe
206030.touch2: If it's you, big brother... it's alright...
206030.profile: Royal Navy's... support carrier... I am Unicorn... I was born to support my big sister Illustrious... Later, I went to support other big sisters... but everyone treated me nicely. I worked hard in lots of different ways, you know? ...It would be nice if I become a little dependable... Ehehe, I'll work harder, big brother
206030.main: Desstroy Moad'? There is no such thing...|Ugean's horn... cannot transform, you know?|'Entee'...? I have no idea what you are talking about, big brother...|Will I, Unicorn, grow up to be just like big sister Illustrious one day?
206030.win_mvp: Was I... of great help to you, big brother?
206030.feeling5: Big brother... can I be selfish before you? Can I have you pamper me...? I, Unicorn... am actually not a good girl... Is that alright as well?
206030.lose: Outside is... so scary... Can I go back...?
206030.expedition: The big sisters out for commission have come back... Big brother... will you greet them?
206030.drop_descrip: Aircraft carrier – Unicorn, Hull Number I72!

206040.feeling4: Spending so much time with the Commander and my Elders has shown me a side of you I never expected to see. For example... Admirable person though you are, Commander, you do sneak away from your duties from time to time. Hehehe.
206040.propose: Having been born into a world of peace, I certainly can't say I am glad to fight... But to meet you, Commander, and to be assigned to your fleet, these are the things that truly make me glad.
206040.detail: My... appearance? Right, well, my name derives from a mythological creature, so that's why I look rather... fantastical?
couple_encourage: Elder One, it is an honour to fight by your side!
206040.feeling1: How could my beloved fleet turn out like this...
206040.upgrade: Thank you, Commander. I continue to strive toward the examples of my Elders.
206040.battle: Elders, let us strive together for victory!
206040.home: I'm learning a lot from how you and the Elders fight, Commander.
206040.login: Commander, I swear to follow the examples of my Elders and strive for greatness once more today!
206040.mission_complete: Commander, how should we handle the mission rewards?
206040.feeling3: It, it isn't really that shocking that I use polite language with the destroyer Elders... is it? B- but to me, those girls are also my Elders, worthy of respect!
206040.unlock: So this is the place where all my Elders who fought in the Second Great War gather... Greetings, Commander, I am Centaur, at your service.
206040.feeling2: Commander, would you mind introducing me to some of the fleet Elders? I don't much like being alone...
206040.touch: You want to try pulling my bowstring? Hehe, it's harder than it looks, huh?
206040.profile: I am called Centaur, name ship of the Centaur-class aircraft carriers. As I was constructed only after the Second Great War, I lived a peaceful life, in spite of it all. And so to me, all the ships of the fleet, even the little destroyer girls, are my Elders. I am at your disposal.
206040.main: By the way, supposing I really was a "Centaur," like a half-man, half-horse? Wouldn't that be funny...? What do you think, Commander?|Peaceful, carefree days certainly are lovely, and yet I can't help but wonder from time to time, why was I even born?|Serving as your secretary ship gives me so many chances to interact with the Elders. I can learn so much from them. Thank you, Commander!
206040.win_mvp: Commander, I think I'm catching up to the Elders, maybe, just a bit...?
206040.feeling5: I understand now that the others are ordinary people, just like me. But it's still not wrong to treat them with respect. ...Not only as their Childe, but also as their sister-in-arms.
206040.hp_warning: Just as the Elders do, I shall hold fast!
206040.expedition: I can hear it. A whisper on the wind... Hehe, just kidding. Huh? The commission team has returned.
206040.mail: Commander, some new mail has come in. I'll go fetch it for you.
206040.skill: I've learnt from the Elders, I'll show you their courage!
206040.mission: Commander, shouldn't you head out to complete this mission? I'll accompany you.

304021.detail: Which pillow would you prefer? The soft one, the hard one, or... perhaps you'd like to use my thighs? Hehe~
304021.login: Adequate rest is important for improving your performance. Commander, I've prepared your pillow. Tonight... enjoy the best sleep of your life~
304021.unlock: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?
304021.touch: Commander, the moon is beautiful tonight. Wouldn't you rather take in the beauty of the night sky instead of staring at me?
304021.touch2: Hehe~ Someone seems quite energetic tonight, Commander.
304021.main: Hehe, it seems like we'll be able to have a pajama party banquet. How about it, Commander? Would you like to join? |Good night, Commander. Don't worry, I'll wake you up when the time is right. |Ah, the plum blossoms shimmering under the moonlight... Commander, shall we go watch the petals together?
304021.drop_descrip: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?

502020.feeling4: You won't trick me this time! I'm telling you... Eh? You like me? Wait, th-this must be your new way of tricking me! Uu...
502020.propose: ... Since you trust me so much, Commander, why don't we plan ahead? The next focus of our fleet is... cost cutting! We've got to maintain the fleet by minimizing expenses, and... Hey! Don't run away!
502020.detail: What is it? You want to watch a martial arts performance?
couple_encourage: Ping Hai! Stop eating my buns!
502020.feeling1: As if I'd eat your buns!
502020.upgrade: I've got to work even harder to balance the fleet's income and expenses.
502020.battle: I'll never hold back against our enemies!
502020.home: I just finished steaming these buns. Why not relax and have a quick snack?
502020.login: Where were you? Lazing around again?! Did you bring me any food...? Hmph. Let's get to work.
502020.mission_complete: Rewards have been counted. We could buy a huge stack of steamed buns... *ahem* The list is here, Commander.
502020.feeling3: Don't always try to change the subject to buns when we're discussing serious business, Commander! Do I look like I can be bought that easily? Ooo... mmm.... So delicious!
502020.unlock: You're the Commander? Well, from this day forward, I'll take the duty of supervising the fleet. I hope you'll coopera... Buns? Thank you, I'll help myself.
502020.feeling2: Come on! What's going on with this month's expenses?! Why are these buns here... Have I eaten? Not yet... Fine, let's eat together.
502020.touch: What, you want to have a go with me?
502020.touch2: *sigh* I won't forgive you, even if you beg God for forgiveness and bribe me with a lifetime supply of steamed buns.
502020.profile: I'm Ning Hai, the first ship of the Ning Hai-class! In order to revive our nation's navy, we have been living as frugally as possible. If you waste our efforts, Commander, I'm going to be very angry with you!
502020.main: Even if you put a giant plate of steamed buns on the table in front of me, I won't relax...|Commander, I would rather see you and the fleet become stronger instead of just myself. |You cannot protect your loved ones if you neglect your training.
502020.win_mvp: Everyone must aspire to outperform me!
502020.feeling5: There's an old saying in our nation: "It's easy to go from a life of frugality to one of extravagance, but not the other way around." I hope that the one I like would not turn me into a frivolous... wh-wh-why would I say that I like you? You must have heard me wrong.
502020.expedition: Commander, the prior commission should be finished just about now.
502020.mail: Reading the mail in a timely manner is a common courtesy. Make sure to properly respond as well!
502020.drop_descrip: Ning Hai-class Light Cruiser, Ning Hai
502020.skill: I'll show you the power of kung fu!
502020.mission: Missions won't complete themselves if you are daydreaming. Let's get going!

102092.detail: Ah, don't you worry, Commander. Your invitation's got top priority to me.
102092.battle: Let's finish this in a flash!
102092.home: Let me join for the next sortie, Commander. It's not my style to just sit on my butt and wait around!
102092.login: Ready yet, Commander? It's time to go to the party!
102092.unlock: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!
102092.touch: What's up, Knight? ... A rose...? Just what I needed! Here, Commander. A little gift from me to you, darling.
102092.main: You wanna come to the party too, Knight? All right... you're coming, too!|Quite a few people have asked me for a dance, but I'm not a great dancer... Commander, could ya help me learn the basics of dancing?|*Phew*... You wanna go for something to eat when the party's over, Commander? I'll treat you, so don't be shy! I mean come on, we're friends~
102092.feeling5: Honestly, what with how people treat me when I wear this tuxedo, for a moment I considered acting more like a boy... But nah! In the end, it's obvious nothing beats being with you, Commander!
102092.mail: Hm? You brought the Commander's mail, Knight? Aren't you a clever dog! Good boy!
102092.drop_descrip: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!
102092.skill: Here's a present for you party poopers!
102092.mission: Commander, let's wrap up those missions pronto before the party starts!

404020.feeling4: Without realizing it, I've come to enjoy supporting both my sister and you, Commander.
404020.propose: A promise, huh? Long ago, I would have despised the notion of being tied down to emotions... but it doesn't seem so bad now.
404020.detail: My duty is to support my big sister who is always charging too far ahead. Admittedly, it gets a little irritating at times.
404020.feeling1: I assumed you were more intelligent, Commander...
404020.upgrade: It's fine as long as you haven't let power cloud your judgement...
404020.battle: Truth only exists within the guns' range.
404020.home: Welcome back. Please take it easy for a while.
404020.login: Welcome back. Ready to get back to work? I've prepared everything you need, Commander.
404020.mission_complete: Rewards distributed. Please accept them when you have a moment.
404020.feeling3: "The Ugly Sisters..." Though we were given that epithet for our achievements, it still hurts a little. Commander, do you think I'm ugly?
404020.unlock: Hello, Commander, I'm Gneisenau. Though my big sister is a bit reckless, we're actually an invincible team. I hope I will be able to sail with her as often as possible!
404020.feeling2: Is it urgent? I prefer simple and effective forms of communication.
404020.touch: Isn't it amazing how different people can come to different conclusions about the same topic?
404020.touch2: Commander, Anton is locked on, you can't escape now.
404020.profile: I'm Gneisenau. Though I'm not as bellicose as my sister, I'm still confident about my combat capabilities. As some of the best ships the Iron Blood has to offer, we hold the record of being the only battlecruisers to sink a standard aircraft carrier. Your faith in us will not be misplaced.
404020.main: You mustn't put off until tomorrow what you can do today. Please take that to heart.|One forgets the cruelty of war after being at peace for too long. The opposite... is true as well, isn't it?|Looking back at it, it's unbelievable that I would mistake that prideful princess as an old-fashioned knight.
404020.win_mvp: Sorry, this is war. There's no room for mercy.
404020.feeling5: The present flies by like an arrow, but the future always arrives too late. I hope that one day, I will be able to see the future that you and I create.
404020.hp_warning: All ships, remember to stay alert!
404020.expedition: A commission has been completed! Care to inspect the results?
404020.mail: Commander, there's mail for you. I'll leave it here.
404020.mission: A mission? Let me do some planning for you...

102220.feeling4: Commander, I always thought you wouldn't like me... and I'm glad that isn't true! B-but, how do we take our relationship to the next level? Wh-what are we supposed to do? I... I don't know about these things...
102220.propose: L-look, Commander... I'm only doing this because you're easier to deal with than my sisters. I only have enough patience to take care of one more person, so thank your lucky stars that it's you! I wouldn't do this for anyone else, got it?!
102220.detail: I set the trap just like the book said, but why haven't I caught anything yet? That's strange...
couple_encourage: You don't always have to put so much emphasis on the "sister" thing!
San Diego, quit screwing around already!
Juneau, you don't have to push yourself if it gets too scary out there...
102220.feeling1: I thought this might happen, but... I won't give up!
102220.upgrade: Now I can escort those carriers even better!
102220.battle: I'll keep the skies clear for you! Everyone, forward!
102220.home: Welcome back, Commander! ... D-did it go okay?
102220.login: Clock's ticking! We gotta get to work— Oh, come on! Here, let me straighten your collar. You're a mess!
102220.mission_complete: Mission complete! Feels pretty nice to be done, huh?
102220.feeling3: Um, I know I can be a little hard on you, Commander. But you get what I mean, don't you? ... Commander?
102220.unlock: I am San Juan, Atlanta-class anti-aircraft cruiser number four. I've served as a support unit for the Eagle Union's carrier fleets. You seem like a person up to your ears in work, Commander... so I now offer to support you!
102220.feeling2: The fleet is gonna lose faith in you if you keep spacing out like that. Commander, get your head in the game!
102220.touch: I know you're tired, Commander, but you don't have to whine about it. ... Okay, once you finish your work, how about I give you a massage?
102220.profile: I am San Juan, Atlanta-class anti-aircraft cruiser number four. I escorted many carrier groups: Enterprise, Saratoga, several of the Essex-class. I fought alongside them all. Let's just say I have a lot of experience in aircraft carrier support combat!
102220.main: Commander... are you daydreaming again?|Supporting a carrier group is just watching the skies all day. I wish supporting you was as easy...|My sisters haven't been causing you any trouble, have they? Oh, thank goodness...
102220.win_mvp: Victory is just a result of the effort we put into the fight. It's nothing to be especially proud of.
102220.feeling5: Um, I was thinking, if you have time, could we go out on a da... date? I know it's my fault for being so hard on you all the time, so I'm trying to make it up to you... Whatever I need to do to take us to the next level, I'll do it... Okay!?
102220.lose: Agh...! Go! I'll cover your retreat!
102220.hp_warning: I-it's just a scratch! I can keep going...!
102220.expedition: The resources from the commission have been delivered. Commander, why don't you... Umm, I'll go check on them.
102220.mail: I got your mail for you. Don't forget to check it.
102220.drop_descrip: Atlanta-class light cruiser – San Juan, Hull Number CL-54.
102220.mission: How do you still have unfinished missions? Well, since you're hopeless without me, I suppose I can help you out...

101261.unlock: Merry Christmas... Commander, Eldridge's outfit... cute?
101261.main: Commander, eat together... Christmas feast! |Commander, present? (Eldridge's hair twirls in anticipation)
101261.drop_descrip: Merry Christmas... Commander, Eldridge's outfit... cute?

502010.feeling4: My past? Those... are stories for your ears only, Commander.
502010.propose: This... is the power of our bond? Every moment we are together is like a dream, one that I am afraid of waking up from. No... it is no matter. From now on, I shall always be by your side.
502010.detail: Is there anything else you would like to know about me, Commander?
couple_encourage: I'm so glad I can be with everyone again, just as before.
502010.feeling1: Commander... You don't seem to be the one I've been waiting for...
502010.headtouch: I am no longer the crybaby that I once was.
502010.upgrade: If only I was able to become this strong sooner, then perhaps...
502010.battle: Ancestors... Yat Sen shall now do her part as well.
502010.home: Ahh, home is such a warm place.
502010.login: We meet again, Commander. Do not worry, I shall stay by your side as promised.
502010.mission_complete: Mission rewards counted and ready for your review... me? No, there's nothing I want...
502010.feeling3: I am overjoyed to be able to return to your side once more, Commander.
502010.unlock: This is the moment I have long waited for... I am Yat Sen, from the First Fleet of the Dragon Empery. Please allow me to be at your service once more.
502010.touch: What's wrong? Please don't have any strange expectations of me.
502010.touch2: To do such a thing to a woman... Surely Commander is prepared to suffer the consequences.
502010.profile: Yat Sen of the First Fleet of the Dragon Empery, reporting in. I heard that my sisters have already arrived. This time, I promise that I will not leave your side.
502010.main: Ning Hai's steamed buns? Mm... they still have the same nostalgic flavor.|Only by remembering the lessons of the past can we move towards a brighter future.|Sometimes, I miss those days when I used to train together with all my sisters...
502010.win_mvp: As the wind blows anew, I can feel my presence once more.
502010.feeling5: When I look at your face, I sometimes forget to breathe... What a strange sensation.
502010.lose: Give up? Why would I do that? I am not the same fragile Yat Sen as before.
502010.hp_warning: I have already witnessed true hell.
502010.expedition: The girls have already returned from commission. Aren't we going to greet them?
502010.mail: The mail? It's on your desk, Commander.
502010.mission: New missions have been assigned! I have finished preparations and am awaiting your orders.

404021.drop_descrip: These Halloween festivities are quite interesting, in a good way. Getting dressed up in these costumes isn't such a bad experience either. Commander, what do you think of my costume?

501041.detail: Commander, did you know? The Dragon Empery has an ancient legend about the monster known as the "Nian." During the Spring Festival, every household will hang up couplets and set off firecrackers to ward it off.
501041.home: Ah, Commander, welcome back... I'm making a lantern... Would you mind helping me hang it up?
501041.login: Fu Shun gets really excited around the Spring Festival, and will even drag Chang Chun and me around...
501041.unlock: O-on behalf of the An Shan class, we wish a prosperous, happy, and healthy new year to Commander, and to everyone here at port... Umm... even though I made this outfit, I feel a bit embarrassed wearing it... Eh? It looks good on me? Um... th-thank you...
501041.touch: I made this outfit myself. My sisters all said it looks good, ehehe...
501041.touch2: C-commander... if you keep messing around, someone's going to get mad!
501041.main: F-Fu Shun, it... it's dangerous to take apart firecrackers like that... Eh? You're doing an experiment? |This year's couplet... Um, Commander, can you help me brainstorm ideas? |Chang Chun, it's a once-in-a-year occasion, it's not good to stay inside your room all day...
501041.feeling5: During the Spring Festival, relatives will all gather to celebrate a reunion. Th-this year, I'd like to have a reunion with my sisters and you, Commander... is that okay?
501041.drop_descrip: O-on behalf of the An Shan class, we wish a prosperous, happy, and healthy new year to Commander, and to everyone here at port... Umm... even though I made this outfit, I feel a bit embarrassed wearing it... Eh? It looks good on me? Um... th-thank you...

301210.feeling4: *Sob*... I can't, I-I can't do it! ... B-but maybe I can hold a conversation with you, Commander...
301210.propose: O-overcoming my timid nature is going to take a lot of time, but I'm not anxious anymore... Because I know you'll always be with me, Commander...
301210.detail: C-Commander, um... I-I'm glad you're c-checking in on me, but...
couple_encourage: F-follow me!
301210.feeling1: C-Commander, i-if you get any closer then I'll s-shoot you!
301210.upgrade: I hope I can be of service to everyone...
301210.battle: I-I'll give it all I've got!
301210.home: C-C-Commander, g-g-great work...! I-I finally managed to say it!
301210.login: *Cries*... I can't possibly be a secretary...
301210.mission_complete: C-Commander, our rewards ha... Huh?! N-no, I don't need any!
301210.feeling3: Umm, C-Commander... C-can I ask you to be my... conversation practice partner...? I-I... want to make friends with everyone in the fleet...
301210.unlock: I-i-it's nice to meet you, I-I'm Hatsuha... U-um... P-please don't stare at me so much...!
301210.feeling2: C-Commander, do you think it's possible for me to get over my fear of s-strangers...?
301210.touch: I need to talk with you more oft... Eek?!
301210.profile: I-I'm {namecode:30}, first ship of t-the {namecode:30}-class... I-I served in the north, together with my s-sisters from Destroyer Division 21... I didn't achieve much, b-b-but I tried my best...
301210.main: I miss my sisters so much...|C-Commander... p-please don't stare at me so much...|I-I'm quite timid, b-but I'll work really hard! ... I hope...
301210.feeling5: C-Commander! I-I just managed to have a normal conversation with someone else! I'm so relieved... I-it's all thanks to you, Commander...
301210.lose: *Cries*... I really am not suited for combat...
301210.expedition: Commander, um, the commission team is back... I-I should go greet them? N-n-n-no, there's no way!
301210.skill: P-please get out of the way, everyone...!
301210.mission: C-Commander! Um, well... you shouldn't ignore your m-missions!

408080.feeling4: Bulldog's really smart. Playing with her is fun. Next time, you should come play with us tooooo.
408080.propose: Commander is so nice to me. I love you. U-110's gonna bite anyone who messes with you. U-110's scaaaryyy. Raaaaaawr!
408080.detail: I'm not a garlic bulb, I'm a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Raaaawr.
408080.feeling1: Why won't you play with me...
408080.home: Commander, your office is so booooring.
408080.login: Commander, did you bring swirly-whirly candies?
408080.mission_complete: Rawr! I've brought the mission rewaaaaards.
408080.feeling3: Believe it or not, this hairstyle was born with meeeee. Mhm, I'm a shaaaark. Raaaawr!
408080.unlock: Raaaawr. U-110 is a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Mess with me and I'll bite yooouuu.
408080.feeling2: You mean my Enigma machine doesn't have any use anymore? Okey-dokey, then let's play a game of decipheriiiing.
408080.touch: Commander, I'll give you a swirly-whirly if you play with meeee.
408080.profile: I'm U-110, Iron Blood Type IXB submarine, and I'm really good at commerce raiding. The Enigma machine I've got in my backpack is awesome. I'm awesome too, I just left my codebooks and charts behind...
408080.main: Codebooks, codebooks... Oops, I forgot them in the dorm.|Commander, let's plaaaaay. Leeeeetttt'ssss plaaaaaayyyy.|I got lectured for pretending to be a shark... But I still had fun.
408080.win_mvp: Raaaawr. U-110 scared the enemies awaaaay.
408080.feeling5: The Commander is my friend. I'll give you some of my codebooks. That way it'll be fine even if I forget mine. Yup-yup.
408080.lose: Codebooks, where are my codebooks... Goodie, they're safe...
408080.hp_warning: U-110's awesoooome. I'm not giving uuuuup.
408080.expedition: Commander, someone's come back to pooort.
408080.mail: I'll take care of your encrypted maaaail.
408080.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type IXB submarine – U-110.
408080.mission: Commander, once your mission's doooone, let's plaaaaay.

408060.feeling4: Commander, hurry up and hop on! There's a school of incredibly rare and beautiful fish passing by today! Who knows how long we'd have to wait if we missed this opportunity!
408060.propose: Don't worry, Commander. As long as you're somewhere Great Shark can get to, call me any time. I swear I'll come for you!
408060.detail: You know about those Union girls who call themselves "Solomon Knights" or something? Well, it has a nice ring to it... All righty, Commander, I'm an "Undersea Knight" from now on, got it?
408060.feeling1: I'm going for a ride! Tschüss~
408060.upgrade: I feel the need for speed!
408060.home: Commander, want me to drop you off at the dorm so you can get some rest?
408060.login: Commander, just hit me up next time and I'll give you a ride, okay?
408060.feeling3: Y'know, I really want to have an all-out race with the other factions' subs. I just know it's gonna get my blood pumping! How about it, Commander, wanna do me a favor?
408060.unlock: Hey! You! That commander over there! How 'bout coming for a ride on my Great Shark? I'll show you a real thrillin' time!
408060.feeling2: When I put in my headphones and rev the engines, I can outrun all my worries. Lemme tell you, Commander, it's one hell of a feeling.
408060.touch: Hop on, Commander, and make sure to hold on to my waist tight! It won't be my fault if you fall off~
408060.profile: I'm U-101, one of the Iron Blood's 7th U-Boat Flotilla. I took part in four wolfpack operations. You could say that disrupting the enemy supply lines is my specialty - I even received a Knight's Cross! My hobby is going on long rides with Great Shark. Commander, wanna come with me?
408060.main: Ah, Commander, wait just a sec. I've gotta finish fine-tuning Great Shark. We can go afterwards. |Great Shark is land-capable, you know. Well, just not as fast. Don't ask why it works that way! |What kind of music do you like to listen to on trips, Commander? Have any recommendations?
408060.feeling5: Commander, look who's back! Hehe, seems like you've fallen in love with Great Shark, huh? All right, get on. Today, I'm going to show you a real special place!
408060.lose: Couldn't get out of the way in time...
408060.hp_warning: Looks like I've gotta pick up the pace...!
408060.expedition: The commission fleet is back? All righty, I'll go pick 'em up!
408060.mail: Hello! Your local courier U-101 has new mail for you~ Hahaha!
408060.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-101.
408060.mission: You have a new task? Want me to take you to where you need to go?

408041.detail: Hey, Commander, can we go check out the kitchen? ... Oh, they're really busy in there? I guess we better not get in their way...
408041.home: Where are you always running off to, Commander? Come play with me!
408041.login: I've heard parties are suuuuuuuuuuper fun! I can't wait!!
408041.unlock: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!
408041.touch2: Hmph! Don't think you're gonna get away with that!
408041.main: Don't give me that face, kitty. Here, look, it's my finger. It's over here! ... Now it's over here!|Commander, have you seen Lord Bismarck? Can we go look for her?|Om nom nom. Delicious! This is really good! Here, Commander, try some!
408041.feeling5: Awww, it's lights out after the party? But I'm not done playing. ... Hey, Commander, won't you play with me a bit more? Eheheh~ I love you, Commander!
408041.drop_descrip: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!

408040.feeling4: Waaahh! Why won't Lord Bismarck hug me? She said I'm too childish! ... Hey, do you wanna sub in for her, Commander? — Eheheh, you really understand me!
408040.propose: I hereby declare before Neptune that I will protect the Commander, no matter the place, no matter the challenge! ... Heh heh. I believe you'll find I'm more reliable than you think, Commander!
408040.detail: Grrryyeeaaaargh! Come at mee!! Haaaah... haaaah... sometimes I get stuck in war mode and need to calm myself down. Ahahahahaa!
couple_encourage: Lord Bismarck! Let's give the enemy a beautiful thrashing!
Sorry, I don't really want to be around you...
Tirpitz! Watch this!
408040.feeling1: Please don't make that face again... okay?
408040.upgrade: The open sea. I have arrived!
408040.home: Commander, I took out a whole bunch of books while you were gone and I kiiinda forgot where they go... Erm, sorry... Eheheheh...
408040.login: Welcome back! Don't you feel super pumped on a day like this?
408040.mission_complete: Mission complete! So can we go play now?
408040.feeling3: Commander, you wanna see how I dive? Heh heh, Lord Bismarck said it looked pretty good. I'm proud of myself too.
408040.unlock: Ahoy! Type VIIC submarine U-556 here! This is my home port, no question! Oh, right, is Lord Bismarck here?
408040.feeling2: Lord Bismarck! I'm here to play! Oh, huh...?
408040.touch: Come on, Commander. Can we go play with Lord Bismarck?
408040.profile: I swore an oath to Neptune himself, that I would protect Lord Bismarck from danger, no matter where she encountered it! ... But there are still some things I can't handle by myself. Ahahaha...
408040.main: Commander, if you don't play with me I'm just going to go find Lord Bismarck|Commander, let's go swimming! Don't worry, I'll keep you safe!|Commander, sitting too long is bad for your health!
408040.feeling5: Commander, you and Lord Bismarck are the most important people to me! Without you, I would lose all will to fight... so if you could stay with me forever, that would make me happy...
408040.lose: I won't fail like I did before... never again!
408040.hp_warning: D-don't lose control at a time like this!
408040.expedition: The girls are back from commission! Should we go greet them?
408040.mail: Beepbeepbeep! U-556 has received new information!
408040.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-556.
408040.mission: Ugh, there's still a mission to do.

408021.detail: It's not really my style to go out with anybody... But I'm worried about getting lost if I'm alone... Commander, you got plans today?
408021.home: Phew... The view up here on land isn't as bad as I thought.
408021.login: Ah, you're here. Me...? Pretty much the same. I just got back.
408021.unlock: I haven't seen much of the world on land... Commander, want to explore it with me?
408021.touch: I don't know my way around on land, so... You're my guide.
408021.touch2: How about I take you on a trip to the bottom of the sea? It's really pretty down there too.
408021.main: Nearsighted? No... there are no lenses in them.|If you're thirsty... You can have half.|My outfit? My friends picked it out for me. I don't usually think about that stuff...
408021.feeling5: Under the sea or up on land, it doesn't really matter... As long as you're with me, it's beautiful.
408021.mail: Mail? ... Is it that postcard we sent?
408021.drop_descrip: I haven't seen much of the world on land... Commander, want to explore it with me?

408020.feeling4: I can visit anytime I want? Thanks... But... For some reason, I feel like I can't really relax here... I'm always on edge...
408020.propose: I'm meant for more than just voyaging through the cold, dark oceans. My place is here, at the port, by your side... When I'm with you, even just sitting in silence, I feel... happy.
408020.detail: Are you sending me out? I can handle it by myself.
couple_encourage: Wolfpack... the hunt is on!
408020.battle: This is where you'll all sleep!
408020.home: So many people here now... It's so loud...
408020.mission_complete: Rewards are in... You don't want to see them?
408020.feeling3: So like, I can't really help with your work at all... But you'll let me stay here... You don't mind?
408020.unlock: Type VIIB submarine, U-47. I don't like crowds... If that's all, I'll be in my room.
408020.feeling2: Your office is very quiet. I like it here.
408020.touch2: You looking to take a nap at the bottom of Scapa Flow?
408020.profile: I'm U-47. I went behind enemy lines at Scapa Flow and sunk Royal Oak. I'm going to go out, sink the enemy, and come back. Just like I did then.
408020.main: Enemies nearby? Welp...|If you need someone to patrol, I'm good to go anytime.|Such a quiet office... I approve.
408020.feeling5: I've spent thousands of hours swimming through the dark depths of the ocean... But lately all I can think about when I'm out on a mission is the warmth and light of your office... I think... I think I need to be with you, Commander.
408020.lose: So this is how it ends...
408020.expedition: Looks like the commission team is back... There's a lot of them. I don't want to go...
408020.mail: New report is in... I hope the enemy doesn't crack our codes...
408020.drop_descrip: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-47.

107080.feeling4: Commander, let me teach you archery. At night, we can practice together. If you get tired, then we can stargaze. How does that sound?
107080.propose: Is this your answer, Commander? … hehehe, I am so very happy! Then—— “I am willing to give everything to you, my dearest Commander”—— Wow, I’m so shy,  i-isn’t this awkward?
107080.detail: Limbs... cams... stabilisers... hmm? Commander, do you require something? I'm quite busy with the inspection, so do as you like~
107080.feeling1: If you don’t want to get shot by me, then just stay away...
107080.upgrade: Oh, my physical strength has grown stronger, it's time to customize my bow.
107080.battle: Let me give you a taste of my Wasp battle style!
107080.home: Commander, what do you think, the outdoors is more comfortable, right?
107080.login: Commander, remember to knock before you open the door next time. Otherwise, I can’t guarantee that I won’t accidentally shoot you...
107080.mission_complete: Commander, come over here and take your rewards from the mission~ It’s too heavy for me to shoot it at you...
107080.feeling3: Someone saw a ghost on the roof last night? Hahaha, that was probably me practicing outdoors~ It’s very comfortable at night, no one bothers you, and you’re surrounded by stars. Commander, you want to come try?
107080.unlock: Hmm? So you are the so-called Commander? Ok... if there is enough room in your fleet, then is it alright for me join you~
107080.feeling2: I like natural but in actuality use a compound bow? Commander, you are stereotyping, this is called going with the times! And the use of a compound bow actually has a long history to it. You can listen to me tell you it all, in ancient times...
107080.touch: Zipper? Hehe, please don’t mind me. This is just more convenient for me to move around~
107080.touch2: Commander, say the word, where do you NOT want to get shot at? I’ll try to avoid it~
107080.profile: I am Wasp class carrier, Wasp~! The first thing I did was go on missions in the Atlantic, and I also supported the Royal Navy. Later on, when in the thick of things in the Pacific theater, I was sent to support my Yorktown sisters. But in the end, I didn’t help quite as much. After all, I was most afraid of torpedoes...
107080.main: Commander, where are you looking at, I am above you. Hahaha, indoor climbing is quite interesting~ | It’s said that the archers of Sakura Empire is totally different from mine. So I really want to see it. | Commander, if there’s nothing I can help with then I’ll go out and exercise?
107080.win_mvp: Hehe, I am very good, right?
107080.feeling5: Archery, combat techniques, and… that sea of stars night, this is all I have. Commander, are you willing to accept me as who I am?
107080.lose: Umm... it seems that today’s status is not very good...
107080.expedition: The commission fleet has returned, that’s good to hear. I also want to head out... Co-man-der~
107080.mail: Commander, did you get the letter I just shot to you from outside?
107080.drop_descrip: Wasp class aircraft carrier- Wasp, hull number CV-7.
107080.skill: Who said a wasp can only sting once?
107080.mission: Commander, we have a new mission. You can give me an errand or a target. But please no paperwork~

408011.home: I'm right here, Commander. ... Not hiding for once? Well, it's not like I can! Nobody could play hide-and-seek in this gaudy frickin' dress...
408011.login: You're LATE, Commander! Just how long are you gonna keep me waiting?!
408011.unlock: *Ugh*... I figured this bulky dress would be hard to move in... Huh? I look pretty? Aha, ahaha... You're makin' me blush...
408011.touch: You wanna hear me play the piano? Errm... I-in a bit, so just hold on a few...!
408011.touch2: Hey! You did that on purpose, didn't you?!
408011.main: This isn't wine, it's a soft drink! Don't believe me? Then have a sip for yourself! C'mon!|Err, you wanna dance with me...? B-b-b-but I have no idea how to dance...|This here kitty is my personal butler! Whaddya think? Is that awesome or what?
408011.feeling5: S-some people told me a serenade is a perfect love song... so I did some practice. Y-y-you wanna hear it? Whuah! Just don't laugh if it sounds bad!
408011.drop_descrip: *Ugh*... I figured this bulky dress would be hard to move in... Huh? I look pretty? Aha, ahaha... You're makin' me blush...

101070.feeling4: Want a taste of my popsicle, Commander? Ah, yeah, it'd be like an indirect kiss, but that's fine... Anyway, can I daydream for a bit and lean on your back?
101070.propose: My life's changed ever since I met you, Commander... I'm sure we'll get to do many new things together. But there's one thing I hope won't ever change: that I'll be together with you...
101070.detail: Sorry, can we keep it brief? I need a new popsicle.
101070.feeling1: (McCall continues licking her popsicle and acts like she didn't notice you.)
101070.battle: We have to fight? Guess I couldn't avoid it forever...
101070.home: It's kinda hot in here, got anything to help me cool down?
101070.login: Commander, can't I just sit around here for today instead?
101070.mission_complete: Help me pack up these rewards... Hey, can we have them sent to my house?
101070.feeling3: Tips for daydreaming? Empty your mind and don't think about anything. Don't forget about your popsicle before it melts, though...
101070.unlock: Hello, Commander. Just call me McCall. I like to sleep, daydream, and eat popsicles. Please assign me somewhere peaceful, will you?
101070.feeling2: I heard those Sakura Empire girls sit around and drink tea all afternoon. I'd like to try that some day!
101070.touch: ... Are you trying to encourage me?
101070.profile: I'm McCall, third ship of the Gridley-class. There isn't much special about me, except that I've lived as long as my big sisters. I'm just relieved know that they're doing well.
101070.main: We all get along around here, don't you think? Care for a popsicle?|Ahh... Hawaii was so hot. I felt like I was melting...|... Ah! Oh no! My popsicle melted.
101070.win_mvp: "Slay the enemy while your blade is still warm"... Is that true for popsicles as well? Oh, it melted...
101070.feeling5: I used to hope that my days of just eating popsicles and daydreaming would go on forever. But after meeting you, Commander, I think I might have been wrong...
101070.lose: Whoa, I got so scared I dropped my popsicle...
101070.expedition: ...Oh, everyone's back. I'll go get some popsicles.
101070.mail: *Sigh* There's no end to all this mail...
101070.drop_descrip: Gridley-class destroyer - McCall, Hull Number DD-400!
101070.skill: Let's finish this before my popsicle melts!

202140.feeling4: Commander, let me have your ear... *kiss*. I like you~ ... Yep. Such a thing would have to be done in reality, right~
202140.propose: With this, the bond of fate has been formed~ There's still a long way ahead of us, so let's take care of each other, darling~
202140.detail: Geez~ If you keep on looking at me like that, I'll be reporting you to the authorities~
202140.feeling1: Do you understand? Even the red string of fate is not absolute. I no longer think about anything concerning you anymore, Commander~
202140.battle: Such disobedient kids~~ They must be punished~
202140.home: Aaaah cease your attacks! I'm on your side!
202140.login: I'm going to do this and that again today. Please take care of it~
202140.mission_complete: I'm gonna take your share of the rewards too, Commander.
202140.feeling3: I like you Commander, but it's important for all of us to be together. I'm troubled~
202140.unlock: I am Galatea, the 2nd of the Arethusa class~ Do you believe in fate, Commander? It is fate that I meet with you~
202140.feeling2: It takes a long time for the bond to form after you tie the red string of fate. Do try hard, Commander~
202140.touch: Hehe~ Commander, you really like to engage in skinship, don't you? Well, just this once, I'm allowing you to continue a bit more~
202140.touch2: Ah... You're daring, Commander --Well then, do you want to hear my wishes?
202140.profile: I am Galatea, the second ship of the Arethusa class. I may not look like it, but in my service in the Mediterranean, I achieved some results~ You'll regret it if you underestimate me~
202140.main: Commander, I'm wearing new clothes today! --Hmm? I didn't say I'm heading out!|Commander, are you free? How about taking a walk together? I want to link our arms and be seen by the other girls|Hmm? Did you not hear that? ...There's no helping it. Lie down over here and let me check your ears
202140.win_mvp: You cannot escape from me! Be good, and accept~ your~ punishment~
202140.feeling5: The red string of fate was what made me grow from a seed, and you, Commander, were the one who made me bloom~ You're so great~ *kiss*
202140.lose: Hmph! ...I curse you to be destroyed by my allies!
202140.expedition: Commander~ *arms folded* let's head to the docks and greet the girls who went off for commissions
202140.mail: Mail time~ I wonder what reward I'll get for bringing it to you~?
202140.drop_descrip: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Galatea, Hull Number 71!
202140.skill: This has nothing to do with my fate~
202140.mission: Yes, let's see what today's missions are about~

305049.home: Artillery training and aviation training... Guess that's the whole package.
305049.login: Hey, please help me out with my training today!
305049.unlock: Aviation battleship Hyuuga, sporting new powers, reporting in! Rest easy, Commander, I'll show you my true post-retrofit power!
305049.touch: *Gasp*...! I couldn't sense your presence until you touched me.
305049.touch2: Prepared to pay for what you just did? You don't stand the shadow of a chance against me.
305049.main: Though battleships have seen better times, I will not give up!|Ise's still behaving like she always has... *Sigh*...|It takes a lot of skill to use planes right... I oughta ask for tips from someone with experience.
305049.drop_descrip: Aviation battleship Hyuuga, sporting new powers, reporting in! Rest easy, Commander, I'll show you my true post-retrofit power!
305049.skill: Main guns: ready! Fire at will!

101262.detail: Commander...won't you be joining Eldridge for class?
101262.login: Commander, want to listen to music...with Eldridge?
101262.unlock: Commander, do you like Eldridge...this way? Meow~...look what I've done to my books...
101262.main: Not being by the Commander’s side while at school, interesting... |Everyone at school gets charmed by Eldridge’s cute gaze...Eldridge is elated! |nil
101262.drop_descrip: Commander, do you like Eldridge...this way? Meow~...look what I've done to my books...

407011.detail: Now that I think about it, other than forcing me to wear this skimpy bit of fabric, what else is this summer season even for?
407011.login: Didn't we agree to go to the beach? Where were you?
407011.unlock: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.
407011.touch: Is it time to depart? Wait a moment, these shoes are a bit hard to put on... Come help me out for a second...
407011.touch2: Hmph... Commander, do you also wish to become food for this child here?
407011.main: Is there a nice vantage point on the beach to sit at? ...There isn't? Oh well... |I only wore this... "clothing" because you told me to. If you didn't come to the beach with me, I'd be... rather upset. |Eugen, don't rush me, the commander is still working. What am I going to do on the beach by myself...
407011.drop_descrip: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.

101390.feeling4: Commander, are you keeping up with your schedule? If you feel like you can't manage everything alone, please let me handle your domestic affairs~
101390.propose: Commander, would you like me to keep cooking for you every day, even after a long, long time? Hm, you'd like there to be fewer weird dishes? Hehe, I guess I can manage that~
101390.detail: Commander, please let me know if there's anything you need me for.
couple_encourage: Fletcher, I'm coming to help you!
101390.feeling1: Cooking for someone you don't like is suffering...
101390.headtouch: Being treated like a kid... feels a bit weird... ahaha...
101390.upgrade: Ah! An inspiration for my new recipe!
101390.battle: I have to work hard for Commander today as well~
101390.home: Commander, good work~ Would you like to have a meal? I kept your food warm.
101390.login: Commander, have you eaten? Should I prepare something for you?
101390.mission_complete: Mission rewards, huh... Should I also prepare something for you, Commander?
101390.feeling3: My cooking would be perfect if I stopped trying to study weird things? Well, that's a darn shame! If you ask me, the element of surprise is the most important spice!
101390.unlock: Hello Commander, I am the Fletcher-class destroyer, Mullany. From today onwards, we'll be spending a lot of time together. Please take good care of me!
101390.feeling2: Commander, what are your interests? My hobby is cooking - though sometimes weird stuff come out, it usually tastes pretty good anyway. Mhm!
101390.touch: Uhh... the black smoke coming from that side of the kitchen? Ahaha... ha... I have no idea what you're talking about~
101390.touch2: C-Commander... so you're also interested in the racy stuff...
101390.profile: The Fletcher-class is pretty big, so it's not strange that you haven't heard of me. Though I had my fair share of dangerous moments, I managed to return peacefully. Right after that, I even went to live the Dragon Empery for a while! Is that why you think I look a bit bigger? Who knows~
101390.main: Aww... I thought I followed the recipe perfectly, so how did it turn out like this...? |Commander, make sure to strike the right balance between work and leisure! It's not good to be lazy or overworked~ |Commander, do your best! Believe in yourself, you're the greatest!
101390.win_mvp: I'm number one? Um... as long as I can be of help to you, I'll be happy...
101390.feeling5: You feel bad for always imposing on me? It's fine, it's fine! I'm happiest when I can be of use to the one I care about~ so feel free to rely on me even more from now on!
101390.expedition: Commander, a commission has been finished!
101390.mail: Commander, there's mail for you. Don't forget to read it!
101390.mission: Work hard to finish your missions, Commander~

213010.feeling4: I'm afraid no longer. Being next to you, I'm willing to become the darkness to your light; And if that light were to swallow me... No, even if I was to be devoured, that would be fine too.
213010.propose: Shadows chase after light, and light embraces the shadows. I've heard of foolish lovers who erase each other, but who can judge another's love? Isn't that right, Commander?
213010.detail: I am not the harbinger of death... I am just..... guiding them after their times are up
couple_encourage: Terror, stay close to me.
Vampire, please imbibe wine - I mean, blood - with moderation...
Lady Warspite, I shall support you.
Saru Legion? What a fun name!
213010.feeling1: Commander, if you fall into darkness, know that it will be me hunting your soul...
213010.upgrade: The purer the darkness, the calmer my mind.
213010.battle: Please remain calm. The darkness will only make the stars shine brighter.
213010.home: The silence after a battle is divine. Take your time and rest.
213010.login: Commander, I'm always here, awaiting for your summons...
213010.mission_complete: Rewards are but worldly possessions. It makes no difference to me whether you collect them or not.
213010.feeling3: Whenever I'm afraid, all I have to do is think of my little sister. It gives me the strength to push on. Even though my sister can't be without me, I can't be without her either.
213010.unlock: Commander, is that you? I'm Erebus. I followed your voice and have come from afar.
213010.feeling2: It was hard to take care of my sister at the beginning, but I got used to it... used to being alone? I'm just used to the fear of it.
213010.touch: Allow me to channel forth the whispers of the dead...
213010.touch2: ... ... uh... ... I'm sorry, it seems like I was having an out-of-body experience.
213010.profile:
Erebus, my name, sounds surreal?
My predecessor was a ship which carried explorers to the North Pole and never returned... like a journey into the abyss.
Please pay more attention to my sisters!
213010.main: Did you just have an out-of-body experience?|I'll always protect my little sisters.|I have to say, this warmth, I don't dislike it.
213010.win_mvp: Allow me to harvest the souls of our enemies.
213010.feeling5: Where there's light, there's darkness. Wherever you are, I'll be near. This isn't fate but the law of this world... It's nothing, it's just something that I've wanted to say for a long time, if I ever found someone who I truly liked.
213010.lose: Even if you manage to defeat me, you'll never escape the infinite darkness.
213010.expedition: I'm not particularly interested in embarking on commissions... The other girls always say I see weird stuff. I suppose it can't be helped... Anyway, your girls are back!
213010.mail: Letters are what connect humans. Hold them dear.
213010.drop_descrip: Erebus-class monitor – Erebus, Hull Number I02!
213010.mission: You'll experience an eternity of restlessness if you die with incomplete missions.

405022.drop_descrip: I bet Bismarck must've been thinking about how to invite me to the party, but ended up asking you to do it, Commander. Hehe... Let's get going soon. It's best not to keep her waiting.

405021.detail: Commander, enjoy yourself to the fullest. Our hard-fought battles are for the sake of peaceful moments like these... and our hard-earned breaks provide us with will to keep fighting.
405021.login: Commander, there's no need to rush yourself. There is meaning in simply waiting for you.
405021.unlock: In the past, I never saw summer as more than a hot and humid slog... But now? My outfit probably says it all... Let's go, everyone's already waiting for us at the beach.
405021.touch: It's a bit stuffy... Commander, would you mind turning up the air conditioner?
405021.touch2: Even though it's summer... there are still some things you shouldn't do...
405021.main: As long as you're by my side, even looking off into the horizon is meaningful. |Some of my colleagues seem to mistake me for some unapproachable ice queen... Perhaps playing beach volleyball with them would help... |The sunset and the beach at night are wonderful views. When you're done with work, want to accompany me for a walk along the shore?
405021.drop_descrip: Summer... In the past, it was always just a hot and stifling season... But now...? Doesn't my outfit tell the whole story? Let's get going, there's bound to be a lot of people on the beach.
405021.mission: Even I can't get fired up about doing missions during the summer... because it's too hot...

405011.detail: Apologies, Commander. Am I acting differently from usual? At times, I don't even know which is the real me...
405011.home: Let us raise our glasses to the heroes who have returned from battle.
405011.login: How's your work coming along, Commander?
405011.mission_complete: A decoration for the banquet? Splendid work.
405011.unlock: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...
405011.touch: A dance...? Oh, no, I wouldn't turn one down, I just haven't been asked until now...
405011.touch2: C-Commander... don't tease me like that...
405011.main: Commander, would you invite Tirpitz for me? Apologies, I'm... still not sure how to ask her myself. |I can keep a lot of people satisfied merely by sitting here with a smile... but only because of my status as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood. |As a leader, I must sometimes say and do things that I do not believe in. Commander, I hope you never lose sight of who you are.
405011.feeling5: In front of my compatriots, I always had to be adamant, solemnly spearheading the march of the Iron Blood. To be the leader of the Iron Blood's indomitable fleet, I had to lock away the Bismarck that struggled to express herself... But when I'm with you, Commander, I can set aside that burden, just for a little bit...
405011.expedition: Once the commission fleet has finished dropping off their supplies, let's invite them to the banquet as well.
405011.mail: Even at the most lavish banquet, it is your responsibility as commander to be well-informed should the situation change.
405011.drop_descrip: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...
405011.mission: Having unfinished work will turn even the finest wine into vinegar. Isn't that right, Commander?

305051.detail: Commander, what are you going to do on your next day off? I-I would not mind hearing you out.
305051.home: Commander, do you hunger? Then do partake of this dango.
305051.login: *yawn* Oh... Commander? I desire a few more minutes of respite... Good night...
305051.unlock: I shall be hosting the commander today. Manjuus, I beseech you to help me look my best. I am... *yawn* a bit sleepy... Urghh... what is that ruckus out there? C-Commander! When did you arrive?
305051.touch: Commander, did you plan to invite me out? ... Very well. Our interests happen to be in concordance.
305051.main: Good timing. I require your assistance in locating my lost clothes... Just so you know, I did not misplace them because I was playing around, understood?! |I sometimes envy Mutsu... Even though I have my freedom now, unlike when I was placed upon a pedestal and worshipped, I can't be carefree like her... |Commander, you should come visit me more often if you're not busy. Though Mutsu and Kawakaze keep me company, this place is still too spacious for my tastes.
305051.feeling5: I-I'm only doing this because... I'm prepared to entrust everything to you, Commander! ...I won't let you take back your word now! I a-absolutely will not allow it!
