305051.drop_descrip: I shall be hosting the commander today. Manjuus, I beseech you to help me look my best. I am... *yawn* a bit sleepy... Urghh... what is that ruckus out there? C-Commander! When did you arrive?

405010.feeling4: Why are you staring at me? Do I have something on my face? I'm pretty, you say...? Um, thank you...
405010.propose: ... Commander, what kind of expression should I have at a time like this? I should... just smile?
405010.detail: Is there something on my face?
couple_encourage: Tirpitz... forgive me...
Eugen, don't go overboard with your games.
No one can stop the march of the Iron Blood.
405010.battle: Follow me, not Eugen. Come – we shall face our opponents, no matter how numerous they may be!
405010.home: You've done well. You've earned your rest.
405010.login: I look forward to working with you.
405010.mission_complete: I'm leaving the mission rewards over here...
405010.feeling3: You're not a bad commander... What? Is it so strange for me to give compliments? ... You're simply overreacting.
405010.unlock: Guten Tag, I am Bismarck. I have fought many foes on many fronts. You may call upon me whenever there is a problem.
405010.feeling2: I am not so easily impressed.
405010.touch2: I... am not good at expressing myself. Please do not tease me on purpose...
405010.profile: I am the Iron Blood battleship entrusted with the name Bismarck. Allow me to prove that Iron Blood engineering is the finest in the world, no matter the battlefield. Eager to see for yourself?
405010.main: Is there a problem? Perhaps my combat experience could prove useful? |"Operation Rheinübung?" I don't have fond memories of it... |Such a slovenly expression, Commander. Now! Lift your chin, puff out your chest, and let me see those eyes! Hut!
405010.win_mvp: Such honors may please a weakling, but I am strong.
405010.feeling5: I... know that I'm not the best with words, but.. I want you to know that... I enjoy being at your side...
405010.lose: For tarnishing my pride... next time, you will pay with your lives.
405010.expedition: ... The commission team has returned. I'll go greet them first.
405010.mail: Be diligent about checking your mail.
405010.skill: Truth can only be found within our range!
405010.mission: Those who cannot finish their missions have no right to stand on the battleground.

404010.feeling4: Hey there, Commander! I just went to train with the other girls. Everyone is full of energy, all thanks to how reliable you are. I'm really taking a liking to this place.
404010.propose: Don't worry. For the fleet, and for you, Commander, I'll learn to protect myself and be less reckless than before. But, as always, please continue counting on me for combat!
404010.detail: Only those who have not been scarred would laugh at someone else's.
404010.feeling1: Cowards have no right to stand on the battlefield!
404010.upgrade: I'm looking forward to the next battle!
404010.battle: Let us trample the shattered remnants of our enemies!
404010.home: Not bad at all. Seems like you're getting used to battle.
404010.login: You're back? Good timing. I'm just about to test my guns.
404010.mission_complete: Rewards? Hah, now that's what I'm looking forward to.
404010.feeling3: You've got a pretty nice fleet here. Being here makes me feel like giving it my all.
404010.unlock: In Scharnhorst's dictionary, the word "retreat" simply doesn't exist! You're the Commander? Let me see what you've got.
404010.feeling2: If only I didn't need to care about anything other than becoming stronger or defeating more enemies. But, reality isn't so simple...
404010.touch2: Stand right there, Commander. If you can take a shot from me, I'll forgive you...
404010.profile: I’m Scharnhorst. I will stand until the last moment of any battle. This is my determination, as well as my pride. Leave all the fighting to me!
404010.main: Those lightweight aircraft carriers simply can't match our combat abilities!|Do me a favor and remind our friends not to sail directly in front of me... I might not be able to resist firing at them...|"The Ugly Sisters"? Hmph, it's not a bad name... Sounds like a good name for this war, too...
404010.win_mvp: If there's anything worthy of my trust, it's my cannon!
404010.feeling5: I've never retreated - not because I'm fearless, but because I've always had a reason to keep fighting. In the past, it was for the Iron Blood. Now, it's for your sake, Commander... I mean, your fleet's sake!
404010.hp_warning: I shall fight until the last bullet!
404010.expedition: A commission has been completed. Seriously, you ought to let me and my little sister handle this stuff.
404010.mail: You've got mail, Commander. You're quite the popular one, aren't you?
404010.skill: Anton, Bruno, Caesar... Cannons at the ready!
404010.mission: Missions? Let's take care of them in one fell swoop.

403053.detail: A ballroom dance...? Sorry, but I don't really know how to... I just need to follow your steps? O-okay, then I could... give it a try.
403053.battle: I will not let you disrupt the party for everyone else!
403053.home: Not everyone in the Royal Navy is like Ajax. I can actually have a productive conversation with most of them...
403053.login: So this is where you were. There are so many people in the hall, and I was worried about what I'd do if I'd lost you...
403053.unlock: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!
403053.touch: Commander, am I in time with your steps?
403053.touch2: Commander, people are staring at us.
403053.main: Ajax... She's not planning something weird for the party, is she?|Everyone here is having so much fun... I could never even imagine my past self being at a place like this.|Commander, my friends are calling for me. Could you excuse me for a bit?
403053.feeling5: Thanks to all the friends I have now, I don't feel lonely anymore. And my encounter with you might be the happiest moment of my life. Ahahah~
403053.mail: I know the party is still going on, but you still have to check your new mail.
403053.drop_descrip: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!

213011.detail: I am still but a shadow. The only difference is, I've found a small, small thing to strive for.
213011.home: Commander, would you like some sweets to replenish your energy?
213011.unlock: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.
213011.touch2: Were you able to touch happiness, Commander?
213011.main: Commander, there's no need to be reserved. I still have a lot of chocolate. |nil|Commander, just being able to watch you like this, and give you chocolate, is enough to make me happy.
213011.win_mvp: No matter how long the night, the dawn will come again...
213011.drop_descrip: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.

102030.feeling4: Commander, a diplomat doesn't usually take on the role of a secretary... but I personally wish to deepen my relationship with you.
102030.propose: Thank you, now I have more confidence in managing the fleet's affairs. Hm? I may act on your behalf for a little? What a pleasant joke. ... At any rate, I will not let you down.
102030.detail: This information is confidential, so please keep it a closely guarded secret.
102030.feeling1: Commander, I'm thinking of resigning because you just don't seem like you're worth the effort.
102030.upgrade: Power is the foundation of gunboat diplomacies. Thank you.
102030.battle: Fire at will! I have you covered!
102030.home: Good work, Commander. I will make sure that the results of your last battle come to good use.
102030.login: You came just in time. A few files need your signature.
102030.mission_complete: Here is a summary of the rewards. Your confirmation, please, Commander.
102030.feeling3: It feels like I've been managing your personal affairs more than foreign affairs lately, Commander... Surely this isn't on purpose, is it?
102030.unlock: I am Brooklyn. I am an elite cruiser, so you may let me handle all foreign diplomacy matters.
102030.feeling2: Commander, my responsibility is to ensure that you have the upper hand in foreign affairs. Rest assured, I am an expert in that area.
102030.touch: Are you interested in my tanned skin, Commander?
102030.touch2: A diplomat is not the same thing as a secretary... Please, restrain yourself, Commander!
102030.profile: As the representative of the then newly constructed pre-war cruisers, I was put in charge of foreign diplomacy. That said, my firepower is never to be underestimated, so please put your mind at ease.
102030.main: It's important to communicate with other nations.|Please don't stare at me in such a weird way.|I may be a diplomat, but don't even think about underestimating my power.
102030.win_mvp: Now then, let us talk about reparations.
102030.feeling5: I wish to fight only for you, to give you the upper hand... Maybe I am no longer suited to be the entire fleet's diplomat.
102030.lose: Now we won't have an advantage during the negotiations...
102030.expedition: Though it may be tough for everyone, completing commissions like this will help raise our reputation. Let's start another one as soon as possible.
102030.mail: There's mail for you, Commander... Hm? Where was this sent from?
102030.drop_descrip: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Brooklyn, Hull Number CL-40!
102030.skill: Deterrence is also a part of diplomacy...
102030.mission: Completing missions is a good way to demonstrate our capabilities. Please take a look at some of the new missions.

403052.drop_descrip: I never thought that I could wear an ordinary uniform and live a peaceful life like this. Thank you, Commander.

201119.detail: Commander, listen to my bell~ It sounds super sweet!
201119.login: Commander~! *Giggle*... *A-ahem*! Don't forget to give it your all today...
201119.unlock: I've grown so much that I can't jump like I used to... Commander, are you surprised by my post-retrofit appearance? *Giggle*
201119.touch: Commander, I can help! Show me~ Hmm... change this here... and maybe here...
201119.profile: I'm the Royal Navy F-class destroyer, Foxhound! I started in the Home Fleet, got reassigned to the Mediterranean Fleet, then the Eastern Fleet, then lastly I was sent abroad! We F-class and E-class destroyers were the first to receive an enlarged design, so we have some pretty good growth! *Giggle*~
201119.main: It feels like you haven't patted me much since I got retrofitted... Commander, pat my head, c'mon~!|By the way, Commander, some call me "Qu'Appelle"~ What do you think? Does it sound cool?|It might be hard to quit my old habits, in spite of my growth... *Sniff sniff*
201119.drop_descrip: I've grown so much that I can't jump like I used to... Commander, are you surprised by my post-retrofit appearance? *Giggle*

304030.feeling4: Can you dance, Commander? You see, um... I was wondering if you could teach me how to do it...
304030.propose: T-this feels a little odd... From now on, you'll be my most beloved... H-how you "compare to my big sisters"? T-that's not at all what I was talking about!
304030.detail: I wish I was as popular as Kirishima... Well, kind of...
couple_encourage: Kongou, am I doing well?!
All those before us... will fall!
Bear witness to my bravery!
Kure Battleship Fleet, charge!
304030.feeling1: I've lost all hope in you.
304030.home: Well done out there. Did you run into any enemies?
304030.login: Nice weather today. We should head out so we don't miss our chance to enjoy it. Don't you agree, Commander?
304030.mission_complete: Kongou, I'm basically already an adult now.
304030.feeling3: After a tough battle, I feel like eating a whole bucket full of rice.
304030.unlock: Hello. I'm the Sakura Empire's latest fast battleship, Haruna. I prefer to use my fists over my blade, but I hope that won't be an issue.
304030.feeling2: Kongou, allow me to give you a shoulder massage.
304030.touch: Do you like Hiei's handmade sweets, too?
304030.touch2: Hah!!!... I'll keep my gloves on next time so I can strike you without getting my hands dirty.
304030.profile: I'm Haruna, the Sakura Empire's speediest fast battleship. I fought hard till the very end. Once more, I will fight with all my heart, holding nothing back!
304030.main: At last... At long last, I will have my battle with Wales...!|When you've got bravery and willpower, no enemy is insurmountable. Isn't that right, Commander?|Joushuu beef is some of the best around. Care to try some?
304030.feeling5: Commander, could I please be your dance partner for the next banquet Hiei is hosting...?
304030.lose: Gah... I'm sorry, but... a loss is a loss...
304030.expedition: All right, I should head out and... Huh...? Not yet...?
304030.mail: I like your voice, Commander. So... could you read this letter out loud for me?
304030.drop_descrip: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Haruna.
304030.mission: Hiei, what do you say we get some exercise?

101263.detail: These clothes, pretty. But hard to hug. Sad...
101263.unlock: Commander, Sakura Empire's New Year looks fun... Go together...? (Eldridge is looking at you expectantly.)
101263.main: Commander, hair bun, big... Want to touch it?|Commander, glasses, cute?|Commander, cherry flower. Watch. (Eldridge's lock of hair is taking the form of a cherry flower petal.)
101263.feeling5: Commander, hold hand. With you, go together to... (Eldridge's lock of hair is forming a heart.)
101263.drop_descrip: Commander, Sakura Empire's New Year looks fun... Go together...? (Eldridge is looking at you expectantly.)

202241.detail: Oh, is it that time already? I've prepared a few simple dishes. Commander, shall we invite the others to join us?
202241.battle: You dare disturb the Commander's vacation? You won't get away with that.
202241.home: What's wrong, Commander? Are you still preoccupied with work?
202241.login: I didn't think this swimsuit stood out, so I was surprised when you still found me right away...
202241.unlock: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?
202241.touch2: Commander, the others are still here.
202241.main: The sea is a tempestuous battlefield, and yet the beach is a relaxing Eden. What an incredible duality.|Beach volleyball? I've heard it's quite fun. Do you think I could give it a try?|The sand is so soft, so fine. It feels so pleasant between my toes...
202241.mail: It's the mail? Don't tell me our vacation is over already...
202241.drop_descrip: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?

10400020.feeling4: I can simply learn things instantly with a plugin? Oh, please, it isn't that simple! Even an A.I. must work hard!
10400020.propose: I am who I am now because of you... I believe I can relate to more people if I am with you. So... may I stay by your side for the foreseeable future, Commander?
10400020.detail: Please, feel at ease. Although my elegant uniform may steal your attention, I am still very much the intelligent super A.I. Kizuna AI I have always been.
couple_encourage: Takao, let us dispense retribution unto the forces of evil!
10400020.feeling1: Can I just drop the act now?
10400020.upgrade: Installation complete! Pardon, I meant to proclaim that I have become smarter.
10400020.battle: Please, everyone take care as to not be injured.
10400020.home: Phew... Kinda tiring to act refined and all... Huh?! Commander?! H-how long have you been here...? My tone of voice sounded odd? No, not all, you must be imagining things! Ohohoho!
10400020.login: Welcome back, Commander. Soon it will be time for our scheduled meeting. Let's get a lot of work done today.
10400020.mission_complete: A mission has been completed. Let us go and collect our rewards now!
10400020.feeling3: As I thought, there are more things I must learn in order to relate to everyone...! Commander, please grant me your guidance and support!
10400020.unlock: Well met. I'm Kizuna AI, the new addition to your base. I will do all in my power to be at least of some use. It is a pleasure meeting you, Commander.
10400020.feeling2: I make strenuous efforts each day to be a mature A.I. so I may relate to everyone.
10400020.touch: Please, do you not know uncouth it is to touch a lady nonchalantly?
10400020.touch2: You are guilty. There is no room for alternate interpretations. You are guilty.
10400020.profile: I am the embodyment of cuteness and etiquette! Please, enjoy the splendor of this smarter and more refined Kizuna AI!
10400020.main: Commander, Hood invited me to a tea party. Would you perhaps like to attend it as well?|Formal attire certainly aids one's composure... Belfast, if you don't mind, would you kindly teach me the Royal Navy's etiquette?|Commander, would it be agreeable with you if I uploaded videos from this base? I am quite talented at video making, you see.
10400020.win_mvp: Gotta hand it to myself: I'm perfectly suited for combat, too!
10400020.feeling5: It is thanks to you that I have matured so much! I sincerely believe it would not have been possible without your help! ... Thank you so much!
10400020.lose: How could an intelligent super A.I. like myself lose...
10400020.hp_warning: Something as trivial as this... will not defeat an intelligent super A.I.!
10400020.expedition: I have pressing information. The commission team has returned. Let us swiftly head out to receive them!
10400020.mail: Mail has arrived. It may be of urgent importance, so please do read it immediately.
10400020.drop_descrip: Well met. I'm Kizuna AI, the new addition to your base. I will do all in my power to be at least of some use. It is a pleasure meeting you, Commander.
10400020.mission: Commander, a new mission has appeared. Let us begin on our preparations at once!

213012.drop_descrip: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?

403043.detail: What belongs to my lowly animal also belongs to me. Therefore, the stronger my lowly animal's fleet is, the clearer the proof of my excellence is.
403043.home: Let's be clear here, I was not waiting for you. I simply can't show off the full extent of my grandeur as a master without the presence of my lowly animal.
403043.login: Still sluggish as always. But because I'm in a pretty decent mood today, I'll forgive you!
403043.mission_complete: Hmph... After seeing these rewards, I'll let you live.
403043.unlock: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!
403043.touch: Dancing? Aha~ I just knew you'd come to me with this request, so I prac... err, prepared beforehand!
403043.main: Lowly animal, you may offer your opinion about me and Graf Spee's dresses. Hmph, I bet your vocabulary doesn't include anything beyond "cute," ahahaha! |Ehh? Graf Spee is actually talking to people from other factions...? I hope she's not being bullied... I'll have to give them a stern warning just in case... |Tell me, lowly animal, why does everyone greet me instead of cowering in fear? ...Because they like me? R-really... Hmph. As a spiritual leader, it's only natural to be respected by all!
403043.win_mvp: You should feel honored to have the privilege of being ravaged by the one-and-only Deutschland while she is in a good mood!
403043.lose: I have a banquet to attend, so I have no time to let myself get dragged through the mud by you lot~
403043.mail: Getting mail right now sure spoils the mood. Let me see those!
403043.drop_descrip: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!
403043.mission: Missions? What mission could possibly be more important than accompanying your master to the banquet?

403042.detail: Lazy swine, don't cut corners. Anything less than a perfectly uniform application of sunscreen is unacceptable!
403042.home: What's with that lax expression of yours as soon as you get back... Ho ho, do you need your master to "tighten up" those loose morals of yours?
403042.login: Way! Too! Slow! Are you trying to get my pristine skin sunburnt?
403042.unlock: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~
403042.touch: To think that a plebeian would look at me with such a hungry, bestial expression. A lewd beast like this needs a thorough flogging.
403042.touch2: Ho ho, it looks like this lowly swine cannot even control its basest desires.
403042.main: Plebeian, fetch those two towels over there and wipe my body dry. |If your eyes wander any lower, they will get detached from their sockets. I say, there is no remedy for being uncultured swine~ |A lifebuoy? What would I use that for? Plebeian, were you not going to carry me on your back while swimming?
403042.drop_descrip: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~

201120.feeling4: Commander, I... I've always watched you-- Am I troubling you... with such a sudden remark?
201120.propose: To think that we've gotten to this point together, Commander... W-well, fortune has guided us... but it's also due to you guiding my hand as well. I will continue to believe in my own fortune... Thank you very much...
201120.detail: Commander... I worked hard but... am I still not good?
couple_encourage: Come on F-class, let's do our best!
201120.battle: Bear witness to the Wrath of GOD!
201120.login: Commander, d-did I make you wait? ...I-I'm... *cries*
201120.mission_complete: Praise be to God for blessing us with such wealth! *gets on knees and prays*
201120.feeling3: I-I have also wanted to talk to the Commander... Umm...
201120.unlock: Greetings, Commander. I-I'm Fortune... As an F-class destroyer, I'll do my best...
201120.touch: I... I'm causing trouble... aren't I...?
201120.profile: Royal Navy's F-class destroyer, Fortune. ...I was transferred to the navy of the Maple Monarchy along with my younger sister Foxhound. ...As an F-class destroyer, I have worked hard...
201120.main: Fortune... means 'wealth' in a way...|If I'm with my sister, I can go anywhere...|Saskatchewan... a new name bestowed by God...
201120.win_mvp: Victory... is a blessing from God...
201120.feeling5: I finally have the courage to can say this... The goddess of fortune has allowed us to meet each other...
201120.lose: Has God... given up on me?
201120.expedition: Commander... Umm, it looks like the commission team is back...
201120.mail: A new mail... Is it the will of God...?
201120.drop_descrip: F-class destroyer ー Fortune, Hull Number H70!
201120.skill: Uh, umm, you are all fated to be destroyed >.< !

403041.detail: Slave, come here... Do not fear, these little bats won't hurt you.
403041.battle: I shall engrave my name into your bones!
403041.home: You've done well for a slave. Come forth, I shall give you a little reward.
403041.unlock: For such a lowly animal, your taste is not bad... That's right, I am Deutschland, Demon Princess of the Iron Blood and Mistress of the Night! Plebeians, no, my slaves, I shall grant you an opportunity to swear fealty to me with a kiss!
403041.touch: Slave, offer your neck to me so that I may feed... Ahahaha! Imbecile, surely you didn't take me seriously!
403041.main: Imbecile! I only wore this costume as a hobby. Who gave you permission to serve me such a repulsive beverage? |nil|Slave, help me get off my throne. Shorty? You imbecilic swine, do you think this is funny?
403041.win_mvp: Scream in agony! Tremble in fear! Kneel before me! Ahahaha!
403041.drop_descrip: For such a lowly animal, your taste is not bad... That's right, I am Deutschland, Demon Princess of the Iron Blood and Mistress of the Night! Plebeians, no, my slaves, I shall grant you an opportunity to swear fealty to me with a kiss!

301180.feeling4: What an idiotic, troublesome commander you are, wishing to make everyone happy… I simply cannot let your stupidity go unsupervised.
301180.propose: *Sigh*… I never imagined a ghost could be brought here. Are you really just as foolish as you appear, Commander? Or have you seen too many of these strange so called "movies"? … Oh well, there is nothing wrong with this, so I shall keep your gift secure.
301180.detail: ... Touch me in the wrong way and you will die.
301180.feeling1: There exists no cure for your stupidity...
301180.upgrade: You certainly are a big fool, spending such precious resources on me…
301180.battle: Allow me to show you all my combat techniques...
301180.home: You may stare all you wish, but it will not make me start floating...
301180.login: Could one say "long time no see," perhaps...?
301180.mission_complete: "Rewards" have arrived… Ah, do not task me with collecting them, you may do it yourself.
301180.feeling3: I will come in the dead of night and devour you soul… I said, and you actually believed it? It was in fact my embers that chased away so many pests, and yet you thought I would harm you? You tremendous fool…
301180.unlock: I am {namecode:20}, the second ship of the {namecode:19}-class... I humbly ask for your kind treatment, Commander.
301180.feeling2: I am the polar opposite of {namecode:19}… If she is light then I am shadow. Commander? Yes, of course, you are a big fool. I do not hate her, but who knows if I hate you…?
301180.touch2: You have a thing for ghosts? You really are something...
301180.profile: I am the {namecode:19}-class... or rather, the second ship of the {namecode:20}-class, {namecode:20}. People mistakenly think my name refers to ghosts, but it is merely the name of a natural phenomena. I personally prefer to think of my appearance as a "cosplay"... That aside, I humbly ask for your kind treatment, you idio... my dear Commander.
301180.main: Floating…|I am bad at dealing with hotheads.|You're standing beside me because I have a "cooling aura"…? Are you an idiot?
301180.win_mvp: I never imaged they would be this weak…
301180.feeling5: *Sigh*... Would it not have been better if I could have been your guardian angel instead… Then I could always intervene… I mean, "protect" you when need be.
301180.expedition: I waited 1 whole minute for you, yet you did not realize that a commission had been completed… It really is true, you are a big fool who cannot do anything if I am not around.
301180.mail: You seem to have "mail"… I should not have to help you with this too...
301180.skill: O, will-o'-wisps, join me for this strike...
301180.mission: It seems we have a new mission… However, I do not care either way.

301300.feeling4: Well, Commander, what type of girl do you fancy~? Me? Maybe someone more refined? ... But is that really true? Right, I've got that on tape now~! Now the question is: who will I play it to~?
301300.propose: Commander, it ain't too late to change your mind yet~ Yeah, that's it, take your time thinking about me~ Hm? The door? Oh no, it looks like it's been locked shut~ What will we do~?
301300.detail: Hoho~ What about me's gotten you so interested?
couple_encourage: It's time for us to stand together again!
301300.feeling1: You're more boring than I ever imagined, Commander.
301300.upgrade: Yup, I'm just oozing with energy~ Hoho~! Now I can go on another rampage~
301300.battle: Watch out for them submarines and torpedoes. Full speed ahead!
301300.home: Look at you, back safe and sound! Reward yourself with a sip of my nutritious drink! Hey now, don't be shy~!
301300.login: Aha, you've finally showed up~! Will we be doin' anything interesting today?
301300.mission_complete: Hm? Payment for those duties? Right then, take care bringing 'em here!
301300.feeling3: My hobbies? 3 rounds of food and sleep and a bit of teasin' you. Hohoho~! That look there is what I wanted to see.
301300.unlock: {namecode:124}, First Destroyer Division ship number one, has arrived. Are you certain you're the commander? Then things are gonna get interesting from now on. *Giggle* Enjoy watching me do my work~
301300.feeling2: Commander, only rookies and small-timers judge equipment by how new it is.
301300.touch2: Well well, looks like your naughty desires are starting to show themselves. How about an exorcism for ya?
301300.profile: I'm {namecode:124}, {namecode:124}-class destroyer number one. I was a part of the First Destroyer Division. My name's got a mighty ring to it, don'tcha think? Hoho~! I fought in numerous battles in the Pacific Islands since the start of the World War, so me being a fleet veteran ain't just for show or me being whimsical. I may not look it, but ASW is my forte. Every time I think about my battle with that wolf pack my blood starts to boil~
301300.main: Winners are those who hold out 'till the very end!|Hawksbill! That girl couldn't beat me, but she put up a real good fight.|Those Fifth Carrier Division folks... they're pretty nice...
301300.win_mvp: You see this? This is what years of experience looks like!
301300.feeling5: Commander... Ya know, I like you~ Oh dear, your face is all red~ So red it's even reached your ears~!
301300.lose: Ugh... Should've known I can't keep up like this...
301300.expedition: Guess the commission team's back again all in one piece. Hum hum, splendid!
301300.mail: Mail, eh... It ain't an errand from the Union, is it...?
301300.skill: Sorry, ain't got time for one-on-ones.
301300.mission: Duties, eh. How's about we go give it a look?

403033.drop_descrip: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...

303010.feeling4: Yeah... Being able to live with Kako and seeing my sisters from the Mikawa and 6th Fleet was always a dream of mine. Commander, you've made my dream come true. That's why... I'll do anything for you!
303010.propose: I've never felt like this in my life before... But as long as I'm with you, I'll be able to feel this way more and more, right? I can't wait!
303010.feeling1: (Furutaka ignores you as she passes by)
303010.battle: I have to do well in this battle!
303010.home: Commander, I tripped again... Do you have a band-aid somewhere?
303010.login: Commander, please be more careful when you open the door...
303010.mission_complete: I bumped into something while getting the rewards... Oww...
303010.feeling3: Commander~ Oww! ...Ehehe... Thanks, I almost fell again. I'm trying to pay more attention so that I don't trip as much, but I was so happy that I let my guard down.
303010.unlock: Ah! Sorry for bumping into you... Huh? You're the Commander?! F-Furutaka, first ship of the Furutaka class, reporting for duty! Can you please forget what just happened? Ehehe...
303010.feeling2: Kako acts like that because she holds herself as the role model for heavy cruisers, but she's actually very gentle.
303010.touch2: I never thought you'd take an interest in me, Commander... Frankly, I'm a bit happy~
303010.profile: I'm the Furutaka-class heavy... Err, just call me Furutaka! I may not look it, but I participated in the First Battle of the Solomon Sea! I also helped my sister Aoba out a lot! In the end though, I rushed too far ahead and didn't make it back myself... Ehehe...
303010.main: Commander, Kako doesn't really hate you, so don't take it too personally.|Um... because I'm not very smart, maybe Kako should take my place at meetings instead...|Ouch...! Ahh, I'm fine... I just nodded off and bumped my head.
303010.feeling5: If you're okay with this... then I don't mind, Commander. But... I've never been in a relationship before, so I don't know what it's like. Can you teach me?
303010.expedition: Commander! Ah... that hurts! I'm fine... I just wanted to tell you that commissions have been completed.
303010.mail: Sorry, Commander... I tripped and fell while getting the mail and now it's all wrinkled...
303010.drop_descrip: First ship of the {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:53}.
303010.mission: A new mission, huh? Seems like it might be a bit tricky.

105100.feeling4: Not all problems can be solved by fighting? Well, I don't really believe that... but you always seem to find a way to solve things. After all, you are my favorite Commander.
105100.propose: You really treasure these strange rings, do you? ...But since it's your decision, I'll go with it! From now on, I will protect you!
105100.detail: Celebration? Honor? Nothing else except for battles will draw my attention.
couple_encourage: I will protect you this time!
105100.feeling1: A saying that I recently heard from my sister, “Never protest your loyalty to the weak”.
105100.upgrade: I really wanna try to shoot a volley from my main gun right now…
105100.battle: Dear opponents, do NOT disappoint me!
105100.home: Sigh, staying in port is so boring...
105100.login: I think I smell gunpowder, has the battle started already? Pfft... turns out it was only Vestal cooking.
105100.mission_complete: Mission rewards... Darn, what a waste of time.
105100.feeling3: The war cannot be won by a single person. Without true sisters fighting alongside you and a reliable backline supporting you, no matter how strong you are, your defeat is inevitable!
105100.unlock: I am Maryland, a member of the BIG SEVEN. “Fighting Mary”, yes, that's what they call me! I heard there are many battles ahead. I look forward to them all!
105100.feeling2: I don't know who granted us the title of BIG SEVEN. But if those two keep mentioning it non-stop, then the title should have some special meaning to it.
105100.touch: Commander, are we going into battle?
105100.touch2: Commander, our fighting power is not in that area of expertise.
105100.profile: Eagle Union Colorado class battleship, ship no. 2 “Maryland”. As one of the BIG SEVEN, I often attended various celebrations. I escaped the attack on Pearl Harbor from behind Oklahoma. After undergoing retrofit, I successfully completed counter strike attacks on the Sakura Empire Navy. I participated in Operation Magic Carpet and received a total of seven battle stars. Commander, I just saw gunfire over there...oh, nevermind it was the sunset.
105100.main: Fighting beside my sisters is the happiest thing in the world! |I hate foul play, only fair duels are real battles! |Working? ...I don’t know much about that, I’ll just do whatever you tell me to do.
105100.win_mvp: Haha! This is just the appetizer before the main course!
105100.feeling5: Look into my eyes, as my most trusted companions, is it even necessary to use words to express the feelings I have for you in my heart?
105100.hp_warning: Now, this is a fun battle!
105100.expedition: Even though commissions are an important part of the war, but I'm just not interested in them.
105100.mail: When writing a reply back, should I carry an anti-aircraft gun with me...
105100.drop_descrip: Colorado class battleship— Maryland, hull number BB-46
105100.skill: No matter how many times it takes, I will sink you again!
105100.mission: If I don’t complete the mission, then I can’t get a battle star.

900133.feeling4: I always believe there is nothing wrong with being ordinary. But after meeting you Commander, I want to change myself a little... after all, my sisters are all so charismatic~ Well.. Commander, are you fond of bunny girls?~
900133.propose: Well, your trust deserves to be rewarded... umm... Commander, do you like bunny girls?~
900133.detail: Being stared like that makes a bit shy...
900133.upgrade: I'll try to work a bit harder~
900133.battle: Don’t be overconfident, and try not to be so nervous while focusing on winning~
900133.home: Ah, hold on, your collar is all messed up. Stand still while I fix it... there you go~ (waves).
900133.mission_complete: The mission rewards were sent out, are you not going to pick it up?
900133.feeling3: If you’re only going by appearances, every child in this fleet looks cute. But in terms of personality, they all have their unique quirks. To be honest, I am a bit envious of them. (strokes chin).
900133.unlock: North Carolina here, awaiting your dispatch. Although I may seem to have a bland personality compared to my sisters. But as the saying goes, no personality is still a personality, hehe. Anyways, awaiting your orders, sir.
900133.feeling2: Commander remembers me~ Not that I’m boasting or anything, but I still have confidence in my low sense of existence. (smiles wryly)
900133.touch: Do you need help with something?
900133.profile: I am North Carolina class ship no.1. I can be considered the big sister battleship of the Eagle Union~ I don’t particularly like or dislike anything, so to speak. Even though I have fought in all kinds of engagements, I have not gained any fame... I am a little bit troubled by this.
900133.main: What do I wear inside? It's not something that’s so significant |If I think about it, I certainly have been to many places... seen many landscapes, and also parted ways with many people. |Sometimes I get so envious of my younger sister Washington and how she’s so energetic all the time.
900133.win_mvp: If the Commander gives me a few praises, then I will be very happy~
900133.feeling5: Do you want to eat something later Commander? And then you can accompany me to go shopping, if you want to get something then let’s go together. Then... hehe... let’s take a walk in the park? Commander, everywhere I go as long as I’m with you will be just fine~
900133.lose: Not so successful... let's try again next time.
900133.expedition: The commission is over, they should be back soon~
900133.drop_descrip: North Carolina class battleship— North Carolina, hull number BB-55.
900133.mission: It’s not good to leave tasks unfinished.

304031.detail: I think people will gawk at us if Kirishima and I walk around looking like this... *Sigh*... It's tough being popular...
304031.battle: Shoot... No time... Let's finish them, quick!
304031.unlock: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.
304031.touch: I always look forward to the lunch box Hiei makes for me every day.
304031.touch2: ... Do you want me to beat you over the head with my bag?
304031.main: I think I prefer working up a sweat in the sports field over reading in the classroom.|Gotta join a club... There's the karate club... Maybe that'll work?|I'm free all week after school. Why don't we hang out a bit, Commander?
304031.drop_descrip: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.

900134.feeling4: Lately, my smile has become more natural? Emm, huh (scratches head), I was recently trying to find a new hobby. While I was searching, I realized that being with you is not so bad… (whispers)
900134.propose: Wait wait! We’re doing “that”, right? Is this your new way of teasing me!... Damn, you bastard, I’m not sure if I should cry or laugh about this...
900134.detail: Hmm, you want to know how well I fight?
900134.feeling1: You are too weak, it’s no fun playing with you, go practice some more.
900134.upgrade: It feels so good to become stronger.
900134.home: I’m glad that you didn’t get hurt—— What?! I don’t have feelings for you!
900134.login: Welcome back... how does my smile look? (Forcibly smiles)
900134.mission_complete: Go grab the reward yourself, I’m not interested.
900134.feeling3: No, no, that’s not right. If we do it this way, won’t it end much the same like in the past? … Don’t try so hard? You sometimes say stuff like that… Hmm? That was a good smile from me just now?
900134.unlock: Hello, Commander, I am Washington... my sister told me that I cannot be so rough once I join the fleet, so I am practicing my smile. Darn, why must I listen to her...
900134.feeling2: What must I do to possess a good smile... think about the things I like? If so, I feel very happy even at the thought of winning against South Dakota... muahahaha...
900134.touch: Don’t touch me as if you’re trying to be intimate with me.
900134.profile: North Carolina class ship no. 2. I am Washington! The thing I like to do the most is to destroy my enemies. Recently, I am practicing on my smile. —— Battle record? I don’t really show off with such things, all in all, how’s my smile?
900134.main: My smile looks beautiful? You jerk... oops, keep smiling, keep smiling. Thank you for your compliments. | Hey, that rigid South Dakota is still the same. Commander, you see, I am cuter than her. | A true measurement of friendship is their actions and not their words, I don’t like people who are rhetorical in nature.
900134.win_mvp: Sure enough, I am happiest when all the foes are annihilated~
900134.feeling5: I couldn’t help but smile when I saw you, this is the first time that I’m feeling this way... although, I also have other feelings rushing towards me. I suddenly want to see your expression when you are bullied by me—— Commander, stay with me for a while. (Laughs)
900134.lose: Oh, I will not forget you!
900134.hp_warning: I won't let go of victories to my enemies!
900134.expedition: Your memory can’t be worse than mine, right? The commission fleet has returned, won’t you go greet them?
900134.drop_descrip: North Carolina class battleship— Washington, hull number BB-56.
900134.skill: Out of my way. I'm ready to fight!
900134.mission: A new mission? Haha, now my blood is boiling.

403010.feeling4: Huh? Who would ever have a crush on you? I’m only tagging along because Eugen wanted to have dinner with you. Don’t get the wrong idea, idiot!
403010.propose: Huh? Why must I wear something like this? Whatever... I’m in a good mood for a change. You’re going to take care of me forever? Hmph! Isn’t that what you’re supposed to do?
403010.detail: What are you looking at, idiot? Get out of my room!
couple_encourage: Who are you calling flat?!
Please begin your performance, Glowworm!
403010.feeling1: You piece of trash! I told you to stay out of my sight!
403010.upgrade: Hah? Did you think something like this would impress me?
403010.battle: Compared to Jutland, a battle like this is mere child’s play.
403010.home: Idiot! If you had already returned, why didn’t you come to see me? Hah? Who would be worried about you?
403010.login: Idiot, so you rolled out of bed? Haah? What are you fantasizing about? I only happened to bump into you while patrolling the port.
403010.mission_complete: Idiot! Hurry up and collect your rewards! Why are you showing it off to me?
403010.feeling3: Huh? Worried about me? Having an idiot like you worry about me doesn’t make me happy at all.
403010.unlock: Huh? You are the commander? Is the war effort going so poorly these days that they’re letting anyone become a commander?
403010.feeling2: Huh? You can’t even do something like that? Are you an idiot?
403010.touch: Huh? Did I give you permission to touch me?
403010.touch2: Huh?! You stupid, moronic, block-headed idiot! Go die! Sink yourself in the Kiel Bay right now!
403010.profile: I am Admiral Hipper, the Iron Blood heavy cruiser named after the undefeated Admiral Franz von Hipper. I have participated in countless battles and given them my all. The Barents Sea? That only happened because Admiral Kummetz was even dumber than you.
403010.main: Blücher, I will definitely protect you this time.|Hah? A novice like you wants to challenge my cruiser-commanding skills?|Hah? Are the Schweinshaxe and beer ready yet? How many servings do we need? Idiot! Is your brain just an ornament?
403010.win_mvp: Hmph. Just today, I shall allow you to praise me a little.
403010.feeling5: Huh? Who would ever fall in love with you? I’m only here to drop off something I found during sortie, per regulations. Huh?! A ring? Who would wear something like that?!
403010.lose: C-c-c-curses! I can’t stand this, ahh!
403010.expedition: You idiot! You still haven’t remembered what you forgot about yet?
403010.mail: Are you too stupid to realize that you have new mail?
403010.drop_descrip: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Admiral Hipper
403010.skill: Huh? Who gave you permission to resist?
403010.mission: Don’t get distracted in the middle of a mission, you idiot!

101392.detail: After studying abroad in the Dragon Empery and being exposed to their history and culture, I've learned to be a bit calmer. However, I'm still the same person as before... as you can probably tell from my cooking...
101392.headtouch: Commander, are you... interested in my new hairstyle?
101392.login: Would you like to have some soup dumplings?
101392.unlock: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?
101392.touch: The elegance of ladies from the Empery, walking with their parasols opened, is a sight to behold. So, I picked up a few things from them - want to see?
101392.win_mvp: The things I learned in the Dragon Empery came in handy.
101392.feeling5: Cooking for someone else... is a whole different experience. Cooking for you? Hm, I'd say that's a bit of a heart-racing sensation, hehe~
101392.drop_descrip: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?
101392.mission: Today's business is best done today, Commander.

305058.detail: I am able to smile from the bottom of my heart when I am here. Yes, I am very fond of this place!
305058.battle: For the sake of our futures!
305058.home: Waiting for a beloved person to come back... is a thing of joy as well, hehe...
305058.login: You are the only one who has the nerve to keep me waiting.
305058.unlock: It may be presumptuous of me, but please take care of me from now on... Is that acceptable? S-Somehow, it feels a little embarrassing... Ahaha...
305058.touch: I never knew that being touched like this... could bring me so much joy...
305058.main: I shall fight on! At long last I have discovered, what it is that I fight for! |I shall never forget... the warmth of the hands that pulled me out from the shackles of my armaments... |What will the future hold in store...? For the first time in my life, I want to know the answer.
305058.feeling5: My name is Nagato. Not the Nagato of the Sakura Empire, but of you only. Because you were the one who reached out to me and pulled me from the depths of my loneliness, I wish to always stay by your side. You... won't reject me, right?
305058.expedition: A commission has been completed. Shall we take this opportunity to take a walk around the port?
305058.mail: My familiars helped bring the mail in. Ehehe, they seem to have taken a liking to you.
305058.drop_descrip: It may be presumptuous of me, but please take care of me from now on... Is that acceptable? S-Somehow, it feels a little embarrassing... Ahaha...
305058.mission: I have arranged the tasks in accordance with your instructions.

402040.propose: I'm so glad that you returned my feelings, Commander. I'll do my best... not to faint in front of you anymore.
402040.detail: C-commander... Please don't stare at me...
402040.battle: Ahh~! I'm so nervous I could faint...
402040.login: Wel... welcome back, Commander. I've arranged your documents...
402040.mission_complete: Ah- Wah! Commander, your rewards have arrived...
402040.feeling3: I won't faint anymore after I've gotten used to it... Also, Commander, being with you... makes me really happy.
402040.unlock: Co- Commander... I'm Leipzig. I black out frequently due to malnutrition, but... I'll do my best to finish the tasks assigned to me...
402040.feeling2: Commander, y-you called for me? Ah... a d-d-date??! ... (faints)
402040.touch: Is this training for learning how to not faint? I'll.. see what I can do...
402040.touch2: Uuu... I really won't be able to move like this... what should I do?
402040.profile:
Um... I'm... Leipzig, the first ship of the Leipzig-class...
One time, I collided with Eugen because of some thick fog... I hope she doesn't still hate me...
402040.main: Eek! I think I saw something...|I'll... I'll try my best!|Commander... is there anything else I can help with?
402040.win_mvp: I feel stronger with Commander around...
402040.feeling5: Fishy... you're on lookout duty... I've got something very important to tell Commander... Don't let anyone in...
402040.lose: Wah... I'll be bitten... It's scary! I'm not going!

402040.mail: Commander, Fishy brought in some new mail...
402040.drop_descrip:
Leipzig-class light cruiser, Leipzig.
<color=#ffde38>Can be built after unlocking</color>
402040.mission: Commander... you've been assigned new missions...

203040.feeling4: My big sisters are so strong, if only I could be of more help to them... Huh? I'm doing a good job as well? Hehehe... I received a compliment~
203040.propose: Hmph, the Commander has finally noticed that under all that hazziness there is brilliance to be found! From now on I can be as lazy as I want. ... Huh? I can't?
203040.detail: My post-retrofit performance is very impressive!
203040.upgrade: Now I can protect myself even if I get lost again!
203040.home: Good work, Commander! Care for a cup of tea?

203040.mission_complete: Commander! How can you also be so forgetful and forget to collect your rewards?
203040.feeling3: Reconnaissance is a very important task! Huh, I'm losing focus? W-what are you saying? I'm just o-observing the weather...

203040.feeling2: Hmm, clear skies, so a great day to scout out the waters~ Do you want to come with me, Commander?
203040.touch2: ... Ah! Commander! If you were here you should have said something.
203040.profile: I'm the fifth ship of the Kent-class. Although I look like this, I can still pull it off when it counts. During the Battle of the Denmark Strait, I basically saved the day!
203040.main: My greatest accomplishments were done just watching the waves like this.|Commander, want to watch the clouds with me? I bet we'll see some wonderful things!|Don't look at me like that, I've been to plenty of places before!
203040.win_mvp: That cloud looks like a.... Oh? We won?
203040.feeling5: Even though it's nice to receive compliments, I am much happier just being able to support you the best I can, Commander.... Why is that?
203040.lose: *Cries*... If only I had paid more attention...
203040.expedition: That cloud looks like cotton candy... hmm? Ah, Commander. The commission team is back~!
203040.mail: Commander... hm... what did I want to say... Ah, right! New mail for you!
203040.drop_descrip: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Suffolk, Hull Number 55!
203040.mission: The weather sure is nice... Oh? Commander! You've got some new missions.

202112.drop_descrip: Ahem! I made this special candy just for Halloween! Here, Commander, take some! Wooaaooah! Wh-who put this pumpkin here? It, it was me?!

201250.feeling4: But that's all right. You may fancy me if you like, but if you don't, then it's... not *not* a problem...
201250.propose: Now that I think about it, we've been so straightforward that we've not even done anything romantic... But now at least we know each other better than anyone else. I say we let romance into our lives starting today.
201250.detail: Do you need anything? Or are you just here to chat?
couple_encourage: Everyone, try to keep up!
201250.feeling1: You are a halfhearted and lousy individual.
201250.upgrade: I will not let your efforts go to waste.
201250.battle: We must face our enemies seriously, no matter who they are.
201250.home: Don't overexert yourself after returning from the battlefield. Relax.
201250.login: Do you know how long you've kept me waiting, Commander? What's the meaning of this?
201250.mission_complete: Commander, our rewards have arrived. Well done, I say.
201250.feeling3: There is one thing I want to set straight with you; I'm not foul-mouthed, I simply say what's on my mind. For instance... do you have a thing for little children?
201250.unlock: Are you the Commander? My name is Jersey, and don't you forget it.
201250.feeling2: Commander, while we're not that familiar with each other, I wouldn't take issue with having tea and chatting with you.
201250.touch: What, you want to nuzzle against my lap? You can keep your fantasies in your dreams where they belong.
201250.touch2: C-Commander?! I-I-I appreciate your straightforwardness, but now isn't the time...
201250.profile: I'm Jersey, of the J class. While I have neither noble blood nor a particularly outstanding combat record, my personality is what it is, so spare me your complaints. What happened in Malta was just a slipup. But, admittedly, mistakes are mistakes. That much I know.
201250.main: I hate it when others underestimate me because of my size!|No one knows what's on a person's mind if they don't say it aloud. I do not like people who are roundabout.|I wish you would compliment me for being honest, rather than for being "cute." Not that I mind compliments like that.
201250.win_mvp: This is the might of the J class! Regret your own carelessness!
201250.feeling5: Commander, I'm a straightforward person, and I'd like my partner to be as well. So be open-hearted and simply say what's on your mind. In return, I will be sincere with you as well.
201250.lose: Ugh... You will pay dearly for staining my dress! Know this!
201250.expedition: Commander, a commission is done. You haven't forgotten about it, have you?
201250.mail: Your mail, Commander. Don't forget to read it.
201250.skill: Now's not the time to be taking it easy!
201250.mission: Stop pretending like you haven't seen the new missions and get them done already.

202152.drop_descrip: I've always believed that music is unique in its power to touch one's heart, so I decided to learn the violin. Commander, please enjoy my performance.

107034.detail: I spent a lot of time learning things about the sea! If you have a marine-related question, just ask, Commander! Professor Sara can teach you anything! Ehehe♪
107034.battle: Sister Sara won't forgive those who would destroy the peace of the seas! Go forth~!
107034.login: Whoosh! Ehehe~ Did you like our passionate welcoming fanfare?
107034.unlock: Friends of the blue sea and sky, your guardian angel and idol Sara has arrived! Ehehe~ Commander, join me in protecting the beauty of the blue seas!

107034.main: It feels great to pet these cuties! Don't you wanna give it a try as well, Commander?|The sea is colored navy blue, and in this moment, Sara is a true marine idol! Heheh♪|Oh yeah, I saw a seal while on patrol the other day! You should come see it with me next time, Commander!
107034.drop_descrip: Friends of the blue sea and sky, your guardian angel and idol Sara has arrived! Ehehe~ Commander, join me in protecting the beauty of the blue seas!

107019.detail: Commander, if you run into a mental problem, you have to solve it on your own. Staring at me won't help you.

107019.main: If we make a little progress each day, we'll be sure to achieve great results one day|This fleet feels different from when I first came. With your hard work, Commander, we can do anything.|We have to punish naughty children. Don't you agree, Commander?
107019.drop_descrip: Listen carefully or I'll step on you!

305060.feeling4: Commander, can we play? Umm, if you've got work to do, I can come back later. I have so much to ask, and also so, sooo much I wanna tell you!
305060.propose: So this means we'll be together as one? That's amazing! It really does feel like I'm together with you when I look at this ring! Why's that?
305060.detail: Commander, help me inspect my third turret!
couple_encourage: Nagato~! Let's give it all we've got!
305060.upgrade: I'll give it all I've got!

305060.login: Oh, hi, Commander! Something I don't understand happened while you were away! Why do... (Mutsu began asking a series of questions.)

305060.feeling3: I know some things you're happier if you don't know about, but... I still want to know! Besides, aren't there lots of things you're happier if you do know about them?

305060.feeling2: Ever since Nagato and I were at Hashira Island, I've wondered... Why is the sky blue? Why can birds fly? Why do we fight? ... There are so many things I wonder...
305060.touch2: Commander, why are you touching me? What's the meaning behind it?
305060.profile: I'm Mutsu, second ship of the Nagato class! Nagato and I used to swap back and forth between being the Combined Fleet's flagship! Later on, Yamato took on the role, though! Isn't it amazing how much there is to see in the world~? My third turret? Uh... I think it'll be okay this time.
305060.main: Why do we need to write like this? Is it wrong to do it this way? Why?|I saw something interesting outside! Can I go check it out?|I wonder where those ants are heading... I wanna find out!
305060.win_mvp: Commander, look! I saw a really pretty fish just now! What kind of fish was it?
305060.feeling5: What I wanted to ask was... umm... do you like me? Are my questions annoying? And... Oh, right! I wanted to say that I love you, and I love all the friends I've made here!
305060.lose: Commander, it feels like my third turret's gonna...
305060.hp_warning: I want to protect my friends!
305060.expedition: Commander, some people just came back to the port!
305060.mail: This must be "mail"... I'll write a "mail" to you, so send me a "reply" later!
305060.skill: Mr. Kitty, hang on tight! I'm gonna get serious!
305060.mission: Commander, what's this mission about? ... What about this one?

303113.detail: Oh no, the ink... Commander, don't step on the paper!

303113.touch2: Commander?! I-I won't be able to write like this...!

303113.drop_descrip: Calligraphy is also a form of self-cultivation, so I am instructing the children... Commander, would you also like to join?

couple_encourage: Let's have our devilish duet! Huh?! Fünf, come baaack!

401360.feeling3: Heheh~ allow me to engrave the seal of the Devilish Idol upon your flesh! W-wait, I'm not done making the stamp yet!

401360.touch2: You'll get hexed for casually touching the Devilish Idol's body!
401360.profile: I am the Bremen-born destroyer Z36, known by many as the Devilish Idol! My friends and I travelled throughout the Baltic Sea, but eventually I was dragged into that deep, black abyss... Hmph. In any case, I'll bring you victory with my powers of bewitchment!

401360.mail: A letter from one of my worshippers? Hmph... it's addressed to you, Commander.
401360.skill: I'll engrave my devilish powers of bewitchment upon your body!

102160.feeling4: Sidling up to me this closely... Are you trying to smell my hair? Hehe, how is it? Does it remind you of the sea breeze?
102160.propose: Do you feel honored? You've managed to earn my recognition. From here on out, I'll have high expectations for you, so don't let me down~

couple_encourage: At long last, we're finally able to fight together. Follow my lead!
102160.feeling1: Hmph. If it's about me ignoring you, you brought this upon yourself!
102160.upgrade: I wonder if I'll be even better at my escort duties now?
102160.battle: Let's go! I want to see everyone at their best!
102160.home: Hehe, not bad. But don't get too cocky. There are still many trials ahead of us.

102160.mission_complete: You've earned these rewards. Take a look when you have time.
102160.feeling3: Who can blame you for being so captivated by me? Very well, I'll allow you to gawk a bit longer.

102160.feeling2: Next, I'll handle the paperwork and review the training plans. Commander, make sure to check my work properly. Don't slow me down, got it?
102160.touch: Hm? You'd like to see me while I'm training? Very well... you'd better burn this into your eyes!
102160.touch2: If you don't unhand me this instant, I'll make you regret it~
102160.profile: I am the Omaha-class light cruiser, Memphis. I've hosted some very famous people, as well as served as flagship of the fleet in the Royal front. Make sure you carefully observe my every move!
102160.main: Capturing everyone's attention with my brilliant performance at Naval Reviews - that's the way I like to do things. |Because of my hectic schedule, I never got much time to relax back in port... But that's fine, someone like me ought to be busy, wouldn't you agree~? |You want me to bring you back a souvenir next time? Should you really be asking that while you still have work to do?
102160.win_mvp: Hmph! Did you witness that? That's the glory that only I can bring to bear~
102160.feeling5: You feel uneasy when I'm not around? Don't worry, I'll always be here to escort you. As a matter of fact, you should make sure to always be around me.
102160.lose: To think that I would lose... how unsightly!
102160.hp_warning: We can't afford to be careless!
102160.expedition: The commission fleet has returned. Don't forget to check the performance records later.
102160.mail: Please go get the mail. I expect some good news.
102160.drop_descrip: Omaha-class light cruiser – Memphis, Hull Number CL-12.
102160.skill: Leave the escort duties to me!
102160.mission: If there are any missions left, take care of them right away. Don't procrastinate... Hey, I'm talking to you, Commander!

305061.detail: Commander, both now and back during the Warring States Period, why do people fight...?
305061.home: Great work on the expedition, Commander!
305061.mission_complete: Commander, how many koku are the mission rewards worth? And what is a koku?

305061.touch: Hiyaaah! ... Hmm, Commander, how do I learn to look cool while swinging my sword like Takao?
305061.main: Commander, why is it that Nagato wants to play with us, but won't say it? Come along, let's invite her to play!|Commander, hey, listen, I know about this massive castle tower! Let's go exploring inside it together!|Commander, Commander! Tell me more stories about the Warring States Period!
305061.win_mvp: Commander, when I imagine I'm an amazing general, my battles somehow get way easier! Why's that?
305061.expedition: Commander, I read in a book that having stuff is important in war! Remember to frequently claim your rewards!
305061.mail: Commander, you have new mail! Is it a report from Mitsu-what's-his-name?
305061.drop_descrip: Commander, check it out! "Nothing can stop me!" Urakaze made it for me! Now I can play warring states with her! Heheh, you should know I'm a force to be reckoned with! Can't you come play with us? Why?

401251.detail: Mr. Anchor has to sit out in the sun as well, or he will get moldy.
401251.home: Commander, which girl are you staring at this time?
401251.login: Phew... It's been a long time since I've been able to enjoy such a refreshing breeze.
401251.unlock: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?
401251.touch: I'm not tired yet, there's no need for you to massage- Ooh... that feels pretty good...
401251.main: Volleyball? Or how about swimming! I won't lose, no matter what you pick! |Liven up! Don't tell me you're tired already! |It's time to let these Royals witness the tactics and teamwork of the Iron Blood! Heheh~
401251.drop_descrip: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?

401250.feeling4: Recently, I've become more and more conscious of the commander. When we are together, I simply can't seem to calm down. Mr. Anchor... what should I do...?
401250.propose: So, you heard everything that I said to Mr. Anchor.... Ughh, I'm such an idiot! However, I'm really happy that you chose to give this to me. Th-there's no going back on this!
401250.detail: Mr. Anchor, what must I do to become as outstanding as my sister...?
couple_encourage: Sis, let's do our best together!
401250.feeling1: Mr. Anchor... I don't want to be here anymore...
401250.upgrade: Becoming stronger... should allow me to get a little closer to Z23.
401250.battle: Z25, currently searching for enemy ships!
401250.home: Good work, everyone. Let's use this time to also check the status of all the equipment.
401250.login: You're right on time. Well then, I should also get fired up.
401250.mission_complete: Mission complete. Well? What are your next plans?
401250.feeling3: Now, all my peers see me as being dedicated and responsible, and want to sortie or go on commissions with me. Commander also feels more at ease when I am around. Mr. Anchor, I've managed to make it!
401250.unlock: 1936-A class destroyer Z25, reporting in. Please be at ease, I shall do my utmost in battle.
401250.feeling2: Even though I told the commander not to worry, I still worry that I won't be able to meet expectations or adapt to this new environment. Mr. Anchor, will I be able to perform well?
401250.touch: Zzz.... woah! Sorry, I shouldn't have been daydreaming...
401250.touch2: Oooh! ...If that was on purpose, you'd better grit your teeth!
401250.profile: From my sister Z23 forth, we were all assigned code names. However, no matter what I am called or where I am deployed, I shall fulfill my duties!
401250.main: Z23... is probably engrossed in her studies right now... |Research plans... commission schedule... Ugh... this is no time to be getting sleepy... |This thing here? He- it's really just an ordinary toy!
401250.win_mvp: Not bad, let's keep this same tempo going!
401250.feeling5: Ehehe... Haah, it's still no good. Mr. Anchor, sorry for making you act like the commander and practice with me for so long. I give up... just being like this should be good enough... Eh... w-wait... Commander?
401250.lose: This battle... I'll have to reflect upon it thoroughly...
401250.hp_warning: I can hang on a bit longer...
401250.expedition: The commission team is already waiting at the harbor. Shall I welcome them back?
401250.mail: New mail has arrived... it would be unfortunate if you glossed over something important!
401250.mission: Don't procrastinate on your missions. Hurry up and get them taken care of!

305023.detail: Banquets are a lot of fun! Next time, we should have a Sakura-style banquet and invite everyone from the other camps!
305023.login: Heheh~♪ Going to a banquet with Milord... Hawawa?! Milord, how long have you been standing there?
305023.unlock: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?
305023.touch: Milord, Milord, I hear that there will be dancing at the banquet! Would it be okay for me to dance with you?
305023.touch2: M-Milord! It's going to be troublesome if everyone sees us!
305023.main: Milord, Milord, what's this? And this? There are so many things I haven't experienced before, my head's spinning! |Milord, are you sure you'd like to take someone like me to the banquet...? I won't make you look bad, right? |Shigure, don't do anything weird at the banquet. You'll bother the others!
305023.feeling5: Milord, Milord, you've done so much for me, so is there anything I can do for you...? Whatever you want, I-I'll do it!
305023.drop_descrip: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?

401234.detail: I've been smiling a lot more lately? ... Well, that's because you've gotten so much more respectable.
401234.home: Commander, you don't mind if I cut a bit loose today, do you?
401234.login: Are you enjoying the party, Commander?
401234.mission_complete: This is... exactly what I'd expect from my Commander.
401234.unlock: Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just looking for Javelin and the others... Say, would you like to keep me company for a bit?
401234.touch: D-D-Dance?! ... Oh my, I never thought it might come to this... Commander, can you teach me how to do it...?
401234.main: When I see everyone's smiling faces, I can't help but think about all the hard work that got us here. How about you, Commander?|The four of us: Laffey, Javelin, Ayanami, and I... Who would have thought we'd all become such good friends?|Champagne? Oh, heavens no, Commander! This is just sparkling orange juice.
401234.feeling5: Erm, well, Commander! I don't usually think about things like this but, you know, tonight, I'm wondering, Commander, when I'm all dressed up like this, do you think I'm... well... pretty?
401234.lose: What can I do? ... I don't want to get my dress dirty.
401234.mail: Look how many invitations you've gotten, Commander. Aren't you popular? Hehehe.
401234.drop_descrip: Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just looking for Javelin and the others... Say, would you like to keep me company for a bit?
401234.mission: Just for today, Commander, I don't mind you putting off your missions for a while.

307031.login: Even though it's the New Year, there is still no shortage of work left to do.
307031.unlock: I tried wearing something a bit different from usual, but I'm not sure it suits me... Commander, what do you think?
307031.touch: Commander, there are some plans for the New Year here. Would you please take a look?
307031.touch2: Commander, this outfit was not tailored for the purpose of satisfying your depravity.
307031.main: Teaching the children how to write New Years' cards is unexpectedly fun. Just reading their innocent thoughts is enough to heal me. |Commander, I'm not some demonic taskmaster... As long as the work gets done, I don't really mind if you set some time aside to relax. |Commander, would you like to go visit the shrine with me?
307031.win_mvp: That's why I've been saying... even though it's the New Year, you can't afford to take it too easy.
307031.drop_descrip: I tried wearing something a bit different from usual, but I'm not sure it suits me... Commander, what do you think?

202019.detail: Mhm, Commander, it's fine to ask things of me every once in a while.
