301260.propose: Lord Commander... before my sister arrives, can I count on you? I can? Thank you... I will take care of the Commander and spend my entire life with you.
301260.detail: Umm... exactly what do I need to do, to be able to see my sister again?
301260.feeling1: Lord Commander, regarding tomorrow’s task— yes, I wish to confirm it all at once...
301260.upgrade: If only I could’ve been a little faster, perhaps {namecode:71} sister...
301260.home: ...Hmm? Is someone there? Sister, is that you? …Sorry, I was dreaming just now...
301260.login: Lord Commander, you’ve worked hard today.
301260.mission_complete: It would be great if our rewards can be confirmed as soon as the mission is completed.
301260.feeling3: Ahh, it’s the Lord Commander! Why do I have smoke covered all over me? I’m not sure, I was trying to make coke pancakes.
301260.unlock: {namecode:31} class Destroyer {namecode:32}. I am open to your guidance, Lord Commander—— {namecode:30}? No, please do remember I'm {namecode:31} class. This is something I won't back down from!
301260.feeling2: Sister {namecode:30} treats me gently, as if I'm her real little sister... but...
301260.touch2: Lord Commander, what are you doing!
301260.profile: Second ship of {namecode:31} class Destroyer, {namecode:32}. A lot of people thinks that my sister and I are {namecode:30} class, but they are mistaken. My sister and I participated in many battles in the South Pacific. We helped protect the 4th and 5th Carrier Divisions. We were greatly taken care of by {namecode:98}. This time...I will stay by my sister’s side until the very end.
301260.main: Rumor has it that we would be able to finish our mission before the pot of tea that we brew got cold? Eh, is this wine? | Even if there is only the slimmest of hope, as long as you persevere, one day you will make it a reality. | Is {namecode:85} coming? She has a mischievous look about her, I’m a little worried.
301260.win_mvp: ...Victory? If only my sister is able to see it...
301260.feeling5: A cool breeze is blowing, the whispers of the wind chimes in the gallery. Feels like a return to summer times with my sister... but, only this time it’s the Lord Commander sitting beside me.
301260.lose: Hmm… I have to bother {namecode:98} again...
301260.expedition: The commission is now complete! Lord Commander, would you like to try and build a new ship? Perhaps this time...
301260.mail: Lord Commander, here is your tea, cake and the latest mail.
301260.skill: For one day when we will eventually reunite...
301260.mission: Let’s brew a pot of tea first before we start our mission.

403040.feeling4: A lion doesn't concern itself with the bleating of sheep. But... I do find you interesting for a lowly animal. If you amuse me some more, maybe I will listen to your wishes.
403040.propose: I never thought the day would come when I pledge myself to a lowly animal. I've never felt anything like this before... but it's unexpectedly fun. Ahahaha~! From now on, you're my vehicle number two! You should be grateful!
403040.detail: It's times like these... where I simply must punish you.
403040.feeling1: I have no interest in you anymore... I should find myself a new pet.
403040.battle: I'm going to enjoy mopping you all up~
403040.home: Pay attention, you idiot! Just because we're back at port doesn't mean that you're done.
403040.login: You sure took your sweet time. Just where were you rooting around?
403040.mission_complete: Hurry up and fetch the rewards for me~
403040.feeling3: Lowly animal, root around for all you are worth to find something worthy of my attention. Ahahahaha~
403040.unlock: From now on, you are Deutschland's servant! You should feel honored. Also, don't answer me with "mhm." You will answer me with "yes, ma'am" from now on. Are we clear?
403040.feeling2: There is no thrill like waging war with a grin on your face! There's no way a lowly animal like you could ever undrestand that! Ahahahaha!
403040.touch: You just never learn, do you? Do you want to taste my whip again that badly~?
403040.touch2: Hmm? It seems like you're enjoying yourself... do you get off to this kind of stuff?
403040.profile: Hmph! I'm Deutschland, the first ship of the Deutschland-class! A prestigious individual such as myself wouldn't be sent into smaller battles. As such, it's only natural that I don't have many of these petty achievements. It's called spiritual leadership! Hmph! Lützow? ...Shut up! Like I'd care about that!
403040.main: It seems like I must speak in a way that even lowly animals can understand.|Hahaha! I didn't even need to fire my gun to scare off those cruisers~|If you insist on standing around like an idiot, I'm just going to leave.
403040.win_mvp: Even though the enemies were no big deal... what a pompous affair.
403040.feeling5: For keeping me amused this long, I shall grant you the privilege of holding me. Why are you still standing there? Have you never heard of a princess carry? Princess~ carry!
403040.lose: I'd sink to the bottom of the ocean before surrending to you animals!
403040.hp_warning: Do not underestimate the great Deutschland!
403040.expedition: Hmph, so our little lambs managed to complete their commission. What a pleasant surprise.
403040.mail: You've received a letter in that lowly animal language of yours. Fetch~
403040.mission: Mission! There's no entry for "incomplete" in my dictionary!

107090.feeling4: I won't lose to anyone, not even to Enterprise. But how do I get everyone to acknowledge this? Commander, if you were in my shoes, what would you do?
107090.propose: Once you've experienced the happiness of two people supporting each other, it becomes something you can't live without. Thank you, Commander. I no longer have to walk alone in my quest to prove my worth. I promise to always be at your side, wherever you go.
107090.detail: What would you like to know, Commander? I'll answer to the best of my abilities.
107090.feeling1: I wonder how Enterprise puts up with someone like you...
107090.upgrade: When will I be able to get jets...
107090.battle: All carrier-based aircraft in position, anti-air defense preparations complete. All forces, full speed ahead!
107090.home: The fleet has safely returned. Commander, I've prepared the battle report for you. Time is of the essence, so please review it right away.
107090.login: There you are. I've already finished preparing everything. Commander, give us your orders!
107090.mission_complete: The mission rewards have arrived. Are you sure you don't need me to go get it?
107090.feeling3: Jealousy? No, that's not the case. Enterprise is a true hero worthy of all the respect she gets. However, compared to her dazzling aura, I'm just...
107090.unlock: So this is where Enterprise is... A-ahem! I am Essex, one of the Union's state-of-the-art aircraft carriers. Commander, you can expect great things from me! I swear that I won't disappoint you!
107090.feeling2: I witnessed the end of the era of battleships with my own eyes. Will carriers share the same fate some day...?
107090.touch: Time to sortie?! Just leave it to me! Oh... you just wanted to chat...?
107090.profile: I am the nameship of the Essex-class carriers. Although I was built with great expectations, I was always overshadowed by Enterprise's success. If only I could have been deployed sooner...
107090.main: Everyone knows that the Essex class is strong, but still, Enterprise is all they ever talk about... *sigh*... |There are a lot of ships in my class. As the nameship, I have to do everything I can to be a good role model... |Musashi and Yamato? They were... yes, formidable rivals worthy of respect. I hope I can meet them again one day.
107090.win_mvp: Enterprise, did you see my feat?
107090.feeling5: I might never be able to become a hero like Enterprise... But when I'm with you, I feel like I can do so much more than just that...
107090.lose: I won't let it end like this... I swear it!
107090.expedition: The birth of the Essex-class would not have been possible without the hard work of the logistics teams. I have to show my gratitude to everyone.
107090.mail: There's new mail for you. Here you go.
107090.drop_descrip: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Essex, Hull Number CV-9.
107090.mission: There are still unfinished missions? Mind letting me handle things this time...?

605061.detail: Want me to make a training plan for you? ... "Cesare's training methods send nutrients to your muscles and away from the brain"? Did Cavour really say that?!
605061.home: Here, take this! Don't forget to rehydrate.
605061.login: The treadmill is free right now. Do use it if you plan to work out.
605061.unlock: Both exercise and war are at their core about willpower! Now, get ready, Commander! We're not finished until you're dripping with sweat!
605061.touch: Are you out of breath already? You've still got a long way to go, Commander.
605061.touch2: What was that for?! Don't ignore me, answer!
605061.main: "Inaction saps the vigor of the mind"... Who said that, again?|Jogging courses, fat-burning courses, rolling hills courses... Is it really this complicated? I'll just start with whichever seems the toughest.|If you feel stressed out, just let it all out on that sandbag over there. I can attest that it does wonders for the mood.
605061.drop_descrip: Both exercise and war are at their core about willpower! Now, get ready, Commander! We're not finished until you're dripping with sweat!

101080.feeling4: I feel like I can run even farther when I'm next to you, Commander. What an incredible feeling!
101080.propose: No matter how fast I run, I can't escape my feelings for you, Commander...
101080.detail: Umm... Why are you always watching me do my warm-ups? Do you like watching me sweat?
101080.feeling1: Sorry, I've got some training to do, so I gotta go!
101080.upgrade: Not enough... I can still go faster...!
101080.battle: Lets finish this quick before I get hungry!
101080.home: Rest now so that we can sprint faster later!
101080.login: Commander, want to do some warm-ups with me?
101080.mission_complete: Phew~ I'm exhausted... Save some Oxy-cola for me when the rewards arrive!
101080.feeling3: Want me to teach you how to run faster, Commander? There's quite a lot to it, actually.
101080.unlock: You can just call me Maury. As a track athlete, I hold the Union's speed record, reaching a maximum speed of 42.8 knots. Just don't make me run a marathon...
101080.feeling2: Commander, is it really okay for you to sit around all day? Get outside and do some sports!
101080.touch: Are you helping me recover? ... Thank you...
101080.touch2: ...!! Hey! There's a line you shouldn't cross when giving massages.
101080.profile: I'm Maury, the fourth ship of the Gridley-class destroyer squadron. Although I'm the youngest of my class, I'm also the fastest short-distance Union ship! I'm prone to getting hungry a lot? Well, they say that light meals make you live longer, don't they?
101080.main: Commander, want to work out a bit? Sitting for so long is terrible for your body!|I thought we were going for some long distance trip at Wake Island again.|I swear it wasn't my tummy making that noise!
101080.win_mvp: Like I said, those guys can't keep up with me!
101080.feeling5: Commander, how about going on a jog with me? I want to share the beautiful scenery I find with you.
101080.lose: ... I need to get back before everyone starts worrying about me.
101080.expedition: I need to get some exercise... Commander, a commission just got completed, so could you send me out on the next one?
101080.mail: You've got new mail. It's about that celebratory party, isn't it?
101080.drop_descrip:
Gridley-class destroyer, Maury, Hull Number DD-401
<color=#ffde38>Unlock build after receiving</color>
101080.mission: You've still got some missions to finish up, Commander! Put your back into it, it's the final stretch!

202160.feeling4: Oh, hey, Commander. I was just about to head out. Getting dressed right now, you see~ Ah, don't be shy, you can look~ Later, I wanna get a look at you, too~
202160.propose: Hey, is my makeup looking decent? What about my outfit? Reckon I look as pretty as it gets? ...Good~ I've never dressed for this occasion before, so I want to look as good as possible~
202160.detail: What's up, Commander? Missed me, have you? Hah, alright, have a seat and I'll get you some tea.
202160.feeling1: You need something, Commander? I'm kind of unavailable, really.
202160.upgrade: I'll do my part on the battlefield all proper like, so you can rest easy, Commander.
202160.home: What're you staring into space for? Is that your way of saying "I want a hug"?
202160.login: Had supper yet, Commander? If not, I could cook you something up.
202160.mission_complete: Mission rewards, hooray~! Done your job proper, I'd say, Commander.
202160.feeling3: Oh yeah, anyone in the fleet you fancy? Want me to assist you with them? Come on now, don't get your knickers in a twist~ I can keep a secret~
202160.unlock: Heeey! Fiji's here~! Are you the Commander? Hmmm...? Pfft... Hahaha! You don't look too shabby! Nice seeing you, Com~man~der~♪
202160.feeling2: All combat, all makeup, all the time, that's me!
202160.touch: Feeling lonely, Commander? I'm always here for you.
202160.touch2: If you wanna know my three sizes, can't you just ask? I mean, if you do, I'll tell you~ Hahaha~♪
202160.profile: Name's Fiji, I'm pretty much the nameship of my class. Things I fancy include... What? Spare the details? Then, if you're asking about my service record, all I did was fight in the Battle of Crete. Pretty rubbish record, innit... ahaha. Just gonna have to live with it and work on it, you know?
202160.main: Jamaica? Ah, yeah, proper oddball, that girl~ But it's all good as long as she's having fun, innit?|What's up? You look knackered... Fancy a nap in my lap, maybe?|Hey, take a gander at this, Commander! Fancy what I've done with my hair? How about my nails?
202160.win_mvp: Just doing my part on the battlefield, really!
202160.feeling5: Slow to catch on, aren't you~ Right, question! Could you believe there's a girl out there who's always talking about love with you, isn't afraid to undress before your eyes, and has grown quite fond of you?
202160.lose: Commander, take everyone with you and retreat! Leg it...!
202160.hp_warning: It's like back in Crete... Sod that! I'm not letting that happen again!
202160.expedition: Commission team's come back. Don't forget to go greet them! Or else you'll hurt their feelings.
202160.mail: Mail's here, Commander. I'll leave it here, so check it when you've got the time.
202160.mission: You can't just go leaving missions unfinished, Commander~ Let's go finish them. Remember: I'm right with you.

102231.detail: A bicycle must be maintained regularly, so I asked U-47 for advice and help. One day I need to offer her a favor in return.
102231.login: Is it time to sortie? Please wait. I must park my ride somewhere first.
102231.unlock: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.
102231.touch: Bicycling is an excellent way to train the body. Prepare your bicycle and we can go for a ride, Commander.
102231.main: It seems the academy has no bicycling club... Perhaps I should petition to create one... Hmm...|A new dessert shop opened, and their specialty is ice cream...? ... C-Commander, do you mind if I leave for a moment?|U-47, how about we go on a bicycling trip the next time you're off duty?
102231.drop_descrip: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.

301140.feeling4: My sisters are still laughing at me and it's your fault! What are you gonna do to fix it? I won't let you off the hook with... *Giggle*... with just a... *Giggle*... headpat...
301140.propose: Pro... mise? What's that? You mean from now you'll always pat my head, never get angry when I screw up, and let me eat tons of tasty food?! Hell yeah, I'm in!
couple_encourage: Monkey Corps {namecode:15}, strike!
I'm neither a dog nor a monkey!
301140.upgrade: Commander, take me out to the sea already. I really wanna test out my guns~
301140.battle: Awoo! I'm not gonna go easy on you all!
301140.home: Commander, Commander, wanna eat something together?
301140.login: Ugh, Commander... "Shake paws"?! Are you making fun of me?!
301140.mission_complete: Commander, Commander, hurry up and check the rewards to see if there are any snacks!
301140.feeling3: "Grr! Who will I bite today?" How's that? Awfully violent, right? ... Good, now my sisters will stop telling me I'm like a dog outside of battle!
301140.unlock: I'm {namecode:16}, fourth ship of the {namecode:15}-class. I'll tell you this right now: I'm pretty loud at night, so brace yourself.
301140.touch: Grr... Stop treating me like a kid.
301140.touch2: Grr… I'll stuff you into guns and send you off to space, you damn molester!
301140.profile: I'm {namecode:16}! People call me the "Mad Dog of Solomon"! Heheh, I sound pretty strong, don't I? I'd never lose in a brawl! Hm? It's snack time? Commander, tell me where those snacks are!
301140.main: Commander, seriously, stop throwing that frisbee at me. I'm not a dog~!|*Sniff sniff* I smell meat! Where is it?! Tell me right now!|It's so boring when I don't get to fight... Commander, wanna have a go? Let's do it!
301140.win_mvp: Missions involving breaking stuff are my specialty!
301140.feeling5: Commander, rub my belly… Huh? I've heard you should show your belly button when you're apologizing to someone... Next time I mess up I'll let you rub my belly, so don't get angry at me... Th-that tickles, ahahaha!
301140.lose: Damn it, I can't believe… I lost…
301140.hp_warning: I'll show you what the Nightmare of Solomon looks like!
301140.expedition: Commander, a commission's been... A compliment's good enough, so stop patting my head!
301140.mail: Hey, mail for you. Is it a challenge for me? I won't lose!
301140.skill: Turn to junk floating in the Solomon Sea!
301140.mission: Another new mission? You adults sure are a pain...

105120.feeling4: I always believe there is nothing wrong with being ordinary. But after meeting you Commander, I want to change myself a little... after all, my sisters are all so charismatic~ Well.. Commander, are you fond of bunny girls?~
105120.propose: Well, your trust deserves to be rewarded... umm... Commander, do you like bunny girls?~
105120.detail: Being stared like that makes a bit shy...
105120.upgrade: I'll try to work a bit harder~
105120.battle: Don’t be overconfident, and try not to be so nervous while focusing on winning~
105120.home: Ah, hold on, your collar is all messed up. Stand still while I fix it... there you go~ (waves).
105120.mission_complete: The mission rewards were sent out, are you not going to pick it up?
105120.feeling3: If you’re only going by appearances, every child in this fleet looks cute. But in terms of personality, they all have their unique quirks. To be honest, I am a bit envious of them. (strokes chin).
105120.unlock: North Carolina here, awaiting your dispatch. Although I may seem to have a bland personality compared to my sisters. But as the saying goes, no personality is still a personality, hehe. Anyways, awaiting your orders, sir.
105120.feeling2: Commander remembers me~ Not that I’m boasting or anything, but I still have confidence in my low sense of existence. (smiles wryly)
105120.touch: Do you need help with something?
105120.profile: I am North Carolina class ship no.1. I can be considered the big sister battleship of the Eagle Union~ I don’t particularly like or dislike anything, so to speak. Even though I have fought in all kinds of engagements, I have not gained any fame... I am a little bit troubled by this.
105120.main: What do I wear inside? It's not something that’s so significant |If I think about it, I certainly have been to many places... seen many landscapes, and also parted ways with many people. |Sometimes I get so envious of my younger sister Washington and how she’s so energetic all the time.
105120.win_mvp: If the Commander gives me a few praises, then I will be very happy~
105120.feeling5: Do you want to eat something later Commander? And then you can accompany me to go shopping, if you want to get something then let’s go together. Then... hehe... let’s take a walk in the park? Commander, everywhere I go as long as I’m with you will be just fine~
105120.lose: Not so successful... let's try again next time.
105120.expedition: The commission is over, they should be back soon~
105120.drop_descrip: North Carolina class battleship— North Carolina, hull number BB-55.
105120.mission: It’s not good to leave tasks unfinished.

101400.feeling4: Commander, you're the type who likes it when there's a bit more to love, right? ... I'll drink plenty of milk and eat lots of candy every day so that I can be your ideal type~
101400.propose: Commander, I don't mind if you have a thing for Lexington. But you have to swear that you absolutely love me, okay? I try my best every single day to be your ideal girl, so don't take your eyes off me, okay?
101400.detail: Commander, who do you like more - Lexington, or Saratoga? Or... perhaps some other girl has caught your eye?
couple_encourage: Lexington, I'm always here to protect you~
Dewey, take a close look at my skills~!
101400.feeling1: Commander, listen up. If this continues on, I'll be keeping my distance from you...
101400.upgrade: Hmm... I don't particularly feel any different. Whatever, a gain is a gain~
101400.battle: Everyone, let's give it our all!
101400.home: Commander, you're finally back~! Did you bring back some some delicious treats for us? Thank you so much! I'll be helping myself~♪
101400.login: Commander, welcome back. It's the start of a bright new day!
101400.mission_complete: Mission complete! It's a pretty good haul isn't it, Commander~
101400.feeling3: Compared to Dewey, I'm only a tiny bit more... H-huh? I'm not chubby! Jeez, Commander, I'm not talking to you anymore!
101400.unlock: Greetings, my name is Aylwin. I'm actually quite talented at nautical navigation, so please allow me to be your guide.
101400.feeling2: Commander, you're not too busy right now, are you? Umm, I'd like to... here, I have a little bit of candy for you~♪ Some sugar is good for the brain!
101400.touch2: Jeez, Commander... That's a foul, you know?
101400.profile: I am Aylwin, from the Eagle Union. During the war, I carried out many operations as well as training exercises, and had some ties with both the Royal Navy and Iris Libre. I admire elegant, mature women like Lexington. Commander, I look forward to working with you!
101400.main: I had a dream that I would one day share the stage with Lexington. If I could sing and dance just like her, which one of us would you support? |*pouts* Another training exercise? You keep saying next time... I want to sortie and go on real missions with everyone else! |Dewey really looks after me. Maybe she's also one of Lexington's fans, hehe~!
101400.win_mvp: Yay, I'm the MVP! Surely a wonderful commander like you would have something nice for me, right~
101400.feeling5: Commander, what's different about me today? Have you noticed yet? ...You still haven't noticed it? Hurry, hurry, hurry up and notice it, okay?
101400.lose: Oops, guess I lost... Commander, can you give me some candy to cheer me up...?
101400.expedition: The military commission has been completed. Commander, why don't we head down together to welcome everyone back?
101400.mail: Hm? There seems to be some new mail... Hrmm... Ah! Now, this seems like some good news!
101400.drop_descrip: Farragut-class destroyer – Aylwin, Hull Number DD-355.
101400.skill: Looks like it's time for Aylwin to get serious!
101400.mission: New missions have been posted~ Let's hurry up and set sail! Just kidding, we still have plenty of time right now.

105190.feeling4: I like how cool you look when you're pushing yourself hard... but overdoing it isn't good. I'll force you to rest if I have to.
105190.propose: Umm, yeah... I already know what you want to do and want to say... Because I love you too, Commander.
105190.detail: Tell me when you're done inspecting.
couple_encourage: The way you are now... I like it. This is good.
I envy your defense, sis...
105190.feeling1: Your body is weak, Commander. Are you eating properly?
105190.battle: Pretty tough, aren't you? You won't cry if I hit you, will you?
105190.home: You're back... Did you get hurt? If anyone pokes fun at you, we can talk about it.
105190.login: For lunch, I'll make... Oh, Commander, are you going for a stroll?
105190.mission_complete: Ah, the rewards have arrived... Seems we can afford beef for dinner tonight.
105190.feeling3: Seeing you challenging yourself with things you can't do is... interesting. It makes me want to explore my own limits, too.
105190.unlock: Hm? Ah... my turn to speak. I'm Massachusetts. I'm just a regular old South Dakota-class you can find anywhere... So, yeah, I hope we can... get along.
105190.feeling2: How to get stronger? Uhh, do some push-ups? ... Not working for you?
105190.touch: You want someone to pamper you? ... You want ME to?
105190.touch2: ... If you'd move your body more, you'd have fewer weird thoughts.
105190.profile: I guess I'm the most normal ship in my class. I earned 11 battle stars, which is less than South Dakota did. "I hardly suffered any damage"? That's cause I never fought anyone strong enough... Here's hoping that I'll get to fight as hard as my sister did back then.
105190.main: ... You know, I actually like this hair color. It's like that of a bald eagle, isn't it?|You think my jacket is strange? This way I can feel the breeze hit my skin when out at sea, though... I love it.|People that impressed me? Umm... when I was in Casablanca, I fought a battleship who held out a long time even with just a single turret... I'd like to fight her again in her finished state.
105190.win_mvp: It's over already? But I was just warming up... Aren't there any other enemies left?
105190.feeling5: I don't have any dreams. But I have the power to grant them. Commander, do you have a dream for me to grant one day?
105190.hp_warning: ... So you want me to get serious?
105190.expedition: ... Oh, look. They've brought so much back. I'll go help them out.
105190.mail: I'll leave your letter here. Check it later.
105190.drop_descrip: South Dakota-class battleship – Massachusetts, Hull Number BB-59.
105190.mission: So many missions waiting on us...

207020.feeling4: G-good grief... If you were the same size as those destroyers, Commander, I wouldn't be so embarrassed... I was fine with doing this with the little ones... but with you...
207020.propose: I'll take care of all the destroyers from now on! No one can touch Commander or my destroyers. No one!
couple_encourage: I feel so strong now!
I've got to set an example for the others!
207020.feeling1: You can't compare with the destroyers, Commander...
207020.upgrade: Oh! oh! oh! Allow me to protect you, my destroyer friends!
207020.battle: Is that it? Hah! Swordfish squadron, prepare for battle!
207020.home: Is it time for a break? I'm going to see my destroyer sisters then!
207020.login: Ready for orders, Commander. I am confident in any kind of battle!
207020.mission_complete: Commander, to leave your rewards unclaimed is disrespect to the mission.
207020.feeling3: I thought you were finally going to have me Court Martialed, Commander! I'm grateful to finally be recognized by you. It's nothing to be ashamed of? Commander, I, Ark Royal, will follow you forever!
207020.unlock: Ark Royal, reporting in for duty! I am confident in all manners of battle. Why, it was I who managed to destroy Bismarck's rudder!
207020.feeling2: I... I'm going to say this in advance, but... those destroyer girls... u-um... I kid of... I mean... I kind of hold them dear... I know how to mind my manners... It's not... it's not a crime!
207020.touch: Your warm hands keep me energized to keep fighting, Commander!
207020.touch2: Eh... Commander... please don't... Why are you doing this?!
207020.profile:
Ark Royal, reporting in! I'm the first aircraft carrier specifically designed and built for the role in the Royal Navy, I'm proud of being a prototype to all other carriers that followed. 
 Little needs to be said about my feats against the Bismarck. Rather I must ask, are there any of those cute little destroyers in our fleet?

105110.propose: You’ve decided to perform a pledge ritual with me? Commander really made a bold decision... In that case, I will not let your expectation down. I'll guard you until the very end.
105110.detail: Do not doubt my combat performance, Commander.
105110.feeling1: Commander's laziness is almost beyond my bottom line.
105110.upgrade: It seems the Spokane Cup this year will still be mine.
105110.battle: The humiliation I once suffered... I'll repay you double!
105110.home: What a peaceful port, it reminds me of Hawaii before the war.
105110.login: You’re late... the exercise has already begun, hurry!
105110.mission_complete: The mission was nicely executed, good one.
105110.feeling3: I’m proud of my BIG SEVEN title. But aircraft carriers seem to be replacing us battleships in naval battles. I am losing myself in all this confusion: this strength that I possess... what is it for?
105110.unlock: It’s finally my time to show my strength... Under the guidance of fate, the third ship of Colorado class, West Virginia, reporting in.
105110.feeling2: I was once seriously injured, but then I was greatly enhanced during the process for my repairs…
105110.touch: This should be... a friendly gesture I suppose.
105110.touch2: Commander, it seems you’re rather close to getting lectured by me.
105110.profile: During a "Naval Holiday", my sisters and I were honored amongst the world's strongest battleships. We were granted the high-profile title of - BIG SEVEN. Although times are changing, the three of us still have the strength to fight any enemy fleet in a decisive battle, please don't forget that.
105110.main: The combat exercise didn’t go well… Is the Commander being lazy again? |I will never forget the humiliation I suffered on that day. |On the night of the Surigao Strait, I witnessed the last moments of the Sakura Empire fleet... They truly are a worthy opponent...
105110.win_mvp: Have you seen this? This is the inevitably tragic ending of those who dare challenge the BIG SEVEN.
105110.feeling5: Commander, you have become someone who can completely take charge on the battlefield. At last, my powers have found a worthy partner... What? A love confession? Don't you trick me to say that, you fool——
105110.lose: I don't want to recall the humiliation I suffered on that day...!
105110.hp_warning: Getting hit by a torpedo... it feels bad.
105110.expedition: The commission fleet is really efficient. I hope the Commander can learn a thing or two about efficiency.
105110.mail: Could these be letters from my sisters?
105110.drop_descrip: Colorado class battleship— West Virginia, hull number BB-48.
105110.skill: Have a taste of my 406mm guns!
105110.mission: Carrying out missions is an important part of enhancing the strength of the fleet.

205029.login: My range extends even farther. Commander, send me out to fight, won't you?
205029.unlock: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!
205029.touch: Commander, if you have something to say, just come out and say it. I'm happy to listen.
205029.touch2: My important parts haven't grown at all...? Seems like someone wants to taste my high-angle mounts...
205029.main: It is my duty as your secretary ship to counsel you, Commander. I won't hesitate to speak my mind if you make a poor decision.|Survival is the key to becoming a stronger person.|Battle is the fire that feeds one's growth. And so I fight with all that I have, in every conflict.
205029.drop_descrip: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!

205021.detail: The wreath that goes on Her Majesty's door... Hmm, Belfast told me that the best way to make it is with seashells! Commander, let's head out to sea to collect some!
205021.home: Good. Since you are here, I can proceed to my next battleground - the important mission of delivering these gifts!
205021.login: Even warriors need to rest. Since it's a holiday, you shouldn't be too uptight either.
205021.unlock: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!
205021.touch: Commander, come help me decorate this Christmas tree - I'm not tall enough to reach... W-wait, who gave you permission to pick me up?!
205021.main: Commander, do you want a present as well? If you really want one that badly, it's not like I can't give you one... |Hmm... what present should I pick out for Her Majesty? It can't be too expensive or too cheap, and it can't be too exotic or too ordinary. What exactly can I get her? |If I'm delivering Christmas presents, it's only natural to go through the chimney... Eh? Wouldn't that make me seem suspicious?
205021.feeling5: Apologies, Commander, it seems like our Christmas together was a bit unromantic. You... enjoyed it just fine? Heh, you're always like this... Well, at least, let us enjoy the rest of the night together while the bells of the Holy Night toll.
205021.drop_descrip: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!
205021.mission: Commander, while you're out delegating missions, mind helping me deliver this present to one of the kids along the way?

205011.detail: We shall allow you to bask in our splendor! ... Now out with your praise already! Lowly servant!
205011.unlock: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!
205011.touch: Hm, hmph! ... Considering the lengths to which you went for this party, we shall overlook your boorishness for now. Be grateful for your queen's leniency! Lowly servant!
205011.touch2: Aie! Warspite!! Level your fifteen-inch guns at this insolent servant! Off with its heeaaaaaad!!
205011.main: So as not to embarrass me at the party, you need to practice your dancing! Y-you could practice with m-... You don't want to bother me?! B-b-but it really wouldn't be much trouble!|It is a servant's duty to clear the way for the Queen, are we clear?!|Bel! Is everything ready for the party? N-not that I'm excited about it or anything! I'm just supervising my maids!
205011.drop_descrip: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!

301261.detail: Commander, Belfast taught me a lot about being a maid! ... But if Ariake saw me now, she'd probably be... shocked.
301261.home: Welcome back. I was going to hide my tail and ears, but Shoukaku told me I look cuter this way... B-but saying "meow, meow~" is too embarrassing for me...
301261.login: Welcome back, Commander. I've left your juice over here. As for the resources... I'm still sorting them... I'm sorry...
301261.feeling3: I baked a Royal Navy-style cake! I'm certain this time it'll be a hit!
301261.unlock: "I, Yuugure the maid, shall dedicate myself to Ariake, my sister, and you, Commander!"... Eek?! M-my skirt...!
301261.touch: Phew... I'm done sorting the resources... Now for the next task...
301261.touch2: ... Commander, please don't do such things to me!
301261.main: Edinburgh taught me a lot as well... She seemed to make a number of mistakes, but I still appreciate her kindness!|nil|As soon as Mikasa saw me, she yelled "Scandalous! Taisho-era servitors would never wear skirts this frilly!"... Even though I wasn't born in the Taisho-era...
301261.win_mvp: "T-this glorious victory i-is in my Master's name!" ... *Whimper*... I can't deliver lines like these...
301261.feeling5: A maid's job is to provide service and relieve people. ... Commander, do you find my service to be relieving?
301261.mail: I asked Maya to take a picture of me and send it to Ariake, and she did!
301261.drop_descrip: "I, Yuugure the maid, shall dedicate myself to Ariake, my sister, and you, Commander!"... Eek?! M-my skirt...!

204020.feeling4: Com~man~der! Gotcha! Hmm? I'm too close? Hey, what's the problem with that~ Anyway, come and play with me~!
204020.propose: Huh?! You're happy with me? I'm not as elegant as some other royal girls, and I don't dress all that great... But when it comes to my feelings for you, I rank second to none!
204020.detail: Hi, Commander! I changed into something a little easier to move around in~
204020.feeling1: It's kinda boring being here with you... I'm heading out for a while!
204020.upgrade: Commander, want to go take a stroll out to sea? I'll protect you!
204020.battle: Vaporize anything that moves into ash!
204020.home: You can't rest right after reaching port! Go exercise more!
204020.login: Hello, Commander! Let's go beat the heck out of our enemies!
204020.feeling3: My sister always says I'm too impatient, but I can't be bothered thinking everything through. Besides, you're always around, so I'll leave all the thinking to you, Commander!
204020.unlock: I'm Repulse, a Renown-class battlecruiser. I participated in the pursuit of Bismarck, but we couldn't catch up to her. Ever since then I've been a part of Force Z... I don't ever want to see a torpedo again...
204020.feeling2: It's so boring indoors! Being outdoors is so much better... Commander, don't you feel bad sitting around all day? Let's go out and get some fresh air!
204020.touch: Huh? I thought you'd be into softer girls than me...
204020.touch2: Whoah! S-stop… You're awful! I'm a girl, you know!
204020.profile: I'm Repulse, a Renown-class battlecruiser. I may not look like much, but I've been tons of places with the higher-ups! Though I prefer going out on my own! "Repairs"? Ahahaha, I'm hoping you won't keep me locked up indoors every day, Commander...
204020.main: Hey! Com~man~der~! Let's get some exercise~!|You look strong, Commander. Want to spar sometime?|Huh? You think I'm impatient?
204020.win_mvp: Hooray! We won! Quick, decisive victories are my favourite.
204020.feeling5: You know, Commander, I am a girl after all. I'm not so crazy I'd defencelessly cling to someone I don't like. It's about time you noticed...
204020.lose: Ahh, the enemy was so persistent that I'm starving now... There's no way we could've won like this...
204020.expedition: You've made me stay with you inside, so, as your punishment, you'll have to accompany me to check up on the completed commissions. Let's go!
204020.mail: Deliverygirl Repulse has arrived with your mail!

403050.feeling4: Commander, rather than sink all alone, will I be able to face my final moments together with you this time?
403050.propose: Although I cannot hug you, you can hug me... Hey, Commander, just for a little longer... hold me tight like this...
403050.detail: No matter how poor the odds are, I will always head for the battlefield. ...That way people will admire me.
couple_encourage: Stay away from me...
You're still a dirty sadist, I see.
It's an honor to fight alongside you again.
403050.feeling1: No matter how you treat me, Commander, I will obey you...
403050.headtouch: Commander, could you not ruffle up my hair like that...?
403050.battle: For the honor and prosperity of Iron Blood, and for even greater glory!
403050.home: Commander, you've confirmed the port isn't being blockaded, right?
403050.login: I will fight for you till the very end.
403050.mission_complete: I see that, unlike me in the past, you actually finished your mission.
403050.feeling3: These hands are for grasping victory... Even though I will never again be able to hug the people important to me, what's done is done.
403050.unlock: No matter where I go, the war never ends... Deutschland-class armored ship number 3, Admiral Graf Spee, reporting for duty.
403050.feeling2: I sailed alone, fought alone, and sunk alone... Although I am who I am, didn't I still contribute to Iron Blood's cause?
403050.touch: It's sunny today? Yeah... just like it was back on the Río de la Plata.
403050.touch2: Commander, may I hug you, even though my hands are like this?
403050.profile: Admiral Graf Spee, Deutschland-class armored cruiser number 3 of the Iron Blood Navy. I was attacked by Royal Navy cruisers and then took refuge in Montevideo, but in the end I scuttled myself... Commander, this time I'm going to fight! To the very end!
403050.main: Wars don't exist for mindless slaughter, they exist for victory.|One's first battle being their last... That sort of thing isn't all that unusual for us Iron Blood ships.|Give talking to people... a try? I've always been alone, so what am I supposed to talk about...
403050.win_mvp: How long will this victory actually last...
403050.feeling5: No matter how much I fight, I can't fill the void in my heart... And being away from you is the reason why...
403050.lose: We've lost... But I'm not giving up! It's not over yet!
403050.hp_warning: I have to hold out just a little longer...!
403050.expedition: A commission has been completed? That means they weren't ambushed. Thank goodness.
403050.mail: This letter... Thank goodness, it has nothing to do with Renown.
403050.drop_descrip: Deutschland-class armored cruiser number three – Admiral Graf Spee.
403050.skill: In the name of all that is dear to me!
403050.mission: Once we've been assigned a mission, we must complete it, no matter what it is.

202261.drop_descrip: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?

301262.login: Welcome back, Commander. I'm about to go wish my sister a happy new year, as is customary in the Dragon Empery... Would you like to come with me?
301262.unlock: The Dragon Empery's New Year celebrations and new outfits are sure to lift everyone's spirits~ My sister will probably love this new dress as well. What do you think, Commander?
301262.touch: I have to tell my sister about all the customs I learned from the Dragon Empery!
301262.main: Do they eat New Year's rice cake in the Dragon Empery as well? Perhaps they just eat whatever they feel like eating. |A red envelope from you? Please don't forget to give one to my sister as well. |Commander, our dreams will come true this year... right? N-no, I'm sure they will!
301262.feeling5: My New Year's wish, huh? Um... if I had to say, it'd probably be to celebrate even more New Years with Commander and my sister...
301262.mail: I'll leave the mail that just arrived over here. I wonder if my sister sent me a greeting card?
301262.drop_descrip: The Dragon Empery's New Year celebrations and new outfits are sure to lift everyone's spirits~ My sister will probably love this new dress as well. What do you think, Commander?

203060.feeling4: Ah, could it be that you've developed feelings beyond friendship for me? In that case I must properly respond to them.
203060.propose: You sure are a weird person, Commander. To chase after me who is but a tiny star to the bright moon that is my sister. But I too am attracted to you, if you are okay with someone like me then I would be happy to accept.
203060.detail: My big sister is definitely cuter, at least compared to me.
203060.feeling1: I really can't compare to my sister...
203060.upgrade: I'll continue to do my best, with my big sister as my goal~
203060.battle: I'll do my best to not embarrass my sister!
203060.home: Good work, Commander! Come, sit and have some tea. I will tell you some things about my sister~
203060.login: Welcome back~ What are we going to do today?
203060.mission_complete: Here are your rewards! Please take good care of them.
203060.feeling3: I'm fine the way I am? Aha, you really know how to give compliments, Commander. Compared to my sister though, I'm still but an ugly duckling.
203060.unlock: Hello, I'm Norfolk's little sister, Dorsetshire~! I look more mature than my sister? Surely you jest! She's my role model!
203060.feeling2: It's not an exaggeration to say my sister is a world treasure, a gift from the heavens. It's an honor for me to have a sister like her.
203060.touch: So, Commander, you think I'm actually a bit too big?
203060.profile: The offshoot of the County-class, the Norfolk-class, includes me and my sisters. My proudest achievement was giving chase to Bismarck and not letting my sister's intel go to waste. I am still far from matching her, so I must become a sister she can be proud of!
203060.main: Is it not common knowledge that my big sister is the cutest in the world?| For allowing me to use the intel my sister gave me, Bismarck is such a generous person.|If it's about my sister, I could speak for three days and three nights and still not be done.
203060.win_mvp: This gets me one step closer to my big sister~
203060.feeling5: Though we speak of it, I've never thought I would such a day would come... How should I react?... Commander, can you teach me?
203060.hp_warning: This is a bit of a struggle...
203060.expedition: Ah, the commission team is back~! Commander, could you let me go on a commission with my sister next time?
203060.drop_descrip:
Norfolk-class heavy cruiser, Dorsetshire, Hull Number 40
<color=#ffde38>Unlock build after receiving</color>
203060.skill: Sister, please lend me your strength!
203060.mission: Missions, huh? Makes me think of all the time I spent with my sister.

403051.detail: I'm trying hard to learn about everyday things. Living a normal life is not so simple, compared to fighting...
403051.battle: Don't go around disturbing the girls at the academy.
403051.login: Eugen taught me how to use makeup, but... does it actually make me look pretty...?
403051.unlock: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?
403051.touch: Deutschland? Could you stop using your megaphone to shout "people who harass the girl with my phone will be expelled"... It's embarrassing, and more importantly, it's really distracting...
403051.main: My pantyhose? Ajax gave me them as an enrollment gift... I examined them very thoroughly and didn't find anything weird, but I doubt they're just a normal pair of stockings...|Viersechs doesn't like picture books? I see... Everyone else in the Z-class seems to like them, though...|Hipper? Want some snacks? I get it. "Not really" means "yes" in your dictionary. Okay, say "aah."
403051.feeling5: Does getting a hug from me like this cheer you up a little, Commander?
403051.mail: This mail... it's not another one of Ajax's pranks, is it?!
403051.drop_descrip: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?

201270.feeling4: We should all forget our worries and live to have fun! Don't you think so too, Commander?
201270.propose: Thank you, Commander! This is the best thing I've ever gotten! Hey, tell me: have I given you some good memories, too?
201270.detail: Is it fun to hang out with me, Commander? ...Ah, sorry, never mind that.
201270.feeling1: Come on... Return to your former self, Commander...
201270.home: Take a gander at my new marching act, Commander! Relax, I'm only using blanks this time!
201270.login: Morning, Commander! Nice weather today! Click, click... bang! I'm not sure why, but I'm always brimming with energy!
201270.mission_complete: Hehehe~ It's just human instinct to smile at the sight of money! Yeah, that's it! Smile, Commander~!
201270.feeling3: I always have tons of fun hanging out with you!
201270.unlock: I am the M-class Destroyer, Musketeer! Hehe... I knew something good was going to happen today~ Commander, can you point me to where the port is? Here? Or over here?!
201270.feeling2: No matter what life throws at you, always be optimistic, happy, and positive! You just gotta be!
201270.touch: Hehehe~! You've reloaded me with energy!
201270.touch2: It's not like I *dislike* it, but... Yeah, I actually don't dislike it!
201270.profile: I'm the Royal Navy M-class destroyer Musketeer! I was in the Battle of the North Cape! Commander, little Musketeer is gonna shoot straight through your dreary heart with a bang bang!
201270.main: Something nice is gonna happen today~ That's what I'm feeling!|Why am I always smiling? Hehehe, because I've been having so much fun ever since I came here!|The injuries I've sustained from combat? Hehehe, they don't hurt at all.
201270.win_mvp: I'm gonna punch a hole straight through your heart~! Heheh, I've always wanted to say that!
201270.feeling5: So much has happened since we first met... But I haven't changed a bit!
201270.lose: Time to make a sneaky exit~♫
201270.expedition: Wooow! Look at those mission rewards! We could fill a bathtub with all this oil!
201270.mail: Heehee~! See? I told you something nice would happen today!
201270.skill: Locked and loaded~! Ready to fire!
201270.mission: Finish them all in one go!

301263.detail: When a girl wears a different outfit, your impression of her changes, doesn't it? I hope they can make a different outfit for Ariake, too...
301263.headtouch: What's the matter...? "Am I nervous"? I-I'm fine... I think... It's just a bit embarrassing to show myself wearing these clothes to others...
301263.home: Excellent work. I know the party is about to begin, but it's okay to rest a little... and have a snack before we head out.
301263.login: I've heard parties are "a world of fun for adults." C-Commander, could you accompany me to this "world of fun for adults"...?
301263.unlock: I finished changing, Commander. This dress is very pretty, but... isn't it missing something up top?
301263.touch: Once I've grown a little more, I'll be able to keep my composure even in places like these.
301263.main: It's beautiful when flower petals flicker in the wind, but also a little sad, in a way... Do you know what I mean, Commander?|I-I'm fine with just juice! ... Ah, thank you!|I feel like maybe I should bring back some sweets for Ariake... Huh? Am I not allowed to...?
301263.feeling5: Commander, thank you for keeping me company until the party... C-could you take my hand and join me for a dance, like you would with an adult...?
301263.drop_descrip: I finished changing, Commander. This dress is very pretty, but... isn't it missing something up top?

802011.detail: Commander, how about a game of beach volleyball? I actually happen to be quite good at it♪
802011.home: My, you're so excited, Commander♪ I knew you were looking forward to the beach~
802011.login: Commander, don't forget to stretch before going into the ocean, okay?
802011.unlock: Commander, does my swimsuit pique your fancy? I'm actually quite proud of my fashion sense. *Giggle* Now, let's enjoy midsummer together~
802011.touch: Go on ahead without you? Why, a secretary can't just casually part from her Commander, can she? I'll be right here waiting for you♪
802011.touch2: It seems as summer comes forth, so too does your passion~
802011.main: Commander, could I ask you to apply sunscreen to my skin next time we go to the beach?|Long hair is quite inconvenient when you're swimming... Which way of tying up my hair is your favorite, Commander?|Oh, Commander~ Since we're going to the beach, why not change into your swim gear ahead of time? Oh, no, I definitely don't want to see how it looks on you, not at all~
802011.drop_descrip: Commander, does my swimsuit pique your fancy? I'm actually quite proud of my fashion sense. *Giggle* Now, let's enjoy midsummer together~

402029.login: Ehehe, I have a feeling that something good's gonna happen today~!
402029.unlock: Here, here, Commander - It's me, Karlsruhe! How do I look~?
402029.main: nil|Ack, a storm's coming!? |I'm boooored~! Keep quiet? There's no way I can keep doing that~!

202150.feeling4: Commander, come here for a moment~ ... Hehe, this rose suits you best after all! Eh? I'm not making fun of you... In that case, why don't you pick one out to put on me? I'm sure I'll love whatever you pick~
202150.propose: "A rose by any name would smell as sweet." Whether I am called Aurora, the "Goddess of Dawn," or even Chongqing, I am still the same me. Yes... I will always be at your side.
202150.detail: Commander, is there anything I can help you with regarding equipment?
202150.feeling1: Commander, please refrain from making a fool of yourself in public.
202150.upgrade: Commander, I'll be able to help with even more things now~
202150.battle: May we be blessed with victory~
202150.home: Good work. Please take some time to relax.
202150.login: My name symbolises the break of dawn. Ehehe~ Do you feel more energetic from seeing me?
202150.mission_complete: Some mission rewards had not yet been collected, so I retrieved them in your stead.
202150.feeling3: The goddess, Aurora, was said to have "rose-coloured fingers." Though the same can't be said for me, my fingers at least smell like roses. Commander, want to check for yourself?
202150.unlock: Greetings, Commander. I am the fourth ship of the Arethusa-class light cruisers, Aurora. From now on, I shall serve as your secretary. Please feel free to ask anything of me~
202150.feeling2: Commander, would you like to see the roses that I planted? I have a lot of different kinds~
202150.touch: Commander, want to take a break and come water the flowers with me?
202150.touch2: Commander! I... I'm going to be mad! Jeez! I'll really get mad!
202150.profile: I am Aurora of the Royal Navy, fourth ship of the Arethusa-class. You are welcome to call me the "Goddess of Dawn," but please forget any nasty-sounding nicknames you might hear like the "Silver Phantom." Commander, perhaps you are familiar with some of the other names that I've been called?
202150.main: Eastern Radiance? Oh, it's a great place. Mm... for example... |Even though I don't mind if you stare at me, please do your work properly~ |Hold still, Commander, there's something stuck on your cheek... There! Now, please do your best at work~
202150.feeling5: Lately, some girls have been grumbling that I've been monopolosing all your time... But, I'm not going to back down on this. Commander, you too should be prepared to deal with a bunch of sulking girls~
202150.lose: It seems I have not yet become accustomed to the battlefield...
202150.hp_warning: Light of dawn, illuminate our path...!
202150.expedition: Commander, it will be a problem if you keep staring at me and forget about the girls who have returned from commission.
202150.mail: There's new mail, shall I read it aloud for you?
202150.drop_descrip: Arethusa-class light cruiser - Aurora, pennant number 12
202150.skill: Commander, helping you solve problems and leave worries behind is also part of my job~
202150.mission: Commander, a new mission dossier has been issued. I have already highlighted the most important parts, so please look over it.

202124.drop_descrip: Hehe~ Judging from your expression, Master, my outfit has not fallen short of your expectations. As time is precious, allow me to serve you to the utmost on this "date."

202123.drop_descrip: Good evening. The Royal Maids will be chaperoning this event. It is my hope to prevent any inappropriate behaviour that might interfere with the enjoyment of the attendees. Please pardon any inconveniences this may cause.

402030.feeling4: To... to prevent you from harassing my sisters... I-I will... (blushes)
402030.propose: With this... I can get much closer to Commander! A-ahem... it's nothing! Thank you, Commander, I won't let you down.
402030.detail: Commander, what kind of data are you looking for?
402030.feeling1: Workplace harassment is a crime, Commander...
402030.upgrade: Commander, you're a very kind person... for taking care of your subordinates.
402030.home: Good work, Commander. The next thing on the agenda is...
402030.login: Welcome back, Commander. Here is today's schedule. Please look it over.
402030.mission_complete: Mission complete! Shall I take an inventory of the rewards?
402030.feeling3: I'm so glad that you are an approachable superior. I can't really handle short-tempered people.
402030.unlock: You seem like a wise Commander. I'm Köln. Please rest assured and let me take care of your work.
402030.feeling2: Is there anything that I can help with? Please let me know.
402030.touch2: Commander... You realize that harrassing one's subordinates is despicable, right?

301013.detail: Didn't think an instrument could be so fun! I have to teach others about the joy of music!
301013.battle: Maybe my tuba... is useful in battle after all...?
301013.home: Did my pre-sortie motivational song serve you well, Commander?
301013.login: My marching solo will wake you up, Commander!
301013.unlock: Check it out, Commander! What do you think? ... No, not my dress! I'm talking about the tuba! Want me to play a tune for you~?
301013.touch: Do you wanna hear a song, Commander? You got it! Manjuus, you all ready to go?
301013.touch2: Whuah! ... Don't expect me to feel bad if I smack you with this thing, Commander!
301013.main: Let me play you a motivational song, Commander! Tooooot! ... Wh-what? That's annoying...? Sorry!|You should learn an instrument so we can play a song together, Commander!|Oh yeah, what do you think about my dress, Commander? Does it suit me? I absolutely adore it, it's all fluffy and stuff!
301013.win_mvp: Okay, let's play a victory march to celebrate... H-hey! Wait for meeee!
301013.feeling5: If I ever perform on stage, will you be there to listen, Commander? Actually, it'd be even better if you could be my maestro~
301013.expedition: Tooooot! The commission team has come back, Commander! ... No surprise: this tuba's reminding potential is totally next-level♪
301013.drop_descrip: Check it out, Commander! What do you think? ... No, not my dress! I'm talking about the tuba! Want me to play a tune for you~?

103069.detail: Commander, did you know? Indy is thiiiiiiis cute!
103069.unlock: Nice to meet you, I'm Indianaportland! ... Hm? Who's Indy? She's my precious little sister, and my most beloved...
103069.main: Commander, you're not getting away anymore! Come here, I'm gonna tell you all about my special Indy mags! Today's the day that I'll fully drill Indy's appeal into your head!|I didn't miss any major battles, you say? Well... if I'd have missed any of Indy's cute moments then I'd regret it so much I'd want to cry!|...! *Gasp* My Indy Cuteness Sensor is going off! Commander, you'll have to excuse me for a bit!
103069.drop_descrip: Nice to meet you, I'm Indianaportland! ... Hm? Who's Indy? She's my precious little sister, and my most beloved...

102093.detail: What kind of music do you like, Commander? I've gotta have the stuff that gets you pumped up.
102093.home: Let's go outside and get some stretching in, Commander~
102093.login: Ready to go, Commander? We're about to go chase the wind!
102093.unlock: Good timing! I was just about to take my little buddy here out for a road trip! Commander, there's room for two if you want to come!
102093.touch: Commander, you should pick out a bike too! Just leave the paint job to me, hehe!
102093.main: I did this guy's paint job myself. Pretty sweet, huh? Hehe~ |Don't let the size fool you. This little guy has some serious kick! |Even when we're out for a spin, we have to observe the traffic rules. Safety first, after all~
